But consuming too much of the strain can knock you out for good if you are not careful. On the other hand, the strain is equally effective at treating medical conditions like insomnia, muscle spasms, anorexia and stress.

Girl Scout Wookies.name: Girl Scout Wookies
Girl Scout Wookies.description: Girl Scout Wookies, also known as “Wookies” or “Wookies Cookies,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Girl Scout Cookies X The White strains. Sorry to say – these cookies were not made by Chewbacca. Rather, they were bred to capitalize on the gorgeous appearance of The White and the potency of GSC, giving Girl Scout Wookies beautiful nugs and a whopping 28% average THC level. Girl Scout Wookies buds have tight minty green grape-shaped nugs with long thin orange hairs and a super thick frosty coating of glittering bright white crystal trichomes. As each dazzling little nug is broken apart, rich aromas of pungent florals and fresh kush with a touch of sour citrus cream are released. The flavor follows suit, blending citrus cream with fresh sweet herbs and pine for a mouthwatering treat that will leave you begging for more. Don't fall victim to the flavor – Girl Scout Wookies is definitely a one-hitter. The high comes on fast and hard, rushing into your mind with a deep-felt sense of euphoria that leaves you uplifted with a sense of creative motivation. As your mind reaches higher and higher, your body will start to sink lower and lower into a potent body high that reaches from limb to limb. Thanks to these effects and its potent THC level, Girl Scout Wookies is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic fatigue, nausea, chronic stress or anxiety, depression, and chronic pain.

Girl Scout Yeti.name: Girl Scout Yeti
Girl Scout Yeti.description: Girl Scout Yeti, also known as “Headband GSC” or “HeadbandGirl Scout Cookies,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the potent Girl Scout Cookies X Yeti OG strains. With its super high average THC level of 29% and CBD level of 3%, this bud packs potent effects that are also medical in nature. The high starts with an uplifted relaxing effect that leaves you happy and carefree for hours on end. You'll feel any negative or racing thoughts be gently eased away as your mind and body settle into a state of long-lasting peace and tranquility. Thanks to these effects and its high potency, Girl Scout Yeti is said to be the perfect choice for patients suffering from conditions such as nausea, stress, inflammation, chronic pain, and migraines or headaches. This bud has a super tasty flavor of sweet berry-flavored candy with a spicy exhale that lingers long after your last hit. The aroma is very similar, although with a hint of pungency to it. Girl Scout Yeti buds have thick light green spade-shaped nugs with amber furry hairs and a coating of matching crystal trichomes.

Girl Time.name: Girl Time
Girl Time.description: Girl Time, also known as “Girl Time!” or “Girl's Time,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through crossing the potent Girl Scout Cookies X Trainwreck strains. Bred specifically to treat the symptoms of PMS, Girl Time is the perfect choice for any woman who's looking for some sweet relief from cramps. The high comes on with a creeping effect, sneaking into both mind and body with a light tingle that is stimulating yet soothing. You'll feel mentally lifted with a sense of happiness that instantly erases any negative or racing thoughts. Your body will feel stimulated yet relaxed, filled with a sense of calm that negates any aches and pains. Your heady state will soon turn hazy, leaving you giggling and unfocused, laughing at anything and everything around you. Combined with its moderate 11-15% average THC level and super high 19-27% average CBD level, these effects give Girl Time an edge in treating a variety of conditions including PMS, chronic stress or anxiety, Parkinson's disease, epilepsy and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and fruity berry mango flavor with a sour citrusy exhale. The aroma is sweet and fruity with a tropical sour citrus overtone accented by woody pine and a hint of creamy cheese. Girl Time buds have hand-shaped dense forest green nugs with blue-green undertones, thin orange hairs and tiny blue-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Glacier OG.name: Glacier OG
Glacier OG.description: Glacier OG is a rare heavily indica dominant hybrid strain (90% indica/10% sativa) created through crossing the classic Snowcap X Double Barrel OG strains. Named for its gorgeously frosty appearance, Glacier OG buds have super oversized fluffy minty green nugs with clear hairs and a super thick coating of sparkling bright white tiny crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each glittering little nugget, sharp aromas of sour diesel and lemony pine are released. The flavor is of lemon-lime with a hint of sour diesel upon exhale that turns spicy and herbal the more that you toke. The Glacier OG high settles into your mind a while after your final hit, sneaking up on you before taking hold with a super relaxing and stoney lift. As your mind flies higher and higher, your body will begin to settle deeper and deeper into the couch, leaving you totally out of it and unable to move. This quickly turns sedative, which will have you dozing in no time at all. With these long-lasting effects and its super high 20-25% average THC level, Glacier OG is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, chronic pain, depression, and appetite loss or nausea.

Glazed Cherry.name: Glazed Cherry
Glazed Cherry.description: Glazed Cherry, also known as “Glazed Cherries,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through a cross of the insanely delicious Cherry OG X Girl Scout Cookies Strains. Like the name suggests, Glazed Cherry has a crazy delicious flavor that's just like a sweet sugary cherry topped with vanilla and cream. The aroma is much harsher, with a skunky pungent overtone that's incredibly dank, which is complemented by sweet berries and fruit as the nugs are broken apart and burned. The Glazed Cherry high is just as sweet, with a happy head high that's incredibly relaxing without weighing you down in the slightest. As this blissful state builds and builds, you'll be infused with a mild sense of energy that can get you off the couch if need be, but isn't really enough to get you motivated to do anything physical. Because of these effects and its powerful 21-23% average THC level, Glazed Cherry is often chosen by patients who suffer from conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress or anxiety, and nausea. This bud has small and leafy super airy forest green popcorn-shaped nugs with long thin amber hairs and a thick frosty coating of tiny milky clear trichomes.

Glookies.name: Glookies
Glookies.description: Glookies is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (20% sativa/80% indica) created through crossing the infamous Girl Scout Cookies X Original Glue (AKA – Gorilla Glue #4) strains. This celebrity child is a patient and breeder favorite thanks to its seemingly flawless combination of effects from both of its parent strains. The high starts with a cerebral influx of lifted creativity and motivation, filling you with the artistic inspiration that you need to take on any task that you have at hand. This is accompanied by a growing sense of euphoria and happiness that fills both mind and body with a warming effect without causing any sedation or anxiety. With these long-lasting effects and its moderately high 15-19% average THC level, Glookies is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from chronic pain, insomnia, PTSD, chronic stress or anxiety and ADD or ADHD. Glookies has a sweet nutty cookie flavor with a chocolaty diesel overtone that lingers long after your final exhale. The aroma is of earthy diesel and pungent chocolate with a spicy overtone that intensifies as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Glookies buds have rounded bright neon green nugs with dark olive leaves, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Glowing Goat #5.name: Glowing Goat #5
Glowing Goat #5.description: The glowing goat is another, relatively new, hybrid strain. With a THC level of around 20% and a CBD level less than 0.5%, this strain is relatively light in terms of strength. The glowing goat #5 is the result of a combination/cross between the Golden Goat and The White which makes it one of the more unique hybrid strains around. The glowing goat is prescribed to patients that are suffering from a severe lack of appetite or have muscular pain. In other words, it is great for appetite stimulation. This strain is recommended for a day time smoke or for occasions such as, say, a quick happy hour. This means that the strain is not too strong and is not bad for people suffering from insomnia. This particular strain has no discernible aroma to it. The closest the aroma comes to is that of herbs. Taste is where this strain really shines. It has two dominant types of tastes, spicy and fruity at the same time. Most smokers find mango as the base taste for it with just a hint of Sriracha (a type of hot sauce). In terms of appearances, it is covered with small patches of light and dark green with a few orange hairs.

Glucifer.name: Glucifer
Glucifer.description: Glucifer, also known as “Gluecifer” or “Glucifer OG,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the classic Blucifer X Gorilla Glue #4 strains. This celebrity child boasts a super high THC level and melting effects that will lift you up and then slam you back down, gluing you to the couch or bed immediately. The high comes on fast and hard, slamming into your mind with a buzzing euphoria that immediately erases any negative or racing thoughts and leaves you feeling unfocused and hazy. You'll feel happy, grinning from ear to ear, in this state as you fade in and out of blissful awareness. A heavy body high creeps into your physical form while your mind lifts, slowly sinking you into the couch and leaving you fully immovable for hours and hours on end. Combined with its high 21-22% average THC level, these melting effects make Glucifer perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic stress, arthritis and depression. This bud has a classic spicy and peppery flavor with a super sour and pungent aroma to match. Glucifer buds have chunky oversized dark olive green nugs with purple undertones, long thin dark amber hairs and a coating of frosty purple-tinted crystal trichomes.

Glue 87.5%.name: Glue 87.5%
Glue 87.5%.description: Glue 87.5% is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the potent Gorilla Glue #4 X Glue 75% BX2 strains. A heavy-hitting indica with a stoney high, Glue 87.5% is the perfect choice for any patient who's after a soothing lift before they get to sleep. The high settles in a few minutes after your final toke, filling your mind with a happy and lifted sense that relieves stresses and bad moods instantly. A building body high comes next, creeping over you in warming waves of pure relaxation that lower you further and further into the couch before dropping you straight off into heavy couchlock and sedation. This combination will turn sleepy, so beware if you have things to do! Thanks to these effects and its high 19-22% average THC level, Glue 87.5% is often chosen to treat patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, cramps or muscle spasms, appetite loss or nausea and depression. This bud has a sweet and sour citrusy lemon flavor with a lightly spicy chocolatey exhale. The aroma is almost the same, with a sour lemony overtone accented by spicy peppery diesel and a touch of mocha coffee. Glue 87.5% buds have airy oversized grape-shaped emerald green nugs with dark leaves, long thin orange hairs and frosty milky white crystal trichomes.

GlueBall.name: GlueBall
GlueBall.description: GlueBall, also known as “Glueball” or “Glue Ball,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Original Glue X Snowball strains. This celebrity child brings on the hard-hitting effects of both of its parent strains, amplifying them to a whole new level of potency. You'll feel a strong and fast rush of cerebral effects almost as soon as you exhale, leaving you lifted and giggly with a heavy mental stone. As you fade further and further into unfocused bliss, your body will begin to follow suit, dropping you off the edge into a buzzing sense of sedated couch-lock. With these hard-hitting effects and its super high 25-26% average THC level, GlueBall is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, headaches or migraines, chronic stress and depression. This bud has a sweet and sour citrusy pine flavor that intensifies the more that you toke. The aroma is very similar, with a heavy pungent diesel overtone that's accented by sour citrus and woody pine. GlueBall buds have dense flat heart-shaped neon green nugs with bright amber undertones, vivid orange hairs and a coating of frosty amber crystal trichomes dripping with sweet sticky resin.

Glueberry OG.name: Glueberry OG
Glueberry OG.description: Glueberry OG is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Gorilla Glue X OG Kush X Blueberry strains. Known for its heavy effects and super delicious flavor, Glueberry OG will have you head over heels in no time at all. The Glueberry OG high starts in the head with a euphoric effect that fills the mind with a light sense of focus before dropping you into a strong forgetful and hazy state. You'll feel a strong physical high soon afterwards, dropping you off into a relaxed state that's immovable for hours on end without causing too much sleepiness or sedation. Thanks to these effects and its high 15-20% average THC level, Glueberry OG is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or PTSD, depression and migraines or headaches. This bud has a super sweet fruity blueberry flavor with a light touch of citrusy fruits upon exhale. The aroma is of earthy pungency with a spicy berry overtone that's accented by sharp citrus and rich woods. Glueberry OG buds have fluffy spade-shaped tapered bright neon green nugs with vivid orange haris and a coating of tiny frosty white crystal trichomes.

Glue Breath.name: Glue Breath
Glue Breath.description: Glue Breath is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (65% indica/35% sativa) created through crossing the classic Gorilla Glue #4 X OG Kush Breath B3 strains. If you love a great flavor and a super heady high, Glue Breath is totally made for you. This potent bud brings on the hard-hitting effects thanks to its super high 24-29% average THC level and relentless potency. The high comes on with a rush of cerebral effects that fill your mind with a hazy buzz that eases out any negative or racing thoughts and leaves you feeling totally out of it and blissful. As your mind expands, your body will start to fade away into a deeply relaxing state that quickly turns sleepy and sedative. Soon, you'll find yourself fading away into a giggly state that quickly turns to a deep and peaceful sleep. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Glue Breath is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, migraines or headaches, chronic fatigue, and depression. Glue Breath has a sweet and sugary herbal flavor with hints of fruits and berries on exhale. The aroma is very earthy and fruity with a spicy herbal overtone that's super sweet as the nugs are burned. This bud has spade-shaped forest green nugs with purple leaves, amber hairs, and coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Glue BX2.name: Glue BX2
Glue BX2.description: Glue BX2 is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the potent OG Glue X OG Glue strains. The perfect high-powered celebrity child, Glue BX2 packs a heavy high and high potency into each and every toke. The high starts with a slow build of effects, creeping into your brain with a lifted sense of happy calm and cerebral stimulation. This calm will leave you feeling blissful and unfocused, giggling at anything around you here and there. A soothing body high comes next, sneaking over your physical form and dropping you off into a super stoney state that will have you feeling sleepy and totally sedated before you realize what's happening. Thanks to these effects and its super high 26-29% average THC level and 0-2% CBD level, Glue BX2 is often chosen to treat those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, arthritis, chronic stress, depression and the effects of PMS. This bud has a sweet and spicy chocolatey mocha coffee flavor with a lightly earthy exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a spicy mocha coffee overtone accented by hints of tobacco and rich black pepper. Glue BX2 buds have oversized rounded dark olive green nugs with deep purple undertones, dark amber hairs and a coating of tiny, bright white crystal trichomes.

GlueChee.name: GlueChee
GlueChee.description: Gluechee is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Cheese X Original Glue (AKA – Gorilla Glue #4) strains. This celebrity child boasts a super potent high thanks to its potent 21-24% average THC level and a truly unique flavor, making it perfect for any hybrid lover who loves a little power behind their medicine. The high comes on with a light cerebral tingly effect that fills your mind with a pleasant fuzziness, easing away any negative or racing thoughts and replacing them with blank happiness. An influx of creativity and sociability accompanies this cerebral state, giving you the fuel that you need to carry on interesting conversations with anyone and everyone around you. With these effects and its high level of potency, Gluechee is said to be perfect for treating conditins such as chronic pain, migraines or headaches, chronic stress and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has a funky cheese and gas flavor with an earthy herbal overtone that turns pungent upon exhale. The aroma is of dank diesel and funky pungent cheese with an earthy overtone that is almost reminiscent of rot. Gluechee buds have oversized spade-shaped minty green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny bright white crystal trichomes.

Glue Fire OG.name: Glue Fire OG
Glue Fire OG.description: Glue Fire OG, also known as “Glue on Fire,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (75% indica/25% sativa) created through crossing the potent Gorilla Glue #4 X Fire OG strains. Known for its upbeat high and long-lasting effects, Glue Fire OG is perfect for any indica lover. The high starts with a slow creeping effect, sneaking into your mind a few minutes after your final toke. You'll feel a light lift with a boost of the spirits and a sense of tingly unfocused bliss sneak its way into your mind, dropping you into a happy and hazy state. A sense of numbness and stillness will work its way into your body as your mind settles, dropping you into an immovable state of comfortable couchlock. In combination with its high 15-23% average THC level and 1% CBD level, these effects make Glue Fire OG perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, mood swings or depression, chronic stress and Bipolar Disorder. This bud has a spicy and peppery earthy flavor that intensifies as you continue to toke. The aroma is of pungent diesel and spicy earth with a heavy black pepper overtone that lingers long after your final toke. Glue Fire OG buds have oversized fluffy and heavy bright neon green nugs with amber undertones, orange hairs and a coating of frosty thick golden amber crystal trichomes.

Glue Zauce.name: Glue Zauce
Glue Zauce.description: Glue Zauce is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Gorilla Glue # 4 X ZOZ BX Zkittlez strains. This celebrity child boasts a super high potency level with a delicious flavor and heady high that's reminiscent of its parent strains. That being said, get ready for one wild ride with this tasty bud. The high comes on fast and hard, rushing through your mind with a warming and expansive happiness that instantly freezes and deletes any negative or racing thoughts. Instead, you'll find your mind filled with a sticky sense of calm that makes focus difficult but leaves you feeling insanely blissful. A heavy physical high comes next, locking your body to the couch and helping you really to stretch out and relax. With these effects and its high 14-22% average THC level, Glue Zauce is often recommended for treating those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or PTSD, depression or mood swings and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet and sour fruity tropical citrus flavor with a light touch of chocolate and spicy diesel. The aroma is of chocolatey diesel with a gassy overtone that turns sour and citrusy the more that you toke. Glue Zauce buds have dense heart-shaped minty green nugs with thin orange hairs and a frosty coating of tiny golden-white crystal trichomes.

GM-UhOh.name: GM-UhOh
GM-UhOh.description: GM-UhOh is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Chemdawg X Girl Scout Cookies Forum Cut strains. The perfect balanced hybrid for any discerning patient, GM-UhOh packs a happy and soothing high with a delicious flavor that will leave you begging for more. Much like its parent strains, GM-UhOh has a sweet nutty cookie flavor with hints of fresh sage, spicy hash and rich black pepper. The aroma is very similar, with a spicy peppery overtone accented by earthy hash and a punch of nutty sage. The GM-UhOh high settles in a few minutes after your final exhale, lifting your mind into a state of happy calm and relaxation. You'll find yourself free of any mental aches or pains as your mind settles into a state of happy bliss. A soothing body high comes next, washing over you and locking you to the couch. A sharp pang of hunger will then make its move, leaving you reaching for anything in sight to snack on. Combined with its super high 32-36% average THC level, these effects make GM-UhOh a great choice for treating conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, PTSD, depression or mood swings and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has oversized and airy spade-shaped minty green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, milky amber crystal trichomes.

GMO Cake.name: GMO Cake
GMO Cake.description: GMO Cake is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the powerful GMO X Wedding Cake strains. The perfect balanced hybrid, GMO Cake is a must-try bud for any fan of its parent strains. The high hits both mind and body with GMO Cake, starting with a creeping build that slowly sneaks in before taking hold. You'll feel the effects in your mind first as your brain is filled with a lifted sense of happy calm. A touch of creativity and sociability accompanies this heady boost, helping you to carry on conversations with those around you. At the same time, a growing body high will sneak into your physical form, eventually locking you to the couch and leaving you feeling totally sedated. With these effects and its high 27-30% average THC level, GMO Cake is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as insomnia, chronic fatigue, depression, PSTD and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has a sweet and creamy vanilla cake flavor with hints of peppery sage and fresh flowers to it, too. The aroma is very similar, with a flowery and earthy overtone accented by herbal sage and sweet vanilla cake. GMO Cake buds have super sticky oversized conical emerald-green nugs with dark purple leaves, deep amber hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

GMO Crasher.name: GMO Crasher
GMO Crasher.description: GMO Crasher, also known as “GMO Crashers,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Wedding Crashers X GMO Cookies strains. If you're on the hunt for a super high-powered indica that will leave you flying for hours, GMO Crasher is perfect for you. This bud brings on a head-spinning high that will boost the spirits, leave you totally stoned and drop you off into a state of pure sedation before you know what's happening. The high starts with a slow build of effects, lifting your chin and filling you with a sense of lifted happiness that has you feeling like you have no cares in the world. You'll be giggly and out of touch with reality, laughing at anything and everything around you as your mind fades into a heavy cerebral stone. This can tun sleepy at times, so mind your dosage if you have thing to do. With these effects and its high 18-20% average THC level, GMO Crasher is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, headaches or migraines, chronic pain, depression and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and sugary vanilla coffee flavor with an earthy and pungent diesel aroma to match. This bud has fluffy dense heart-shaped forest green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, amber crystal trichomes.

Gnarsty.name: Gnarsty
Gnarsty.description: Gnarsty is a sativa dominant hybrid (80% sativa/20% indica) strain with unknown genetics due to breeder secrecy and controversy surrounding its origins. This dank bud boasts an insanely high THC level ranging from 18-26% on average and a myriad of both indica and sativa effects. Users describe the Gnarsty high as having an almost immediate onset of a very clear-headed and motivated euphoric head high. This high leaves you with complete mind pain relief and a sense of anti-nausea. Upon the come down from this head high, you'll feel a mild body buzz with no couch-lock or lethargy that leaves you completely pain-free and warmed through and through. Due to these potent primarily cerebral effects, Gnarsty is said to be an ideal strain for treating patients suffering from conditions such as nausea, mild to moderate cases of depression, fatigue, and chronic stress. Gnarsty buds have a very nutty brown sugar aroma with a taste of nutty brown sugar with a hint of sweet vanilla upon exhale. These nugs have small to medium-sized leafy airy popcorn-shaped dark olive green nugs with a spattering of translucent twisty hairs and rich blue undertones. These nugs are frosted with a fine layer of almost translucent trichomes and sweet sticky resin.

Gnu Glue.name: Gnu Glue
Gnu Glue.description: Gnu Glue is an indica dominant hybrid strain (63% indica/37% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other hybrid strains, although it is rumored to actually be a Gorilla Glue #4 X Platinum Kush Mints cross. Even with the debate about its heritage, Gnu Glue is often sought out for its immediate effects and high potency level that are great for helping you to settle down after a long and stressful day. The high will hit you between the eyes as soon as you exhale, instantly numbing the brain and leaving you feeling mentally calm and lifted, filled with hazy happiness. A calming sense comes next, washing over your body and helping you to settle down into a state of pure relaxation and ease. You'll find yourself becoming giggly and giddy in this state, laughing at anything around you for any reason at all. Combined with its super high 22-23% average THC level, these soothing effects make Gnu Glue a great choice for treating conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, PTSD, chronic pain and depression or mood swings. This bud has a sweet and fruity chocolatey mocha coffee flavor with hints of savory skunk and spicy menthol. The aroma takes a pungent turn with hints of savory skunk, spicy menthol and heavy dank that intensify the more that you toke. Gnu Glue buds have conical forest green nugs with amber undertones, thin amber hairs and matching crystal trichomes.

GOAT Milk.name: GOAT Milk
GOAT Milk.description: Goat Milk, also known as “G.O.A.T. Milk,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the tasty Cereal Milk X Georgia Pie #50 strains. Best known for its super tasty flavor and surprisingly energizing effects, Goat Milk is a great choice for any hybrid lover. This bud has a super sweet and creamy vanilla milk flavor accented by hints of fruity berries and fresh spicy cherries. The aroma is very similar, with a creamy vanilla milk overtone accented by spicy menthol, fresh fruity berries and a touch of gassy diesel. The Goat Milk high will smash you between the eyes almost as soon as you exhale, launching your brain into a state of lifted euphoria and mental energy. You'll be sociable and outgoing in this state, filled with the mental ability to chat with anyone around you, friend and stranger alike. A tingly and arousing body high rounds out the effects of this bud, relaxing your body without causing any sedation. Combined with its high 22-23% average THC level and 0-2% average CBD level, these effects make Goat Milk great for treating chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic stress, depression or mood swings and chronic fatigue. This bud has oversized flat heart-shaped forest green nugs with amber undertones, thick orange hairs and tiny, bright amber-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Goblin.name: Goblin
Goblin.description: Goblin, also known as “Goblin Kush,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the powerful SoCal Master Kush X Kingsblood strains. Although this bud is hard to come by, its relaxing and hazy effects are beloved by any user who tries it. The high hits you first with a euphoric lift that boosts your mood and leaves you insanely happy, although very hazy and spacey. As your head high builds into distant bliss, your body will succumb to a building buzzing effect that will leave you completely at ease although slightly hungry. A sleepy feeling comes next, washing over you and gently pulling you down into a peaceful napping state. These effects and its powerful THC level that bottoms out at 18% on average make Goblin ideal for treating conditions such as insomnia, chronic pain, nausea, muscle spasms, and appetite loss. This bud has a super pungent stench of rotting rapes and sweet earth and a flavor of sweet earth topped with lemongrass and fruity grapes with just a hint of nuttiness. Goblin buds have medium-sized forest green spade-shaped nugs with bright orange hairs and a thick frosty blanket of amber colored crystal trichomes.

God's AK-47.name: God's AK-47
God's AK-47.description: God's AK-47 is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through a powerful cross of the classic God Bud X AK-47 strains. Hard-hitting from start to finish, this bud is perfect for getting to sleep after a stressful day and doing it quickly. That being said, God's AK-47 does have a pretty high level of potency, hitting about 16-20% with its THC level, and you should definitely mind your dosage if you have any plans for the evening. It starts with a subtle build, sneaking into your mind with a lifted effect, pushing your spirits higher and higher while filling you with a sense of warming calm and relaxation. This will soon spread its soothing tendrils throughout the rest of your body, locking you to the couch and leaving you hopelessly sedated, often falling asleep immediately. These heavy-hitting effects give God's AK-47 an edge in treating experienced patients suffering from chronic pain, insomnia, depression, chronic stress and appetite loss or nausea. God's AK-47 has a sweet yet spicy chocolate woody flavor with a heavily pungent and skunky aroma to match. God's AK-47 buds have oversized pepper-shaped forest green nugs with thin amber hairs and tiny crystal trichomes.

God'S Blue Cough.name: God'S Blue Cough
God'S Blue Cough.description: God's Blue Cough is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious God Bud X Blueberry X Strawberry Cough strains. Like the name suggests, this bud has a heavenly flavor profile that will leave you coughing after just one tasty toke. The flavor is sweet with a rich blueberry earth taste that fills the lungs with delicious fruitiness. The aroma is of pungent herbal earth with a notable hit of blueberries and strawberries as the nugs are broken apart and burned. If you love the taste, you'll love the high even more. God's Blue Cough starts with a happy lifted feeling that is slightly tingly, filling your head with calming, unfocused feelings and erasing any negative or racing thoughts. A deep sense of relaxation will wash over you, leaving you completely at ease without a care in the world. With these effects and its super high 29-30% average THC level, God's Blue Cough is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as depression, chronic stress or anxiety, pain, and fatigue. This bud has heart-shaped forest green nugs with furry orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of sandy amber trichomes.

God'S Green Crack.name: God'S Green Crack
God'S Green Crack.description: God's Green Crack is a super rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (55% indica/45% sativa) created through crossing the infamous God's Gift X Green Crack strains. This powerhouse packs a super heavy high that's perfect for relaxing days where you want a little energy to get up and moving but still want to kick back and relax. You'll feel a light build at the onset of the high, infusing you with a tingly effect in the back of your head before spreading through the rest of your mind with a sense of focused energy. Soon after, your physical form will succumb to the same tingly feelings, leaving you totally relaxed in both mind and body. Thanks to these effects and its high 22-25% average THC level, God's Green Crack is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, ADD or ADHD, migraines, and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has oversized fluffy forest green spade-shaped nugs with purple leaves, bright orange hairs, and a coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes. As you break apart each tiny little nugget, aromas of tangy fruits and rich tropical mango are released. The aroma is very similar, although with a spicy earthy effect as the nugs are burned.

God's Green Gift.name: God's Green Gift
God's Green Gift.description: God's Green Gift, aka simply as "God's Gift," is an indica-dominant hybrid (10:90 sativa/indica ratio) with THC levels that can top 22%. That makes this one of the strongest choices available for medical relief. CBD levels are negligible, so this isn't a good choice for patients suffering from epilepsy or other conditions that respond to CBD marijuana. The indica-fueled body high is intensely lazy, with a shot of euphoria and a strong mood boost. Sleepiness is also common, making this a great product for treating insomnia. Other medical uses include stress and anxiety, chronic pain, and depression. Anyone looking for deep relaxation should give this effective strain a try. Side effects are possible, as always, especially dry mouth and bloodshot eyes. Other adverse effects are more limited, including dizziness and paranoia. God's Green Gift has a strong pungent odor and a sweet earthy flavor. The dense buds have a vibrant purple hue with a dense layer of trichomes. This relatively recent strain was born in California in 2005. It's most common on the West Coast and in Michigan, though it can be found in other places.

God's Vagina.name: God's Vagina
God's Vagina.description: God's Vagina is an indica dominant hybrid strain (75% indica/25% sativa) created through crossing the potent Dream X Hellfire OG strains. The perfect bud to help you take control of negative or racing thoughts before you get to bed, God's Vagina packs a punch thanks to an insanely high 28-32% average THC level. That being said, patient beware - God's Vagina can easily overwhelm you if you're not careful with your dosage. The high comes on with a creeping effect, filling your cerebral state with a heavy and expansive euphoria that's packed full of creativity and a giggly overtone. A heavy body high comes next, seeping into your body and locking you to the couch almost immediately, filling you with a sense that you're being pulled down into pure sedation. These heavy effects make God's Vagina the perfect choice for treating chronic stress, mood swings or depression, chronic pain, Bipolar Disorder and insomnia. God's Vagina has a sweet and fruity flavor with a lightly spicy hashy exhale. The aroma is very similar, although with hints of peppery earth to it, too. God's Vagina buds have grape-shaped super dense dark olive green nugs with dark amber hairs and a coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Godbud.name: Godbud
Godbud.description: Godbud, also known as “God Bud,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic Hawaii X Purple Skunk strains. With its heavenly flavor and full-bodied effects, just one taste of Godbud and you'll be hooked for life. Godbud has a unique sweet chocolate flavor with hints of mild spices and sweet earth. The aroma is much like a mocha coffee with hints of sweet mild earth and herbs. Godbud buds have totally oversized bright round piecey nugs with bright fiery orange hairs and a coating of chunky golden colored crystal trichomes. The Godbud high is definitely one for the ages, with a euphoric overtone that will leave you feeling happy for hours on end. The high starts with a happy lift that leaves you feeling completely at ease and utterly relaxed. This calm state will slowly spread throughout the rest of your body in warming waves, leaving you feeling sedated and sleepy. With these effects and its powerful 14-22% average THC level, Godbud is the perfect choice for treating patients who are suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression, muscle spasms, chronic stress, and insomnia.

Godbud x Shiskaberry.name: Godbud x Shiskaberry
Godbud x Shiskaberry.description: Godbud X Shiskaberry is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain with an insanely high THC level that bottoms out at about 20% on average. With Godbud X Shiskaberry, get ready for an insanely delicious flavor – this bud packs sweet berries and rich spices with a fruity earthy overtone into each skunky little nugget. The aroma isn’t half bad either, with a chocolate earthy overtone that becomes slightly spicy and pungent as the nugs are burned. The Godbud X Shiskaberry is just as soothing and delicious as the flavor, with lifted effects that are perfect for social situations when you need a little boost to get the conversation flowing. You’ll feel the cerebral effects first as the high slowly starts to take hold, creeping into your mind with deep relaxation and a sense of happiness. You’ll soon find yourself giggly and more outgoing, engaging in conversation with those around you with ease. Thanks to these effects and its high 20% + average THC level, Godbud X Shiskaberry is often chosen to treat patients suffering from conditions such as chornic anxiety or stress, depression, headaches or migraines, and nausea. This bud has tiny round minty green nugs with lots of light amber hairs and a frosty thick coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

GodCrack.name: GodCrack
GodCrack.description: Green Crack and God Bud were crossed to create GodCrack, a potent near-even hybrid with a sativa/indica ratio of roughly 45:55. There isn't much available information about this well-liked but rare medical choice. The nugs are reportedly quite large, with a layer of trichomes, but beyond that little is known about its appearance, aroma, or flavor. Based on GodCrack's parentage, though, users can expect a sweet, fruity taste and a pungent, earthy smell. This strain isn't terribly popular, but it's also new, and it may just be a matter of time before it catches on. It's already known for its potency, though exact THC levels are hard to come by. But it definitely isn't known for its CBD contents, so it probably shouldn't be used as the sole treatment for seizures or other disorders that respond to CBD. Instead, use GodCrack to treat anxiety, insomnia, inflammation, and lack of appetite; this strain produces a powerful case of the munchies. The high, which leans slightly toward the indica side, is deeply relaxing, both mentally and physically, yet isn't overpowering for most patients. GodCrack is sold in California, but elsewhere it's still a rarity.

Goddess Kush.name: Goddess Kush
Goddess Kush.description: Goddess Kush is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Blueberry X OG Kush strains. This delicious combination yields a super potent bud with an addictive flavor that will leave you practically begging for one more taste. Goddess Kush buds have a super sweet berry citrus flavor with hints of rich spicy pine upon each beautiful exhale. The aroma is very earthy and citrusy with a spicy berry overtone that turns slightly herbal as the nugs are broken apart and burned. The Goddess Kush high settles in mere moments after your first exhale, working its way into your brain with a light lifted effect that infuses you with a sense of euphoria without causing any sort of anxiety or paranoia. As your mood lifts higher and higher, your body will start to settle into a deeply relaxing state that lulls you into a light couch-lock with a bit of physical sedation that won't spread to your brain. With these long-lasting effects and its high 23-26% average THC level, Goddess Kush is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, headaches or migraines, chronic fatigue, depression, mood swings, and chronic stress. This bud has oversized rounded dusty green nugs with rich amber hairs and a coating of tiny sandy amber crystal trichomes.

Godfather OG Kush.name: Godfather OG Kush
Godfather OG Kush.description: Godfather OG Kush, also known as “Godfather OG,” is often called the “Don” of all of the OG strains due to its powerful effects and powerful THC level of 22-28% on average. This bud is created through a cross of the potent Granddaddy Purple X OG Kush strains for a myriad of powerful parents. The Godfather OG Kush high is not for beginners – use with caution! This high hits you hard with a powerful creeping effect that suddenly leaves you completely couch-locked and helplessly sedated within 20 minutes of toking. You'll be trapped within your own mind as you soar through deep introspection. Nonetheless, you'll be happy and euphoric in this state, although unable to move for anything other than a snack or five. These effects coupled with its powerful THC level make Godfather OG Kush ideal for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, muscle spasms, chronic pain, tremors, appetite loss, and insomnia. This bud has a pungent earthy flavor with hints of skunky pine and an aroma of pungent earthy pine topped with herbal spiciness and a hint of pepper. Godfather OG Kush buds have small rounded popcorn-shaped light minty green nugs with bright orange and red hairs and a fine coating of sweet sticky resin.

Godhead.name: Godhead
Godhead.description: Godhead, also known as “God Head,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Blockhead X 88 G-13 Hash Plant strains. Potent and stimulating with long-lasting effects, Godhead is the perfect balanced hybrid for any discerning patient. The high hits you pretty immediately, knocking into the side of your forehead and back of your neck with a tingly lifted sense. You'll be happy and giggly in this state, pretty out of touch with reality. This tingle will soon spread its warming tendrils throughout your entire body, leaving you feeling super relaxed and at ease without too much couchlock. Thanks to these effects and its super high 22-24% average THC level and 0-2% average CBD level, Godhead is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including chronic stress or anxiety, PTSD, ADD or ADHD, Parkinson's Disease and Alzheimer's Disease. This bud has a super sour lemony citrus flavor with a fruity strawberry exhale. The aroma is a blend of fresh fruity berries accented by sour lemony citrus and nutty earthiness. Godhead buds have oversized and heavy dense spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with purple undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of chunky, golden-white crystal trichomes.

Godzilla Grape.name: Godzilla Grape
Godzilla Grape.description: Godzilla Grape is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous GOD X L.U.I. strains. Named for its insanely oversized buds and super delicious flavor, Godzilla Grape is perfect for any indica lover. This baby has super heavy oversized forest green heart-shaped nugs with rich purple undertones, brown hairs and a coating of frosty white purple-tinted crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of spicy grapes and fruits are released, all wrapped up with an earthy diesel overtone. The flavor is of spicy grapes and fruits with a lightly herbal exhale. The Godzilla Grape high is just as addictive as the flavor, with relaxing effects that hit your body with a high level of potency. The onset is sort of creeping in nature, with a light tingle felt in the spine and back of the neck that slowly expands throughout the rest of your body until you are totally physically sedated and couch-locked. A building euphoria and sense of creativity accompanies this physical high, lifting the spirits and keeping you totally relaxed from start to finish. With these effects and its high 15-18% average THC level, Godzilla Grape is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such has chronic pain, cancer or chemotherapy, chronic stress or anxiety and insomnia.

God\u2019s Treat.name: God’s Treat
God\u2019s Treat.description: God's Treat is created by marrying God Bud with Dutch Treat. This results in an Indica dominant strain that contain 75 percent Indica and about 25 percent Sativa. The plant has tall cone shaped flowers that are covered with thin leaves that are a prominent feature in Sativa strains. The leaves are green with golden and yellow leaves and crystals. It has a flowering period of about seven weeks. The strain provides a very mellow yet uplifting effect that continues to linger on in your body for quite some time. It has an earthy aroma with strong hints of candy and floral scents. Its flavor is quite the same and feels quite earthy yet sweet. Gods Treat has a high THC level of up to 22 percent. It produces a heavy buzz that has calming effects on your system. It makes you quite energized and euphoric when you smoke it. Gods Treat is best used for treating anxiety and stress as it can alleviate the symptoms of anxiety from your body conveniently. It is also used for relaxing muscle spasms and providing relief from tremors. It tends to dry your eyes and mouth at times. Other than that, it is safe to use.

Goji Berry.name: Goji Berry
Goji Berry.description: Goji Berry is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through as a phenotype of the delicious Goji OG strain. Best known for its super energizing high and delicious flavor, Goji Berry is a great choice for any wake-and-bake. The effects hit you as soon as you exhale, filling your brain with a lifted sense of energy that is near electrifying. You'll feel insanely creative and happy, ready to get to work on your to-do list or chat with anyone around you about anything at all. A substantial boost in motivation accompanies this lift, helping keep you in this energizing state as long as you need. Thanks to these effects and its super high 26-28% average THC level, Goji Berry is often chosen to treat those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, depression, headaches or migraines and chronic fatigue. This bud has a classic fruity blueberry cherry flavor with hints of fresh tangy citrus, too. The aroma is very similar, with a sour citrusy overtone accented by fresh fruity berries and a hint of earthiness. Goji Berry buds have fat small heart-shaped blue-green nugs with thick yellow-orange hairs and a coating of chunky white crystal trichomes.

Goji DC.name: Goji DC
Goji DC.description: Goji DC is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through a cross of the highly medicinal Goji X ACDC strains. The first place winner of the High Times' Cannabis Cup in 2015 for best CBD concentrate, Goji DC packs a super relaxing high that's totally full of CBD, making it perfect for taking on a wide variety of conditions with ease. That being said, the Goji DC high is pretty mellow in nature, with tingly and relaxing effects that will have you kicking back without causing paranoia or too much sedation. A mental and physical calm will wash over you a few minutes after your first toke, washing over your entire being and keeping you suspended in pure bliss for hours on end. In combination with its super high 15-20% average CBD level and 5-10% THC level, these effects give Goji DC an edge in treating conditions such as inflammation, chronic pain, epilepsy, cramps or muscle spasms and insomnia. Goji DC has a mellow woody spicy flavor with a flowery overtone that is pleasant and light. The aroma is of earthy florals and rich woody pine, turning slightly spicy as the nugs are burned. Goji DC buds have airy piecey spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with dark olive green leaves, yellow-orange hairs and a coating of tiny white crystal trichomes.

goji gorilla.name: goji gorilla
goji gorilla.description: Goji Gorilla, also known more commonly as “Goji Glue,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the powerful Goji OG X Gorilla Glue #4 strains. This bud is highly sought after for its flawless blend of its parents' effects and its addictive flavor. Goji Gorilla has a sweet and creamy flavor of buttery rum with hints of pineapple and citrus flavored candy. The aroma is of creamy butter with a tropical overtone and hints of smooth sickly sweet caramel as the nugs are burned. Goji Gorilla buds have leafy grape-shaped light minty green nugs with deep purple undertones, light lavender colored hairs and a frosty coating of tiny crystal white trichomes. The Goji Gorilla high is that of a classic indica with both mind and body effects that are relaxing and sedating as a whole. The high starts with a mood boost that lifts your spirits and leaves you euphoric but very hazy and introspective. As this high builds, a slightly buzzy effect will start in the back of your head and spread throughout the rest of your body in warming waves. As the buzz spreads through your limbs, you'll start to become very couch-locked and sedated before falling into a deep sleep. Because of these effects and its 20-24% average THC level, Goji Gorilla is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, nausea, appetite loss, and chronic pain.

Goji Gushers.name: Goji Gushers
Goji Gushers.description: Goji Gushers is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Goji OG X Gushers strains. With parents like these, you know that you're in for one delicious toke with this bud. Goji Gushers packs a mouthwatering sweet fruity berry flavor with hints of sour citrus, too. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy citrusy overtone that intensifies with sour spices the more that you toke. The Goji Gushers high is just as bright as the flavor, with effects that hit both mind and body, launching you into a giddy state of euphoria that is totally pain-free in nature. You'll feel motivated and creative with a giddy sense that has you fading in and out of focus, falling victim to fits of giggles before you even realize what's happening. A tingly body high accompanies this heady lift, relaxing your aching muscles without causing any sedation in the slightest. Thanks to these effects and its high 19-20% average THC level, Goji Gushers is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, stress, depression, chronic fatigue and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has thick rounded fluffy minty green nugs with dark olive undertones, long thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny white crystal trichomes.

Goji OG.name: Goji OG
Goji OG.description: Named after the bright red Himalayan berry, the Goji OG stain is also a sativa dominant strain with 80:20 sativa/indica ratios. It is a hybrid strain created by crossing the Snow Lotus strain with the Nepali OG. This strain provides a wicked high due to its astonishingly high THC level of 22% and 0.5% CBD content. This alone should be enough to deter the novice smoker from this strain. It provides a high unlike any other. This strain can be used for medicinal purposed which include, stress relief, anger control, bipolar disorder, nervous conditions, Alzheimer, depression, Parkinson's disease, chronic pain, cancer, insomnia, and anorexia. Although this strain is a hybrid cross, it has almost all the properties of an OG. Some even call it the perfect package. As the name suggests, the strain has a fruity, sweet flavor to it. Slight earthy as well as black cherry and licorice undertones can be felt. The appearance of this strain is similar to other OG strains. It has a mossy and flaky texture to it. Smoky white with hints of brown and orange can be seen.

Goji Raz.name: Goji Raz
Goji Raz.description: Goji Raz, also known as “Goji Razz,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Goji OG X another unknown hybrid strain. If you're on the hunt for an amazing fruity flavor and a soaring high that will keep your mind spinning, you've found it with Goji Raz. Like its name suggests, Goji Raz has a sweet and fruity berry flavor with hints of fresh blueberries, ripe cherries and sugary strawberries galore. The aroma is very similar, like a bouquet of freshly picked berries coated with fresh earth and accented by fragrant flowers. The Goji Raz high will settle in a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your brain with an uplifted feeling that boosts your mood and activates your senses. You'll feel creative and sociable, ready to chat with anyone and everyone around you about anything at all. A light giggly sense comes next, leaving you falling into fits of laughter at just about anything. Thanks to these effects and its moderate 14-15% average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, Goji Raz is often chosen to treat conditions such as insomnia, chronic stress or PTSD, depression and chronic pain. This bud has dense and oversized conical olive green nugs with deep purple undertones, pinkish red hairs and a coating of tiny, pink-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Goji Tang.name: Goji Tang
Goji Tang.description: Goji Tang is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the potent Pootie Tang X Goji Berry strains. Perfect for anyone who loves a great eye-opening flavor alongside their high, Goji Tang is super sweet from start to finish. The flavor is very sour with a spicy pungent overtone that turns more and more tangy as you continue to toke. The aroma is very earthy and sweet with a fruity berry overtone that's accented by spicy citrus and rich earthy herbs. The Goji Berry high is just as breathtaking as the flavor, with frenzied effects that are best suited for those who do not suffer from anxiety or paranoia. You'll feel lifted and slightly out of focus, with increased sociability and creativity that leaves you joining in on conversation easily. Thanks to these effects and its high 20-23% average THC level and 1-5% CBD level, Goji Tang is said to be the perfect medicinal strain for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, depression, chronic fatigue, migraines or headaches, and nausea. This bud has oversized piecey bright neon green nugs with pinkish undertones, clear amber-tinted hairs, and a coating of sparkling clear crystal trichomes.

Gold Bali.name: Gold Bali
Gold Bali.description: Gold Bali, also known as “Bali Gold,” is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) or slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the classic Blue Dream X Acapulco Gold strains. Named for the Gold Bali Kratom plant, this strain is best-known for its gorgeous appearance and well-balanced effects. Gold Bali buds have fluffy oversized heart-shaped bright neon green nugs with thin orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of tiny clear golden crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of peppery earth and spicy blueberries are released, intensifying in sweetness as the nugs are broken apart and burned away. The Gold Bali is just as delicious as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that will have you feeling lifted for hours on end. You'll feel a growing sense of euphoria expand through your entire body, lifting your spirits and filling you with a touch of creative energy and motivation. This is accompanied by a relaxing body high that keeps you grounded as your mind soars higher and higher. With these effects and its high 19-23% average THC level, Gold Bali is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, inflammation, chronic stress and appetite loss or nausea.

Gold Coast Candy OG.name: Gold Coast Candy OG
Gold Coast Candy OG.description: Gold Coast Candy OG may be an indica strain but it is not to be taken lightly. Even though it is potent, it can be used by individuals who are new to smoking cannabis. The strain has a 17% THC content and it may not appeal to most experienced cannabis users but it should not be underestimated in any way. The buds are ordinary and are dense and sticky with gold hues amidst the greens. As for the taste and smell, it is fruity and sweet. The sweet indica strain is known for its mellow effects. It is the perfect strain to medicate with if you do not plan to leave the house. The strain and its effects tend to last longer and will leave you with an exceptional high that is calming to say the least. Apart from that, a hit or two is more than enough to last you a solid hour without breaking a sweat. However, most experienced will need a bit more before they can actually feel the full force of the strain. That being said, it is important to keep in mind that the numbing effects of the strain are perfect for individuals who are suffering from pains, migraines and even nausea.

Golden Berry.name: Golden Berry
Golden Berry.description: Golden Berry, also known as “Goldenberry,” is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the classic Kushberry X Jew Gold Cut strains. Named for its gorgeous appearance and mouthwatering flavor, Golden Berry is the perfect bud for any hybrid lover who appreciates a slight sativa lean in their medicine. This bud has super fluffy dark olive green nugs with deep golden amber undertones, vivid red-orange hairs and a coating of frosty chunky white crystal trichomes with an almost golden tint to them. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of fresh spicy berries and sweet citrus are released with a punch of nose-tickling mint, too. The flavor is of sweet fruity berries and slightly sour citrus that has a notable undertone of mint. The Golden Berry high is one that will get your eyes open and your body off the couch, with energizing and stimulating effects that are perfect for a lazy day. You’ll feel uplifted with a cerebral stimulation that gets your mind focused and clear, ready to tackle any creative task. A lightly relaxing body high accompanies this lift, easing aching muscles without dampening your energy level. Combined with its high 14-20% average THC level, these effects make Golden Berry perfect for treating chronic pain, nausea or appetite loss, chronic stress, depression and chronic fatigue.

Golden Boy.name: Golden Boy
Golden Boy.description: Golden Boy is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through an unknown combination of indica strains. This one-of-a-kind bud is totally perfect for those days when you need to calm down but just can’t get there. It starts with a subtle build in the back of the head, filling your mind with a slowly expanding euphoria and pure blissful happiness. A sense of creativity accompanies this heady state, boosting your mood and easing away any negative thoughts. A lightly relaxing body high comes next, calming your physical form as your mental state reaches a new level of wholesome tranquility and ease. These effects aren’t too sedative and won’t cause you to fall asleep or become couch-locked in the slightest. Thanks to these effects and its moderate 10-15% average THC level, Golden Boy is said to be perfect for treating a variety of conditions, including chronic pain, appetite loss or nausea, depression and cramps. Golden Boy has a spicy fruity flavor with a lightly herbal woody exhale. The aroma is of earthy herbs and spices with a sweet fruity overtone that lingers. Golden Boy buds have fluffy airy bright neon green nugs with rich golden amber undertones, matching hairs and a coating of clear crystal trichomes.

Golden Glue.name: Golden Glue
Golden Glue.description: Golden Glue is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Gorilla Glue #1 X Golden Ticket strains. This heavy sativa is the perfect bud for an afternoon when you need to get up and moving before you finally get to sleep. The high starts with an almost immediate onset, slamming into your mind with a high-flying energizing effect. You'll feel insanely euphoric with a sharp increase in focus and motivation. Your senses will sharpen as your mind clears, letting you easily concentrate on any task at hand. This heady state will soon take a hazy turn, relaxing the mind and leaving you falling in and out of sleepy sedation. Combined with its super high 20-29% average THC level, these heady effects make Golden Glue ideal for treating experienced patients suffering from chronic stress or anxiety, appetite loss or nausea, insomnia and depression. This bud has a classic spicy yet sour lemony citrus flavor that tingles on the tongue. The aroma is of earthy herbs with a touch of light spicy pine and fresh sour citrus galore. Golden Glue buds have fat fluffy dark olive green nugs with thin amber hairs and a coating of tiny bright white crystal trichomes.

Golden Jamaican Kush.name: Golden Jamaican Kush
Golden Jamaican Kush.description: Being an indica dominant hybrid strain, Golden Jamaican Kush has a 70:30 indica/sativa ratio. It has an acceptable 20% THC content and is produced by crossing Blueberry Kush and Jamaican Gold. As for the buds, they are golden in color with hues of purple. Additionally, they mostly have a good amount of crystal coverage as well. The smell is unique and offers an amazing blend of spice and fruity scents with kush undertones. The first hit will taste like kush but after some time you will notice a delicious blueberry taste. Two to three hits are more than enough before that smooth and easy feeling sets in. However, a few more hits after that will knock you out if you are not careful. But then again, you will feel relaxed due to the body numbing effects of the strain. On the other hand, experienced users mostly feel energized by its effects and may feel creative at the same time. TV will never seem more appealing and music will not sound as good as it will after smoking Golden Jamaican Kush. That being said, it is often recommended for patients suffering from medical conditions like anorexia, depression, anxiety, muscle spasms and chronic aches as well.

Golden Lemons.name: Golden Lemons
Golden Lemons.description: Golden Lemons is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid (60% indica/40% sativa) strain created through crossing the delicious Kosher Kush X Lemon Skunk strains. Like its name suggests, Golden Lemons has a sweet citrusy flavor and a gorgeous golden appearance. This bud has a sweet herbal lemon flavor with a dank citrusy overtone and a fresh pungent aroma to match that carries a bouquet of woodiness as the nugs are burned. Golden Lemons buds have flat oversized bright neon green nugs with sparse orange hairs and a coating of tiny golden amber crystal trichomes that sparkle in the light. The Golden Lemons high is just as cerebrally bright and eye-opening as its flavor, with a heavy body high to keep you anchored to the world below. You'll feel an immediate hit between the eyes of lifted euphoria that infuses you with a slight touch of creativity and energy. As this effect grows, your body will start to succumb to a creeping sedative body high that washes over you in warming waves of building strength. These effects give Golden Lemons an edge in treating conditions such as depression, chronic stress, muscle spasms, migraines or headaches, and chronic pain.

Golden Monkey.name: Golden Monkey
Golden Monkey.description: Golden Monkey is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Animal Cookies X Masters'N Crime strains. Named for its gorgeous appearance and playful high, Golden Monkey is perfect for any hybrid lover. This bud has fat spade-shaped forest green nugs with golden amber undertones, vivid orange hairs and a coating of minty green crystal trichomes that have hints of gold to them, too. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of sweet skunk and pungent diesel are released, intensifying in spiciness as the nugs are burned away. The flavor is on the lighter side, with a sweet nutty cookie taste that's accented by a light touch of savory diesel. The Golden Monkey high isn't quite as eye-opening as the flavor, with soothing and relaxing effects that are great for when you feel like hanging out with friends but don't have much of anything to do. You'll feel lifted yet relaxed with a sense of euphoria and an increase in sociability that has you carrying on easy conversations with those around you. Combined with its high 21-23% average THC level, these effects make Golden Monkey perfect for treating conditions such as chronic stress or PTSD, depression or mood swings, chronic anxiety and appetite loss or nausea.

Golden Papaya.name: Golden Papaya
Golden Papaya.description: Golden Papaya is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the potent Kosher Kush X Papaya strains. Named for its delicious flavor and gorgeous appearance, Golden Papaya is the perfect choice for any hybrid lover who appreciates a slight sativa lean in their medicine. This bud has beautiful, fluffy oversized popcorn-shaped olive treen nugs with beautiful golden undertones, thin yellow-orange hairs and a coating of tiny, frosty golden crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sparkling little nugget, aromas of sweet tropical fruits and fresh creamy mangoes are released, accented by a punch of spicy diesel. The flavor is sweeter, with a sugary mango overtone accented by a punch of sour tropical citrus and a touch of earthiness. The Golden Papaya high will hit you almost as soon as you exhale, beginning as a tingle behind the eyes and in the forehead. You'll feel stimulated and euphonic in this state, mentally free of any aches or pains. This tingle will soon work its way throughout the rest of your body, leaving you feeling fully relaxed from head to toe and pretty sleepy at times. With these effects and its high 18-19% average THC level, Golden Papaya is often chosen to treat migraines or headaches, chronic stress or anxiety, inflammation and cramps or muscle spasms.

Golden Pineapple.name: Golden Pineapple
Golden Pineapple.description: The golden pineapple sounds like a strain that is exotic and helps you battle a lot of things that you may be going through due to one reason or the other. The Golden Pineapple proves to be very effective both in the short run and in the long run regardless of the problem you may be facing. The Golden Pineapple is a very popular hybrid that is considered to be a cross between the Pineapple Kush and the Golden Goat. This particular strain naturally has a fruity and a very tropical flavor and aroma which are similar to that of a sour pineapple. Apart from its great taste, this strain is quite effective at battling stress, anxiety and depression. This particular strain also provides you with a good amount of energy, allowing you to seize the day. This is a good strain to smoke especially when you have a long and hard day in front of you. However, the only thing to look out for is the fact that if you take it in larger doses you can find it hard to focus on whatever you will be doing that day.

Golden Spruce.name: Golden Spruce
Golden Spruce.description: Golden Spruce is a sativa dominant hybrid strain of unknown origins due to a high level of breeder secrecy about its heritage. Even with the lack of information about its heritage, Golden Spruce is highly sought after by breeders and patients alike for its gorgeous appearance and deliciously unique flavor. Golden Spruce buds have dense and super fat spade-shaped minty green nugs with surprisingly purple undertones, vivid orange hairs and a coating of frosty amber-tinted white crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sparkling little nugget, aromas of fresh mint and woody pine are released with a strange accent of what can only be described as soap. The flavor is very similar, with a sweet minty pine soap taste that isn’t too overwhelming. The Golden Spruce high is perfect for a wake-and-bake when you don’t have much of anything to get done. Yes, you’ll feel energized, but at the same time you’ll be relaxed and unfocused, happy to just sit back and watch the world go by. You’ll feel a warming euphoria throughout the duration of the high, keeping your spirits lifted and you feeling on top of the world. With these effects and its high 21-22% average THC level, Golden Spruce is often chosen to treat chronic fatigue, depression or mood swings, chronic pain and migraines or headaches.

Golden Star.name: Golden Star
Golden Star.description: Golden Star, also known as “GoldStar,” is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Sensi Star with the beautiful Malawi Gold strain. The result is an insanely gorgeous bud with a bright spicy flavor and super heady effects. Golden Star buds have small round dark olive green nugs spattered with bright orange hairs and coated in a thick frosty layer of tiny golden crystal trichomes. As you break apart each little nugget, sweet floral earthy spices are released accented by a sharp kick of mint as the nugs are burned. Each inhale brings on fresh mint and florals with a spicy fruity effect that lingers long after exhale. The Golden Star high is one of full-bodied energy and motivation that's perfect for days when you need a little extra oomph to get going. The high starts with a heady electric jolt that blasts through your body with an almost frantic sense of energy that launches you into stoney focus. As your head grows, your body will fade into a warming tingly body high that won't weigh you down or cause any sort of sedation. In combination with its moderate 14%+ average THC level, Golden Star is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as mood swings, chronic fatigue, bipolarity, and chronic stress.

Golden Stormz.name: Golden Stormz
Golden Stormz.description: Golden Stormz is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the iconic '91 Afghan X 24K strains. Names for its super gorgeous appearance, Golden Stormz packs a super heavy high and long-lasting effects that are perfect for anyone who appreciates a classic indica. This bud has spade-shaped forest green nugs with golden amber undertones, thin orange hairs, and a coating of sparkling tiny amber crystal trichomes that look almost golden in the right light. As each sticky little nugget is pulled apart, aromas of sour spicy citrus and peppery earth are released. The flavor is very much the same, although with a touch of sweet orange to it at times. The Golden Stormz high isn't quite as eye-opening as the flavor, with effects that are best suited for a lazy night in when you don't have much of anything to get done. The high starts with a lifted effect that begins with a tingle in the back of the mind before taking hold of your entire cerebral state. Soon, this buzz will begin to spread throughout the rest of your body, leaving you feeling totally relaxed and at ease as you settle deeper and deeper into a heavy couch-lock. This quickly turns sleepy, leaving you dozing off and on before you finally fall asleep. Thanks to these effects and its high 20-24% average THC level, Golden Stormz is perfect for treating chronic pain, depression, chronic fatigue, nausea, and chronic stress or anxiety.

Golden Strawberries.name: Golden Strawberries
Golden Strawberries.description: Golden Strawberries is a rare slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through crossing the classic Golden Goat X Strawberry strains. This bud brings it all in the appearance department – each fluffy neon green nug is totally wrapped with long thin bright red hairs and is completely coated in a thick frosty layer of golden white crystal trichomes. As you break apart each sticky little nugget, fresh aromas of sweet strawberries and tropical fruits are released with just a hint of earthy herbs and spices as the nugs are burned. The flavor is very sweet and fruity, with a strawberry overtone accented by spicy tropical fruits and fresh earth. The Golden Strawberries high is just as delicious as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that will leave you totally lifted for hours and hours on end. The high starts with a rush of cerebral effects that launch into your mind with a slightly arousing tingle. This buzzing quickly spreads throughout the rest of your body, leaving you relaxed and totally at ease without affecting your energy level or causing sedation. Soon, you'll feel yourself slipping away into never-ending cases of the giggles, laughing at anything and everything around you for no reason. In combination with its high 18-26% average THC level, these effects give Golden Strawberries an edge in treating chronic stress, depression, mood swings, migraines or headaches, and nausea or appetite loss.

Golden Tree Plush Berry.name: Golden Tree Plush Berry
Golden Tree Plush Berry.description: Golden Tree Plushberry is a high THC version of the classic Plushberry strain, an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain that descends from Black Cherry Soda X Space Queen. With a THC level that ranges from 22-26% on average and powerful full body effects, it's easy to see why Golden Tree Plushberry is a consumer favorite. The high hits you fast and hard with a punch of giddy energy that can be felt in your forehead and the back of your neck. This energy quickly subsides into a hazy introspection that leaves you feeling happy and content with a deep sense of relaxation. A buzzing body high will build alongside your head high, pulling you down into a sense of complete calm that doesn't cause couch-lock or weigh you down. As the high continues, a sleepy feeling will start to overcome you that often leaves users dozing off into a deep sleep for hours on end. These effects make Golden Tree Plushberry perfect for treating chronic anxiety or stress, inflammation, mood swings, and chronic headaches or migraines. This bud has super colorful and dense nugs that are a myriad of purples, pinks, oranges, and blues. Each nug is dusted with clear crystal trichomes and has a fine coating of sweet sticky resin. Golden Tree Plushberry has a sweet fruity aroma of berries and blackberries with a smooth sugary exhale. The aroma is of earthy citrus with a sweet fruity effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart and burned.

Gold King's Thai.name: Gold King's Thai
Gold King's Thai.description: Gold King's Thai, also known as “Gold King's Thai Stick,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain bred as a rare cut of the classic Thai Stick from 1979. This infamous bud packs a super potent 15-20% average THC level and energizing daytime effects that are perfect as a wake-and-bake or when you need a quick boost of energy throughout the day. You'll feel the onset almost immediately, lifting you into a state of happy energy and focus. You'll feel an increase in creativity and motivation, making this bud perfect for when you have to get down to business and focus. A tingly body high accompanies this cerebral state, leaving you relaxed and pretty aroused. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Gold King's Thai is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including chronic fatigue, depression, mood swings, chronic pain, nausea or appetite loss, and chronic headaches or migraines. This bud has dense and heavy bright lime green nugs with lots of furry amber hairs and a coating of chunky oversized white crystal trichomes. As each nug is broken apart, you can detect fresh aromas of earthy florals and sweet lemon lime. The flavor is very sweet and tropical with a lemon lime overtone that will leave you begging for more.

Goo #13.name: Goo #13
Goo #13.description: Goo 13 is an indica dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the classic Afgoo X G13 strains. With its insanely powerful 20% + average THC level and full body effects, Goo 13 is the perfect pick for a user who loves an indica high and needs it to be strong. The high starts with an uplifted happy effect that boosts you mood but doesn't really give you any kind of energy. Rather, you'll be completely calm and relaxed with a sense of overwhelming wellbeing that permeates your entire body. This effect is accompanied by a slowly building body high that's not buzzy, but simply sits and eases away any aches and pains, replacing them with sleepiness and a pang of hunger. These effects and its powerful THC level make Goo 13 a great choice for treating conditions such as chronic stress, insomnia, depression, appetite loss, and nausea. This bud has a sweet flavor of fruity earth that's complemented by a spicy but smooth exhale. The aroma is almost sour, with a tangy fruity effect that's accented by earthy pine and pepper. Goo 13 buds have dense tight dark olive green grape-shaped nugs with bright orange hairs and a thick frosty coating of golden crystal trichomes.

Goo-Che.name: Goo-Che
Goo-Che.description: Goo-Che is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through crossing the potent Northern Californian Gooey X Chelumbian strains. If you're looking for a bud with a sticky heady high, you've found it with Goo-Che. This bud packs super stoney cerebral effects that will have you kicked back and without a care in the world. The high starts with a subtle lift, filling your mind with a sense of tingly euphoria that instantly pushes out any negative or racing thoughts. This is accompanied by a heavy case of the giggles that has you laughing at anything and everything around you. A relaxing body high comes next, slowing seeping into your limbs and weighing you down with a light and enjoyable heaviness.
