Combined with its high 15% + average THC level, these effects give Goo-Che an edge in treating conditions such as headaches or migraines, chronic stress, depression, nausea or appetite loss and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet and flowery herbal flavor with a super heavy pungent and dank earthy aroma to match. Goo-Che has conical airy olive green nugs with golden undertones, thick orange hairs and a coating of frosty golden chunky crystal trichomes dripping with sweet sticky resin.

Goo Berry.name: Goo Berry
Goo Berry.description: Goo Berry is a heavily indica dominant hybrid strain (90% indica/10% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Afgoo X Blueberry strains. Named for its sticky high and insanely delicious flavor, Goo Berry is absolutely perfect for any indica lover. The Goo Berry high starts in the head with a rush of euphoric effects that immediately leave you feeling focused and lifted. As your mind gets stuck in this state of clarity and bliss, your body will begin to fade away, falling victim to a heavy buzz that leaves you slightly sedated and hopelessly couch-locked without causing you to become too sleepy or doze off. With these effects and its high 18-20% average THC level, Goo Berry is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, mood swings or depression, and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has a sweet fruity berry flavor with a lightly spicy flowery exhale. The aroma is of sweet pine with a fruity herbal overtone that turns spicier as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Goo Berry buds have elongated grape-shaped minty green nugs with lots of orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of tiny golden amber crystal trichomes.

Good Medicine.name: Good Medicine
Good Medicine.description: Good Medicine is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created by breeders at the infamous Bodhi Seeds as a cross of (Green Crack X Tres Dawg) X Harlequin. Good Medicine was bred specifically to capture a super high CBD level – in this case it hits about 1:1 THC: CBD, although it has been recorded as high as 1:3 THC:CBD. These levels typically fall about the 15% mark on average, making Good Medicine highly medicinal but still with beloved THC effects. The high is super relaxing and mellow in nature, with uplifting and happy effects that are perfect for use any time of the day. A wash of relaxation will overcome you, leaving you slightly lazy but still able to get up and move if need be. These highly medicinal and long-lasting effects make Good Medicine perfect for treating a wide variety of conditions including inflammation, chronic pain, muscle spasms or tremors, and depression, among many others. It has a light sweet tropical mango flavor with a sugary candy overtone. The smell is of sweet yet spicy herbal tropical fruits with a sugary effect that can be detected as the nugs are burned. Good Medicine buds have long elegant conical forest green nugs with lots of orange hairs and a coating of dusty green crystal trichomes.

Good Morning.name: Good Morning
Good Morning.description: Good Morning is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) or slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica), depending on the breeder, that is created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains. The perfect bud for when you need a quick boost to get you going, Good Morning isn’t quite the best wake-and-bake but will work well on a weekend when you don’t have much of anything to get done. The high comes on with a cerebral effect at the onset, filling the mind with a lifted energetic euphoria that stimulates the spirits, leaving you feeling creative and happy, ready to take on the day. While your mind reaches new heights of energetic bliss, a relaxing body high will wash over you, keeping you anchored without causing too much laziness or couchlock. With these long-lasting effects and its moderate 5-19% average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, Good Morning is often chosen to treat conditions such as mood swings, depression, chronic stress, chronic fatigue and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet and flowery rose flavor with a heavily earthy aroma to match. Good Morning buds have thick flat spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of dark amber hairs and a frosty thick coating of golden amber crystal trichomes.

Gooey Block.name: Gooey Block
Gooey Block.description: Gooey Black is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the potent Afgoo X Blockhead strains. Like its name suggests, Gooey Black has super dense leafy dark olive green nugs. Each nug is spattered with dark amber hairs and coated with a layer of clear crystal trichomes and sweet sticky resin that look almost black in the right light. As you break apart each syrupy little nug, fresh fruity aromas are released with a touch of hashy pungency that can be detected as the nugs are broken apart. The flavor is very much the same, with a fresh berry pine taste accented by a zesty citrus exhale. Almost as soon as you exhale, you'll be smashed with the hard-hitting cerebral effects of Gooey Black. This will leave you insanely uplifted and euphoric with a hazy effect that leaves you unable to focus on much of anything. This cerebral effect will soon become introspective and stoney, dropping you off into a dazed, but relaxed, state that lasts for hours on end. Thanks to these potent effects and its super high 18-24% average THC level, Gooey Black is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, migraines or headaches, appetite loss, and chronic pain.

Gooey Wreck.name: Gooey Wreck
Gooey Wreck.description: Trainwreck was crossed with Afgooey to create this sativa-indica hybrid (the exact ratio of sativa to indica is unclear, but it's probably indica-dominant). The bud is reddish brown, with green and a fuzzy layer of trichomes. Gooey Wreck has a citrus aroma and a sweet flavor. It's definitely a rarity, probably found in few places except the West Coast. THC levels are unknown, though this isn't known as the world's most potent strain. CBD levels are likewise a mystery, but there's little evidence that this is an appropriate strain for patients with seizure disorders or other conditions alleviated by CBD. The high from Gooey Wreck is relaxing, with a likely focus on body effects as opposed to cerebral effects. It's apparently best used to treat physical symptoms, including inflammation, migraines, and chronic pain. Adverse effects may include dry eyes and dry mouth, though there are few reports on the subject. It may be possible to find this medical strain in some California dispensaries, but elsewhere it's pretty rare. The Afghani and Haze genes in Gooey Wreck make it a pleasant choice for some patients, but not popular enough to be easy to find.

Gorilla'd Cheese.name: Gorilla'd Cheese
Gorilla'd Cheese.description: Gorilla'd Cheese is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Gorilla Glue #3 X Clementine strains. If you're a hybrid lover who's after some serious potency behind their medicine, look no further than Gorilla'd Cheese. This bud packs everything you need and more into each delicious toke, with effects that will knock you flat out in no time at all. You'll feel them hit you almost as soon as you exhale, lifting your mind into a stimulating and tingly sense of euphoria. You'll be unfocused and giddy, totally unaware of any mental aches and pains whatsoever. At the same time, a stimulating tingle will work its way throughout your physical form, leaving you feeling fully relaxed and helplessly couch-locked with a pretty potent case of the munchies, too. With these effects and its super high 30% + average THC level, Gorilla'd Cheese is recommended for experienced patients suffering from conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, insomnia, chronic stress or anxiety and depression or mood swings. This bud has a sour citrusy flavor with a creamy citrusy exhale. The aroma takes a super pungent turn, with heavy rotting cheese and sharp sour tangerines galore. Gorilla'd Cheese buds have small rounded forest green nugs with deep amber undertones, dark hairs and a coating of milky amber crystal trichomes.

Gorilla Berry.name: Gorilla Berry

As your mind soars higher and higher, you'll feel a sense of calm wash over your body, keeping you anchored to the world below as your cerebral state falls into a heavy stone. With these hard-hitting effects and its super high 19-29% average THC level, Gorilla Wreck is best for treating the experienced user suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, appetite loss or nausea, mood swings, depression, and chronic fatigue. This bud has a super sweet candy grape flavor with a rich nutty diesel exhale. The aroma is super pungent and spicy with a citrus candy effect that quickly turns to heavy diesel as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Gorilla Wreck buds have dense fluffy dark olive green nugs with rich amber undertones, lots of orange hairs, and a coating of frosty tiny bright white crystal trichomes.

Gorilla Zkittlez.name: Gorilla Zkittlez
Gorilla Zkittlez.description: Gorilla Zkittlez is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the potent Original Glue X Zkittlez strains. If you love a great hybrid with a slight indica lean and a great flavor, Gorilla Zkittlez is totally made for you. This bud packs the best of everything, with a stimulating yet soothing high and a mouthwatering taste that will leave you begging for more. The high starts with a slow creeping effect, sneaking into the brain with a subtle lifting build. Suddenly you'll find your mind flying high into the clouds with a sense of pure happiness and ease that can leave you falling into fits of giggles at times. This is accompanied by a boost in creativity and a touch of sedation that has you fading away into long-lasting artistic thought before you finally fall asleep. In combination with its high 20-24% average THC level, these effects make Gorilla Zkittlez a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression or mood swings, appetite loss or nausea and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and fruity tropical flavor with hints of chocolate candy, too. The aroma is very similar, with a spicy overtone that's accented by creamy dark chocolate and earthy flowers. Gorilla Zkittlez buds have fat oversized olive green nugs with deep blue-purple undertones, thin clear amber hairs and a coating of tiny frosty white crystal trichomes.

Gorilla Zookies.name: Gorilla Zookies
Gorilla Zookies.description: Gorilla Zookies is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Animal Cookies X Gorilla Glue #4 strains. Best known for its head-slamming high and long-lasting effects, Gorilla Zookies is perfect for any hybrid lover. The high comes on with a slow build of effects, creeping up on your mind with an uplifted euphoria that pushes out any negative or racing thoughts with ease. As your mind settles into this state of focused happiness, a calming body high will slowly wash over you, leaving you feeling fully relaxed in both mind and body. You won't feel sedated in this state, but rather you'll feel totally at ease with the world around you and completely carefree. Thanks to these effects and its high 22-23% average THC level, Gorilla Zookies is often said to be perfect for treating conditions such as depression, mood swings, chronic stress, ADD or ADHD and chronic fatigue. This bud has a sweet and nutty flowery berry flavor with a lightly herbal exhale. The aroma is very similar, although with hints of peppery earth to it, too. Gorilla Zookies buds have dense and fluffy spade-shaped minty green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny frosty white crystal trichomes.

GORO.name: GORO
GORO.description: GORO is a rare sativa dominant hybrid (70% sativa/30% indica) strain created through crossing the infamous Zeta S.A.G.E. strain with the rare Wonkstar strain. With parents like these, you know you're in for one crazy high with GORO! Thanks to its super high 18-25% average THC level, this is pretty much guaranteed. The GORO high comes on fast and hard, slamming into your mind with powerful cerebral effects that can cause anxiety if you're not careful. You'll feel an immediate rush of uplifted energy and euphoria that leaves you almost frantic as you speed to get work done. As this state expands, a sense of sharp focus will creep in accompanied by a touch of creativity, lending themselves well to mental tasks. Thanks to these hard-hitting effects and its high THC level, GORO is recommended for experienced users suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, migraines or headaches, and nausea. This bud has a super sour fruity pine flavor and an earthy fresh aroma to match. GORO buds have thick round olive green nugs that are spattered with orange hairs and coated with tiny milky white crystal trichomes.

Got Bars OG.name: Got Bars OG
Got Bars OG.description: Got Bars OG is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created as a backcross of the famous Face Off OG. If you're looking for a light flavor with a heavy hazy high, you've found it with Got Bars OG. This bud brings on a sweet and mellow flowery pepper flavor with touches of sour citrus and fresh herbs. The aroma is earthy and spicy with a flowery overtone that turns to mellow sour citrus as the nugs are burned away. The Got Bars OG high settles in a few minutes after your final toke, filling your mind with an uplifted sense of creativity and happiness that ebbs and flows with warming tingly waves. You'll feel relaxed and without a care in the world, falling into fits of giggles here and there. This quickly turns hazy and unfocused, leaving you hopelessly stoned before you know it. With these effects and its super high 20-24% average THC level, Got Bars OG is said to be perfect for treating chronic pain, migraines or headaches, insomnia, depression and chronic stress. This bud has fluffy heart-shaped forest green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Graateful Dave.name: Graateful Dave
Graateful Dave.description: Grateful Dave is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other hybrid strains. Although its true parentage is unknown, Grateful Dave is often thought to be a member of the Grateful Breath family due to its soothing yet energizing high. The high settles in a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your brain with a lifted sense of energy and creativity that has your artistic mental gears turning. As your mind flies higher and higher into this happy state, you may find yourself falling out of touch with reality, succumbing to fits of the giggles before you even realize what’s happening. Throughout this high, a lifted sense will keep your head held high and your mood among the stars. In combination with its high 16-17% average THC level, these effects make Grateful Dave a great choice for treating conditions such as chronic pain, headaches or migraines, chronic stress or depression. This bud has a spicy and sweet fruity strawberry flavor with a lightly earthy cherry exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a strawberry overtone accented by spicy herbs and fresh earthiness. Grateful Dave buds have airy emerald-green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, golden white crystal trichomes.

Grace's Cookies.name: Grace's Cookies
Grace's Cookies.description: Grace's Cookies is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain created as a cross of the classic OG Kush X Durban Poison strains. This bud is the sister of Girl Scout Cookies and brings on the same flavors and effects, although with a slightly heavier touch thanks to its super high 22-23% average THC level. The Grace's Cookies high comes on slowly, filling you're your mind with a happy lift and a touch of energy. This energy grows as your euphoria does, leaving you feeling uplifted and active even as you start to fall into state of deep relaxation. Your mind and body will settle together, dropping you into a slightly sedated feeling, although not entirely sleepy. Thanks to these effects and its powerful THC level, Grace's Cookies is often chosen by experienced users to treat conditions such as chronic pain, nausea, appetite loss, chronic fatigue, and depression. This bud has a sweet and spicy dank cookie flavor with hints of rich earth on each exhale. The smell is very pungent and earthy with a sweet pine overtone that's rather mellow. Grace's Cookies buds have round olive green nugs with lots of furry orange hairs and a coating of tiny frosty amber crystal trichomes.

Gracie Slick.name: Gracie Slick
Gracie Slick.description: Gracie Slick is an indica dominant strain and has a 70:30 indica/sativa ratio. The strain is exotic looking and has plenty to offer for new and experienced cannabis users alike. With an amazing 24% THC content, it produces some of the finest buds to medicate with. The colors of the nugget will remind you of Halloween and they are rich in bright orange and dark purple hairs. The smell is exquisite and skunky at the same time. It smells the same as skunky grapes but is not as exceptional as its taste. During the inhale, Gracie Slick is musty, skunky and earthy but the taste transforms into a crisp grape flavor that will keep you coming back for more each time. The strain is strong to say the least. Gracie Slick can be used during the day or the night and its effects vary depending on consumption. The strain is better known for its medicinal effects and offers a heady high instead of knocking you out for good. However, a few more hits are more than enough to make you feel sleepy and exhibit symptoms of couch-lock. Gracie Slick is perfect for individuals who wish to socialize without being in a haze. That being said, it is equally effective at treating medical conditions like depression, anxiety, nausea and mood disorders.

Grandaddy Blueberry.name: Grandaddy Blueberry
Grandaddy Blueberry.description: Granddaddy Blueberry, also known as “Blueberry GDP,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through a tasty cross of the potent Blueberry X Granddaddy Purple strains. This bud is pretty rare, but is sought after for its 24% average THC level and powerful body heavy effects. The high takes a hit or two to gain traction, but once it does, get ready for a ride! You'll feel a building wave of euphoria and relief of mental pain that is slowly followed by a creeping body buzz that leaves you helplessly couch-locked and sedated. As the body high builds, you'll slowly succumb to a sleepy introspective state with a huge case of the munchies. These potent effects and its powerful THC level make this bud perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, muscle spasms, and tremors. This bud has a flavor much like its Granddaddy Purple parent, with flavors of sweet skunky berry accented by fruity grape and a hint of earth. The aroma is of sweet grape with a hint of musky fruitiness that's released as the nugs are broken apart and smoked. This bud has long dense light minty green pepper shaped nugs with lots of light amber hairs and a super thick coating of tiny crystal white trichomes.

Grandaddy Bruce.name: Grandaddy Bruce
Grandaddy Bruce.description: Grandaddy Bruce is an insanely potent indica dominant hybrid (80% indica/20% sativa) strain created by breeders at the infamous Green Depot. This dank bud is a cross between the hugely popular and extremely potent Grandaddy Purple X Bruce Banner strains and boasts a dope THC level ranging from 26-28% on average. Grandaddy Bruce has thick, dense light green nugs that are spade shaped, extremely leafy and fluffy, and have dark green undertones. These nugs have a spattering of long, thin rich amber hairs and a frosty layer of crystal trichomes. This strain has an aroma of sugary sweet grapes with an intensifying earthy overtone, and a taste of sweet floral with a spicy vanilla exhale. The Grandaddy Bruce high is described as a clean, mild cerebral high with pronounced body sensation. Users report feeling an onset of a mild, warming head buzz that slowly melts into a mellow, sedative couch-lock that still leaves you functional. This relaxing body high is pain-relieving and gives the user a sense of peaceful tranquility and general well-being. Due to this combination of potent body and mild head highs, Grandaddy Bruce is an ideal strain for treating patients suffering from conditions such as migraine headaches, chronic muscle pain or tension, nausea, and depression.

Grandaddy Crack.name: Grandaddy Crack
Grandaddy Crack.description: Granddaddy Crack is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Granddaddy Purps with the powerhouse Green Crack. The result is a head-spinningly powerful high that can leave you feeling anxious and paranoid if you're not careful. The high comes on fast and hard, slamming into your mind with an energetic cerebral lift that launches you into a state of uplifted bliss. As your mind soars higher and higher, so will your creativity, leaving you in a frantic artistically inspired state that can leave you distracted and introspective as well. Thanks to these powerful effects and its moderately high THC level, Granddaddy Crack is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, mood swings, Bipolar Disorder, and chronic stress or PTSD. Granddaddy Crack has a super sweet and spicy berry citrus flavor and gets tangy on each sour exhale. The smell is very tropical and sweet with a fruity citrus overtone that can be spicy at times. This bud has round lumpy olive green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny frosty amber crystal trichomes.

Grand Bay.name: Grand Bay
Grand Bay.description: Grand Bay, also known as “Bay 11,” “Grandaddy Bay” or “Grand Daddy Bay,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through crossing the classic Hindu Kush X Skunk strains. If you're a sativa lover who's after some serious power behind their medicine, Grand Bay is the perfect choice for you. With its high potency level and heavy effects, you'll be kicked back yet energized for hours on end with this bud. The high has an immediate effect, slamming into your eyes and forehead as soon as you exhale with an insane sense of uplifted and energizing euphoria. You'll find instant relief from negative moods or racing thoughts as they're replaced with a heady and unfocused happiness. A relaxing physical sense accompanies this heady lift, keeping your limbs anchored and leading to a pretty heavy case of the munchies eventually. In combination with its high 23-30% average THC level, these effects make Grand Bay a great choice for experienced patients suffering from chronic pain, appetite loss or nausea, depression and chronic fatigue. This bud has a sweet and sugary fruity citrus flavor with a lightly nutty vanilla exhale. The aroma is much like freshly baked citrusy cookies, with touches of sour earth to it, too. Grand Bay buds have small and dense spade-shaped forest green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny golden amber crystal trichomes.

Grand blue.name: Grand blue
Grand blue.description: Grand Blue, also known as “Granddaddy Blueberry” or “Blueberry GDP,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic flavorful Blueberry X Granddaddy Purple strains. With an addictive flavor and an even more addictive high, Grand Blue is one strain that will have you hooked after a single toke. Grand Blue has a sweet fruity flavor that brings together sugary berries and spicy grapes with a topping of fresh earth. The aroma is of pungent berries with a sweet earthy kush effect that has a potent hint of spicy pepper as the nugs are broken apart. Grand Blue buds have long and super dense pepper-shaped dark olive green nugs with purple and blue undertones, dark amber hairs, and a frosty thick coating of tiny lavender colored crystal trichomes. If you like the flavor of Grand Blue, you'll love the effects. The high hits you almost immediately after toking with a powerful heady effect that launches your mind to the skies and relaxes you through and through. Your body will become completely calm with a warming effect that ebbs throughout your limbs, making you very sleepy and completely sedated. Because of these effects, Grand Blue is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as appetite loss, insomnia, chronic pain, and muscle spasms.

Grand Canyon Purple.name: Grand Canyon Purple
Grand Canyon Purple.description: Grand Canyon Purple is an insanely dank hybrid strain that's indica dominant (70% indica/30% sativa) and boasts a moderate 18-22% average THC level. With an uplifting relaxing body high characterized by a mild body buzz and a warming sensation, this strain is ideal for day smoking and for newer users. Patients describe the high as a slowly creeping cerebral head high followed by an intense sense of body relief and relaxation that still leaves you functional. The exact genetics for the Grand Canyon Purple aren't well known due to secrecy of its breeders, but it is recognized by cannabis critics to most likely be a Grand Canyon Kush phenotype possibly crossed with Purple Urple, Grape Ape, or Purple Kush. This bud has an intensely fluffy popcorn-shaped olive green body with purple undertones and thin red hairs woven throughout. It has a spicy sweet pine aroma and floral and woody tastes with a sweet exhale. The Grand Canyon Purple is ideal for treating depression and anxiety and the perfect bud to accompany you on your next adventure through nature.

Granddaddy Cheese.name: Granddaddy Cheese
Granddaddy Cheese.description: Granddaddy Cheese, also known more commonly as “Purple Cheese,” is an indica dominant cross of the classic Cheese X Grand Daddy Purps strains. This celebrity child is infamous for its powerful stench that's almost like rotting rapes and cheese with a super funky creamy overtone. The taste is slightly milder, with a sweet fruity cream flavor that's accented by spicy cheese and herbs. Granddaddy Cheese has an uplifted yet sedating high that hits you hard in both mind and body. The high starts with a euphoric lift that gives your mood a substantial kick of positive energy that quickly lulls into a hazy calm state. A buzzing sedative effect comes next, washing over you and leaving you completely relaxed and sleepy with a sharp pang of hunger that leaves you reaching for anything within sight. Because of these effects, its powerful 20% average THC level, and 5% average CBD level, Granddaddy Cheese is perfect for treating insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has super dense and leafy dark olive green nugs with purple undertones, fiery orange hairs, and a super frosty coating of giant lavender crystal trichomes.

Granddaddy Grape.name: Granddaddy Grape
Granddaddy Grape.description: Granddaddy Grape is an indica dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the classic Granddaddy Purps X Grape Ape strains. This bud is said to be like either of its parents but to the nth degree. The flavor is like an amplified Granddaddy Purps, with a super sweet flavor of fruity grapes topped with spicy dank musk. The aroma is of pungent spicy grapes with a musky sweet skunky effect that will fill any room with a powerful stench. This bud has dense spade-shaped light minty green nugs with purple undertones, thick orange hairs, and a frosty thick coating of tiny purple crystal trichomes. The Granddaddy Grape high is that of a heavy indica, with psychoactive mind effects and completely relaxing body effects that blend beautifully. The high starts with a euphoric lift that is very hazy and happy, leaving you introspective and very spacey. This is accompanied by a building body buzz that washes over you, leaving you completely couch-locked and stoned without any hope of moving any time soon. These effects paired with its 16-20% average THC level make Granddaddy Grape the perfect choice for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, appetite loss, and chronic stress or anxiety.

Granddaddy Haze.name: Granddaddy Haze
Granddaddy Haze.description: Grandaddy Haze is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the classic Granddaddy Purps X Super Silver Sour Diesel Haze strains. The perfect happy bud for a lazy afternoon, Grandaddy Haze will have you feeling fine for hours and hours on end. The high starts a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your mind with a lifted snese of pure happiness and ease. You'll find laughter comes easily in this state as you fall in and out of focus, leaving you uncontrollably giggly at times. A soothing physical relaxation accompanies this heady high, helping your limbs to stretch out, completely free of aches and pains whatsoever. Thanks to these effects and its high 13-23% average THC level, Grandaddy Haze is often chosen to treat those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, PTSD, epilepsy, hypertension, chronic anxiety and multiple sclerosis. This bud has a sweet and sour fruity candy flavor with a lightly citrusy exhale. The aroma is like a bouquet of sour fruits, accented with sweet earthy diesel and a hint of spiciness. Grandaddy Haze buds have rounded spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with minty undertones, long thin orange hairs and a chunky coating of minty white crystal trichomes.

Granddaddy OG.name: Granddaddy OG
Granddaddy OG.description: Granddaddy OG is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the classic Granddaddy Purps X OG Kush strains. This celebrity child boasts a super gorgeous appearance and high-powered effects that are absolutely perfect for any indica lover. Granddaddy OG buds have rounded dark olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, thick dark orange hairs, and a coating of frosty chunky bright white crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each dense sticky little nugget, fresh aromas of herbs and earth accented by spicy grapes and pungent pine are released. The flavor is on the more mellow side of things, with sweet and spicy grapes accented by fresh pines and earth. The Granddaddy OG high is just as amazing as the flavor, with creeping effects that are perfect for when you need to kick back and let the stressors of your day drip off of you. You'll feel lifted and totally relaxed throughout the duration of this high, with a deep felt sense of euphoria that lasts from start to finish. Thanks to these effects and its high 19-26% average THC level, Granddaddy OG is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as depression, chronic stress, migraines or headaches, and nausea or appetite loss.

Grand Daddy Purple.name: Grand Daddy Purple
Grand Daddy Purple.description: Grand Daddy Purple is an indica dominant strain and is a cross between Big Bud and Purple Urkle. This blend explains why it has a complex berry and grape aroma while its nugs are oversized with a compact bud structure. The nugs are incredibly dense and fuzzy with deep purple hues that run throughout the buds. Additionally, the nugs are covered by orange hairs and contrast well with its resin-coated buds. What really sets this strain apart from the others is that it is easy to identify by the taste alone. Its taste lingers on the tongue for longer and will help you feel relaxed. The strain has a serious kick to it and its psychoactive effects are evidently detectable in both body and mind. It manages to deliver an overwhelming feeling of physical relaxation and cerebral euphoria. You will find yourself fixed in one spot while your thoughts float in a dreamy buzz for the duration of Grand Daddy Purple's effects. Just like any other indica dominant strain, it is primarily used for medical uses. The strain is quite effective for patients suffering from appetite loss, pain, insomnia, muscle spasms and stress.

Grand Daddy Purple x Bl....name: Grand Daddy Purple x Bl...
Grand Daddy Purple x Bl....description: GDP X Blackberry is a rare evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain with a super potent 24% average THC level and a mouthwateringly fruity flavor. GDP X Blackberry has a super sweet berry flavor with hints of fresh citrus and spices on each smooth exhale. The aroma is very spicy and dank with a heavy berry overtone that has a hint of pungency to it. With each fruity inhale comes lifted feelings of happiness and euphoria with a touch of energy. This energetic state will continue to grow with a tingly feeling throughout your entire body, leaving you relaxed and incredibly aroused. This buzzy effect will start to sink into your very limbs, leaving you slightly sedated and incredibly relaxed, although not sleepy or couch-locked in the slightest. In combination with its super high 24% average THC level, these effects give GDP X Blackberry an edge in treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, stress or anxiety, mood swings, and chronic pain. GDP X Blackberry buds have small super tight fluffy olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, clearish amber hairs, and a coating of dark amber crystal trichomes.

Grand Daddy Purp X Grap....name: Grand Daddy Purp X Grap...
Grand Daddy Purp X Grap....description: GDP X Grape Gorilla, also known as “Purple Gorilla” or “Grand Daddy Gorilla/GDG,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) with classic heritage. If you're looking for a bud that packs a punch of flavors and effects, you've found it. GDP X Grape Gorilla brings on a super potent high with a 22-29% average THC level and effects that can leave you dazed for hours on end. The high comes on with a rush of cerebral effects that creep up on you before suddenly slamming into you with a sense of euphoria and pure bliss. You'll feel your mind go from a state of focus and motivation to a hazy and unfocused feeling that leaves you dazed, slightly stoney and totally at ease. As your mind fades away, your body will start to follow suit, leaving you a bit couch-locked but not too sedated. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, GDP X Grape Gorilla is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, headaches or migraines, appetite loss or nausea, and chronic stress. This bud has a sweet and spicy berry flavor with hints of earthy herbs upon exhale. The aroma is very earthy and flowery with a spicy berry overtone that turns slightly pungent as the nugs are burned. GDP X Grape Gorilla buds have dense rounded forest green nugs with purple undertones, dark amber hairs, and tiny matching crystal trichomes.

Granddaddy Quin.name: Granddaddy Quin
Granddaddy Quin.description: Granddaddy Quinn is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the iconic Grandaddy Purps X Harlequin strains. The perfect combination of soothing and lifted effects, the Granddaddy Quinn is definitely one that you need to experience at least once in your life. Because it has a fairly low THC level of 6-7%, the effects of Granddaddy Quinn are overall pretty mild in nature. You'll feel lifted almost as soon as you exhale, filling your brain with a happy euphoria that has you feeling like you have not a care in the world. At the same time, a sense of calm will wash over you, filling your physical form with a deep sense of relaxation that helps soothe aching muscles and joints, letting you stretch out and kick back without any physical pain to speak of. Thanks to these effects and its low THC level and high 7-8% CBD level, Granddaddy Quinn is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including inflammation, chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic stress and depression. This bud has a sweet and fruity cherry berry flavor with a lightly woody exhale. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy woody overtone accented by fresh cherries and lightly spicy herbs. Granddaddy Quinn buds have small grape-shaped emerald green nugs with golden undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny, frosty white crystal trichomes.

Grand Daddy Urkel.name: Grand Daddy Urkel
Grand Daddy Urkel.description: Grand Daddy Urkel is an indica dominant hybrid strain with a 60:40 indica/sativa ratio and is the finest of its kind. The strain is produced by crossing Urkel with Big Bud. Grand Daddy Urkel has dense buds that are purple in color and rich in trichome coverage. The strain extensively borrows from its heritage and offers a taste and aroma unlike any other. It is a mouthwatering treat, to say the least. Even though the taste and aroma are no different, they offer a unique blend of berry and grape flavors. The strain is potent and offers psychoactive effects and is not limited in any way. As soon as you smoke the strain, you will feel its effects take control of your mind and body. You will be able to experience a perfect fusion of physical relaxation and cerebral euphoria, which is indescribable until or unless you give the strain a try. After a few minutes, you may exhibit symptoms of couch-lock. This is why it would be wise to smoke it before you go to bed. However, the strain is more commonly used for its medical effects as it is able to treat chronic pains and aches, muscle spasms and even loss of appetite.

Granddaddy Wonder.name: Granddaddy Wonder
Granddaddy Wonder.description: Granddaddy Wonder is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through a potent cross of 60-Day Wonder X Granddaddy Purps. Known for its consistent grow and long-lasting high, Granddaddy Wonder is the perfect bud for any indica lover who appreciates a great flavor, too. The Granddaddy Wonder high is packed full of stimulating mental effects and super relaxing physical effects, with a deeply relaxing overtone. You'll feel a growing euphoria at the onset, filling your mind with a sense of focused creativity and energy. As your mind lifts higher and higher, your body will begin to fall victim to a heavy body high, dropping you off into couch-locked relaxation and ease. Thanks to these effects and its high 15-20% average THC level, Granddaddy Wonder is often chosen to treat patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression or mood swings and chronic fatigue. This bud has a sweet bubblegum candy flavor with a lightly spicy grape exhale. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy herbal accent that finishes it off when the nugs are broken apart and burned away. Granddaddy Wonder buds have oversized fluffy rounded popcorn-shaped dark olive green nugs with deep purple undertones, dark amber hairs and a coating of matching crystal trichomes.

Grand Fire OG.name: Grand Fire OG
Grand Fire OG.description: Grand Fire OG is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the classic Blueberry X Grandaddy Purple X White Fire OG strains. This celebrity child yields a super potent high that can daze even the most experienced of users thanks to its insanely high 22-27% average THC level. The high starts with a rush of cerebral effects that burn their way through your mind, leaving a sense of happiness and calm in their wake. As your mind settles into a deep and long-lasting peace, your body will begin to follow suit, leaving you feeling slightly couch-locked and totally sedated, drifting in and out of sleep before fully succumbing. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Grand Fire OG is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, insomnia, appetite loss or nausea, and depression. This bud has a sour lemon flavor with a sweet fruity grape exhale that turns slightly spicy the more you toke. The aroma is of earthy herbs and spicy grape with a pungent sour citrus effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart and burned. Grand Fire OG buds have spade-shaped forest green nugs with lots of amber hairs and a thick frosty coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Grand Heft Auto.name: Grand Heft Auto
Grand Heft Auto.description: Grand Heft Auto is an indica dominant hybrid strain (65% indica/25% sativa/10% ruderalis) created through crossing the classic Northern Lights X AK-47 Auto strains. This autoflowering strain is a favorite of patients and breeders alike due to its easy grow and super lifted full-bodied high. The high is definitely one that's relaxing in nature, with effects that hit both mind and body with a high level of potency. You'll feel a heady lift that boosts the spirits almost as soon as you experience your final exhale, filling you with a giggly and sociable sense that has you easily chatting and laughing with those around you. A stoney body high comes next, locking you to the couch out of nowhere and leaving you totally kicked back and slightly sedated. Combined with its high 15-18% average THC level, these effects make Grand Heft Auto great for treating conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, mood swings or depression, chronic fatigue and chronic pain. This bud has a spicy and flowery taste with a super pungent and dank earthy aroma to match. Grand Heft Auto buds have oversized and super heavy bright neon green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny bright white crystal trichomes.

Grandi Candi.name: Grandi Candi
Grandi Candi.description: Grandi Candi is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of super sweet hybrid strains. Although its exact parentage is unknown, Grandi Candi is a favorite of breeders and patients alike for its amazing flavor and even more amazing potency level. Like its name implies, Grandi Candi has a super sweet and fruity candy flavor, with hints of fresh cherries and sour apples galore. The aroma is just as tangy, with a sour citrus candy overtone accented by a bouquet of fresh fruits and granny smith apples. The Grandi Candi high will hit you between the eyes almost as soon as you exhale, launching your mental state into one of calm and happiness. You’ll be unfocused and kicked back mentally, drifting in and out of reality. At the same time, a soothing body high will wash over you, relaxing your muscles and helping you stretch out before completely locking you to the couch. This combination will turn sedative, so be ready for a nap! Combined with its high 23% + average THC level, these effects make Grandi Candi a great choice for treating insomnia, chronic pain, depression or mood swings and cramps or muscle spasms. This bud has small tight grape-shaped dark olive green nugs with dark purple undertones, thin red-orange hairs and frosty purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Grandma Anderson\u2019s Cookies.name: Grandma Anderson’s Cookies
Grandma Anderson\u2019s Cookies.description: Grandma Anderson's Cookies, also known as “Gramma Anderson's Cookies,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the potent Girl Scout Cookies X an unknown hybrid strain. This celebrity child boasts everything you know and love about its Girl Scout Cookies parent, all wrapped up with an even sweeter flavor and a super high CBD level. Grandma Anderson's Cookies has a sweet and airy chocolate cookie taste with a light touch of sour citrus upon exhale. The aroma is of sweet nutty cookies with a spicy chocolate overtone and touches of earthy citrus. The Grandma Anderson's Cookies has a creeping effect, sneaking into your mind with a slow build before fully taking hold. You'll suddenly find yourself feeling fully euphoric with a lifted sense of happiness that pushes out any negative or racing thoughts. As your mind reaches new heights, a deeply relaxing body stone will wash over your physical form, dropping you off into a state in which you're purely immovable. Thanks to these effects and its high 15-20% average THC level and super high 5-10% CBD level, Grandma Anderson's Cookies is often chosen to treat depression, inflammation, insomnia, seizures, chronic stress or anxiety and chronic pain. This bud has dense grape-shaped bluish-green nugs with lots of orange hairs and a coating of tiny blue-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Grandmaster Chem.name: Grandmaster Chem
Grandmaster Chem.description: Grandmaster Chem, also known as “Chem Master,” is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Master Kush X Chemdawg D strains. When it comes to heavy-hitting hybrids, Grandmaster Chem is totally what you need. This bud brings on the super powerful potency, with a THC level that hits about 23-28% on average and effects that can last for hours on end. The high starts with a rush of cerebral effects that rip their way through your brain, leaving you with a sense of focused energy and motivation that wipes out any negative or racing thoughts with ease. As your mind lifts higher and higher, a tingly effect will start to build in the back of your head, working its way through the rest of your body, leaving you slightly buzzy and totally aroused. A giggly heady effect comes next as your mind starts to fade into haziness, leaving you laughing at anything and everything around you for no reason at all. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Grandmaster Chem is said to be perfect for treating depression, mood swings, chronic stress, seizures, chronic pain, and ADD or ADHD. This bud has as super spicy chemical pungent flavor with hints of woody sweet diesel upon exhale. The aroma is super pungent and harsh with a chemical diesel overtone that has a light sweet and sour earthy effect that's released as the nugs are burned. Grandmaster Chem buds have forest green spade-shaped nugs with purple undertones, dark amber hairs, and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes with resin throughout.

Grand Master Kush.name: Grand Master Kush
Grand Master Kush.description: Grand Master Kush, also known as “Grandmaster Kush” or “Master Kush,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the iconic Hindu Kush X Skunk strains. A celebrity in the world of medical marijuana, Grand Master Kush is a favorite of both patients and breeders alike for its heavy potency and classic indica effects. The high has a sedative and relaxing overtone that permeates both mind and body, settling in a few minutes after your final toke. You'll suddenly find yourself feeling lifted with a sense of happy calm and creativity while your body is slightly sedated and couch-locked. This relaxing feeling will grow and grow, eventually creeping into your mind, too, and pulling you down into a deep and heavy sedation that often ends in sleep. Thanks to these effects and its high 18-28% average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, Grand Master Kush is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress, depression, chronic pain, nausea or appetite loss, insomnia and muscle spasms or cramps. This bud has a classic sweet and fruity flavor with a lightly sour and lemony exhale. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy flowery overtone accented by fresh fruits and sour citrusy lemons. Grand Master Kush buds have grape-shape forest green nugs with thin yellow-orange hairs and a coating of chunky, golden-white crystal trichomes.

Grand Master Sexy.name: Grand Master Sexy
Grand Master Sexy.description: Grand Master Sexy, also known as “Grandmaster Sexy,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the iconic Oreoz X Scotty 2 Hotty strains. A delightfully flavorful bud with super arousing effects, you'll find yourself calling upon the Grand Master Sexy again and again. This bud has a super sweet and creamy sugary chocolate flavor accented by hints of fresh caramel and vanilla. The aroma is very similar, with a creamy dessert-like overtone accented by a slight touch of spicy diesel. The Grand Master Sexy high is perfect for getting it on, with stimulating and arousing effects that are great for getting anyone in the mood. You'll feel lifted and giggly with an outgoing sense that has you easily chatting with anyone around you, although you may find yourself laughing uncontrollably at times for no reason whatsoever. With these effects and its high 22-23% average THC level, Grand Master Sexy is often said to be perfect for treating patients with conditions such as chronic stress or PTSD, mood swings or depression, insomnia and chronic pain. This bud has fluffy and oversized heart-shaped dark olive green nugs with thick orange hairs and tiny, minty white crystal trichomes.

Grandpa's Finest.name: Grandpa's Finest
Grandpa's Finest.description: Grandpa's Finest is a super rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other high-powered hybrids. Although its exact parentage is unknown, rumor has it that Grandpa's Finest is actually a member of the infamous Girl Scout Cookies family, although this has yet to be confirmed. Nevertheless, Grandpa's Finest stands tall on its own, with a myriad of happy heady effects and a delicious flavor, too. The high hits you almost as soon as you exhale, filling your brain with a lifted sense of euphoria. You'll find your senses activated with a heavy focus and your mind turn up your creativity to new heights. Mental tasks will come easily and conversations will flow perfectly in this state, but you may find yourself falling out of touch with reality at times. Combined with its high 28% + average THC level, these effects make Grandpa's Finest a great choice for treating conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, depression, chronic stress and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet and sour citrusy lemon flavor with a lightly peppery and herbal aroma to go with it. Grandpa's Finest buds have fat and fluffy rounded blue-green nugs with thin yellow-orange hairs and frosty, chunky white crystal trichomes.

Grandpa's Stash.name: Grandpa's Stash
Grandpa's Stash.description: Grandpa's Stash is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the potent 1994 Super Skunk X 1992 OG Kush X 1970s Afghan Kush strains. Known for its heavy potency level and super happy high, Grandpa's Stash is one bud that you'll want to break into again and again. It starts with a heady lift, filling your mind with an ecstatic euphoria and a flowing creativity that gets those mental juices going. You'll feel chatty and ready to carry on conversations with anyone and everyone around you. This is accompanied by a sense of physical relaxation that helps your body settle into a pain-free state of ease. In combination with its super high 23-24% average THC level, these effects make Grandpa's Stash a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression or mood swings, chronic pain and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and fruity woody pine flavor with a light touch of skunkiness to it, too. The aroma is on the skunkier side, with deep pungent anise and sharp woody pine accented by fresh earth. Grandpa's Stash buds have spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thick orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny white crystal trichomes.

Grandpa Bub.name: Grandpa Bub
Grandpa Bub.description: Grandpa Bub is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain with unknown parentage due to a high level of breeder secrecy about its origins. Even with the lack of information about its heritage, this super-powered bud is infamous for its insanely pungent stench and its long-lasting effects thanks to a super high 29.4% average THC level. Grandpa Bub has a super dank and skunky flavor that becomes more and more intense with each toke. The aroma will fill any room with its heavy stench of skunky kush and dank rotting earth. The Grandpa Bub high is that of any classic OG, with a super lifted effect that fills both mind and body with pure relaxation and a sense of laziness. You’ll feel a heady onset a few minutes after your last toke that lifts your spirits to new heights, infusing you with a sense of utter happiness. A deep relaxation will wash over you afterwards, filling you with a tingly effect that causes you to feel slightly lethargic and a little couch-locked at times. With these effects, Grandpa Bub is the perfect choice for killing the effects of depression, chronic pain, inflammation, muscle spasms, and anxiety or stress. This bud has dense oversized super heavy dark nugs with olive green leaves, lots of furry dark amber hairs, and a coating of matching crystal trichomes.

Grandpa Simpson.name: Grandpa Simpson
Grandpa Simpson.description: Grandpa Simpson is an indica dominant hybrid strain with unknown parentage due to a general lack of knowledge about its history. Nonetheless, this bud is definitely a must-have for any Simpsons fan or simply anyone who appreciates a mellow full-body high. One visit from good ole Grandpa Simpson and you'll be feeling relaxed and hazy for hours on end. It starts with a happy lift that is pretty hazy, boosting your mood and leaving you unable to focus on really anything around you. Even with this lack of clarity, you'll be super talkative, blabbering on to anyone that will listen to you about nothing in particular. Coupled with its 14-19% average THC level. These long-lasting effects give Grandpa Simpson an edge in treating conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, mood swings, PTSD, and chronic pain. Grandpa Simpson has a super skunky aroma that's accented by pungent pine and a touch of fruity earth as the nugs are burned. The flavor is surprisingly sweet with touches of berries and pine and a sharp skunky aftertaste that's surprisingly pleasant. This bud has round fluffy forest green nugs with dark orange hairs and a coating of tiny milky white crystal trichomes.

Grandpa\u2019s Breath.name: Grandpa’s Breath
Grandpa\u2019s Breath.description: Grandpa's Breath is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic OG Kush with the infamous Grand Daddy Purple strain. This celebrity child packs potent full-bodied effects that are perfect for when you need high-powered relief that lasts and lasts. You'll feel an immediate clear-headed effect after your first hit or two of Grandpa's Breath, leaving you mentally pain-free and euphoric. This is accompanied by a touch of creativity that quickly turns unfocused and sleepy as the high continues to work its way through your mind. Depending on how much you toke, you may fall asleep at this point in the high or experience a rally of mental energy. With these effects and its high THC level, Grandpa's Breath is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, PTSD, depression, chronic fatigue, and insomnia. Grandpa's Breath has a super dank and spicy diesel flavor with hints of fresh apricot hidden throughout. The aroma is very earthy and pungent with a fruity diesel overtone that's almost sweet at times. Grandpa's Breath buds have heavy dense dark olive green nugs with purple undertones, almost clear amber hairs, and a coating of super sticky resin dotted with clear crystal trichomes.

Grand Poobah.name: Grand Poobah
Grand Poobah.description: This indica-heavy choice is a cross between the potent sativa Purple Diesel and Granddaddy Blueberry, an indica-dominant hybrid. Don't look too hard for information about Grand Poobah; there isn't much out there. It's described as a good strain for chronic pain, insomnia, and poor appetite. It can also treat anxiety and mood disorders. The buds are densely packed and sticky, with a heavy coating of trichomes. The smell is skunky, while the grape flavor harks back to this strain's Purple ancestry. It's an open question how much of this strain is indica and how much is sativa. The same goes for the CBD and THC contents of Grand Poobah. The high is relaxing but energized, with a heavier focus on body effects. Likely side effects include dry mouth and red eyes, though others are possible. Though it would be easier to find on the legal market, and is probably more common on the West Coast, it isn't widely available anywhere. It's not especially noteworthy as a medical strain, but some patients may find that it helps with their physical symptoms.

Grand Purple Tragedy.name: Grand Purple Tragedy
Grand Purple Tragedy.description: Grand Purple Tragedy is an indica dominant hybrid (90% indica/10% sativa) strain bred from the combination of the immensely popular Grand Daddy Purple X Tragic strains. This dank bud boasts a 15-17% average THC level and a myriad of indica and sativa effects. Grand Purple Tragedy is often described as "the perfect nighttime bud" due to its potent effects. Users describe the high as a slowly creeping body buzz that melts into a heavy indica body stone with a pleasant warming euphoric head buzz. This high has a mellow fade into droopy eyes, munchies, and a deep peaceful sleep. Because of these potent body relaxing and euphoric effects, Grand Purple Tragedy is ideal for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, especially from conditions such as cancer and multiple sclerosis (MS), migraines, tension headaches, and sleep disorders. This dank bud is said to smell like a walk through a pine forest - fresh pine with a floral twist. Grand Daddy Purple tastes just as good as it smells - it has a fruity pine taste that fades into a syrupy sweetness upon exhale. This dank bud has dark green, dense spade-shaped nugs with bright green leafs and rich brown hairs that are practically dripping in resin.

Gran Flora.name: Gran Flora
Gran Flora.description: Gran Flora, also simply called “Great Plant,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through crossing the infamous Afghan X Ticinensis Purpurea strains. Although its hard to come by outside of South America, Gran Flora is a great choice for the hybrid lover who appreciates a classic flavor. Gran Flora has a sweet honey taste that's accented by lemongrass and flowers with just a hint of pine. The aroma is of pungent skunky earth with an overtone of rich florals and woods topped with sweet honey. Gran Flora buds are beautiful to behold, with medium-sized spade-shaped nugs that are a bright olive green with purple undertones and hairs and a thick coating of chunky trichomes that appear almost lavender in the light. The Gran Flora high is just as sweet as its flavor, with incredibly balanced effects that bring together the best of both indica and sativa. The high begins with an almost immediate onset of an uplifted cerebral rush that leaves you clear-headed with a sense of creative energy that's slightly numbed and not in the least bit overwhelming. A building body buzz will creep up on you next, filling you with warmth and relaxation without weighing you down. These effects paired with its high 18% average THC level make Gran Floral perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, migraines, chronic stress or anxiety, and ADD/ADHD.

Granny Derkle.name: Granny Derkle
Granny Derkle.description: Grannny Derkle is an indica dominant hybrid (80% indica/20% sativa) strain created through a four-way cross of the classic NYC Diesel X Purple Haze X GDP X Purple Urkel strains. This celebrity child packs a mellow clear-headed high that's perfect for kicking back at the end of a long stressful day when sleep just won't come. It starts with a relaxing lift that boosts your mood without increasing your energy level. Rather, it infuses you with a sense of calm and clear-headed bliss that leaves you aware of everything going on around you without making you anxious about it. You might become a little sleepy as this head high builds and your level of clarity fades into comfortable haziness. With these effects and its moderately high 14-16% average THC level, Granny Derkle is a great choice for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has long and piecey dark olive green nugs with purple undertones and leaves that are completely coated in oversized white crystal trichomes. The Granny Derkle flavor is very sweet and spicy with hints of citrus and floral and just a touch of grape. The aroma is incredibly fragrant with a floral overtone that's accented by fresh citrus.

Grapealicious.name: Grapealicious
Grapealicious.description: Grapealicious is a slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through an unknown combination of other fruity hybrid strains. A great well-balanced hybrid with a slight sativa lean, Grapealicious is the perfect bud for anyone who’s after a relaxing high that will stimulate mind and body before helping both to settle down. The high comes with a with a cerebral boost of euphoria a few minutes after your final toke, filling your brain with an expansive happy sense. A relaxing body buzz accompanies this heady lift, helping to keep your physical form anchored as your mind flies higher and higher. This combination does quickly turn sedative and heady, which will leave you giggling and unfocused before you finally fade away into a long and peaceful sleep. With these effects and its moderate 12-19% average THC level, Grapealicious is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression, insomnia, chronic pain, muscle spasms or cramps and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has a sweet and fruity berry grape flavor with a lightly sour and kushy exhale. The aroma is of spicy fruity grapes, sweet berries and a kushy spicy overtone that intensifies the more that you toke. Grapealicious buds have fat and rounded olive green nugs with dark purple undertones, deep red-orange hairs and a coating of frosty, purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Grape Animal.name: Grape Animal
Grape Animal.description: Grape Animal, also known as “Grape Animals,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Pie X Animal Cookies strains. This celebrity child boasts an insanely delicious flavor and soothing effects that will have your mind flying and your body settling for hours on end. Much like its name suggests, Grape Animal has a super sweet and fruity grape berry flavor with a sugary candy exhale. The aroma is just as delicious, with a sugary grape overtone accented by touches of earthy herbs and a hint of spice. The Grape Animal high will hit you almost as soon as you exhale, filling your brain with a lifted sense of cerebral energy and euphoria. You'll feel your senses activate as you easily carry on conversations with those around you, free of any negative moods or racing thoughts. At the same time, a soothing body high will wash over you, helping your physical form to settle down and relax before you finally become fully couch-locked. Combined with its high 23-25% average THC level, these full-bodied effects make Grape Animal a great choice for treating experienced patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression or mood swings, PMS, chronic pain and headaches or migraines. This bud has spade-shaped dark forest green nugs with deep purple undertones, thick orange hairs and frosty chunky purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Grape Berry.name: Grape Berry
Grape Berry.description: Grape Berry, also known as “DJ Short Grape Kush,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid (60% indica/40% sativa) strain that is a Blueberry phenotype bred by the infamous DJ Short to draw out a more grapey flavor than its Blueberry parent. The taste is definitely very grape-like, with hints of fruity berry and pungent muskiness to complement the sweetness of the grape flavor. The aroma is very pungent and earthy with hints of musky grapes and spices that are released as the nugs are burned. Grape Berry buds have tight and super dense forest green nugs with purple undertone, sparse orange hairs, and a coating of super sticky resin and tiny clear crystal trichomes. The Grape Berry high is very much like those of its parents, with both head and body effects that are stoney and long-lasting. The high starts with a cerebral onset that leaves you uplifted and blissfully hazy, before lulling you into a completely sedated state with a powerful body buzz that creeps up on you. You'll be utterly stoned and helpless to do anything except sit on your couch and maybe eat a snack. Because of these effects and its high 16-18% average THC level, Grape Berry is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, depression, muscle spasms, inflammation, and chronic stress or anxiety.

Grape Blow.name: Grape Blow
Grape Blow.description: Grape Blow is a heavily indica dominant hybrid strain (90% indica/10% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Pie X Blow Pops strains. Best known for its super delicious flavor and heavy indica effects, Grape Blow is the perfect choice for any experienced patient. Much like its name suggests, Grape Blow has a super sweet fruity grape candy flavor with hints of sour citrusy lemon upon exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a fruity grape overtone accented by sour lemon and a punch of spicy nuttiness. The Grape Blow high will hit you a few minutes after your final exhale, rushing into your brain with a happy, lifted effect that will leave you feeling blissful and unfocused. This state will quickly ebb and fade into a stoney cerebral state that will have you totally out of touch with reality. A calming body high comes next, washing over you and lulling you into a state of pure relaxation that will quickly turn sedative and sleepy. With these effects and its super high 24-34% average THC level, Grape Blow is often said to have an edge in treating chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, arthritis, insomnia, nightmares and PMS. This bud has fat triangle-shaped minty green nugs with deep purple leaves, golden undertones, dark amber hairs and a coating of chunky bright white crystal trichomes.

Grape Cake.name: Grape Cake
Grape Cake.description: Grape Cake is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Grape Stomper X Cherry Pie X Wedding Cake strains. Known for its super delicious flavor and long-lasting high, Grape Cake is the perfect bud for any indica lover who needs a little power behind their medicine. This bud has a super sweet and fruity grape flavor with a lightly spicy and savory cherry diesel exhale. The aroma is very similar, although with a deep pungent berry overtone that intensifies the more that you toke. The Grape Cake high settles in slowly after your first toke or two, taking on the mind before spreading to the body with a high level of potency. You'll feel a heavy influx of creativity and focus, filling you with a mental clarity that's perfect for taking on any task at hand. As your mind flies high, your body will begin to settle into a relaxing state that's not too sedative in nature. With these effects and its high 20% + average THC level. Grape Cake is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as depression, chronic stress, ADD or ADHD, chronic fatigue and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has fluffy spade-shaped dark olive green nugs with deep purple undertones, dark brown hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

Grape Cheese.name: Grape Cheese
Grape Cheese.description: Grape Cheese is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the potent Grape Stomper X UK Cheese strains. A potent bud with a unique flavor, Grape Cheese is a favorite of indica lovers across the country. Like its name suggests, Grape Cheese has a sweet and fruity grape berry flavor with hints of fresh creamy cheese and a punch of spicy dank to it, too. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy herbal overtone accented by spicy dank, creamy cheese and rich fruity grapes. The Grape Cheese high will settle in a few minutes later, washing over both mind and body in warming waves, lulling you into a state of lifted yet relaxed euphoria. You'll feel happy yet physically stoned, not really able to do much of anything at all. This combination will quickly turn sleepy, leaving you dozing off and fading into a long and peaceful sleep before you know what's happening. With these effects and its high 22-27% average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, Grape Cheese is often chosen to treat those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, inflammation, insomnia and depression or mood swings. This bud has small and tight spade-shaped dusty green nugs with thin, pinkish-orange hairs and a coating of tiny, bright amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Cola.name: Grape Cola
Grape Cola.description: Green Man Grape Cola is more often known as part of hybrid strains than known for being used on its own. However, it is one of the best quality strains available. Not only does it offer 90:10 Indica/Sativa effects, it also has a taste people find to be very delicious. The parent strains of Green Man Grape Cola are Bubba Kush and Pre 98. The smell of this marijuana strain is very potent. The smell is a cross grape and that is also the taste generated. It has a bubbly type of feeling that it creates in the mouth. It is similar to drinking a cola beverage that is fizzy. It is typically consumed through a vaporizer or glass pipe for optimal taste. Individuals suffering from severe chronic pain often use Green Man Grape Cola to help them control it. This includes pain due to MS, muscle spasms, and arthritis. It can also help to increase appetite and reduce nausea. Such side effects are very commonly experienced by those using various prescription medications for their health concerns. This strain can also help reduce stress and anxiety.

Grape Crush.name: Grape Crush
Grape Crush.description: The indica genes win out in this hybrid (the exact sativa/indica ratio is unknown), though the sativa keeps the high energized and easy. Grape Crush is a descendant of indica Blueberry parents, so its distinct purple coloring and sweet berry flavor are no coincidence. This strain produces a euphoric, lazy sensation with both head and body effects. The high is happy, focused, and occasionally sleepy. Grape Crush is effective as a treatment for anxiety and stress, as well as sleeplessness, chronic pain, and migraine headaches. Dry mouth is fairly common, as are dry eyes and dizziness. Headaches and paranoia are more limited. THC levels can vary considerably in this strain, but available tests peg them at slightly more than 12%. CBD levels, meanwhile, are just 0.28%, not enough to recommend Grape Crush as a treatment for epilepsy or other disorders that respond to CBD. This strain can be found on legal medical markets in California, Oregon, Arizona, Colorado, and Canada. It may appear on the black market in some places, so while it's relatively popular, it isn't exactly a staple among patients.

Grape Diamonds.name: Grape Diamonds
Grape Diamonds.description: Grape Diamonds is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the classic Pink Grapefruit X Member Berry strains. Named for its gorgeous appearance and delicious flavor, Grape Diamonds packs a super giddy high that will have you flying to new heights before you know it. Grape Diamonds buds have fat pepper-shaped minty green nugs with dark olive green leaves, deep purple undertones and a frosty thick blanketed coating of tiny sparkling purple-tinted crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sparkling little nugget, aromas of fresh spicy grape and sour citrus are released, all wrapped up with a skunky overtone. The flavor is very similar, with a sweet and spicy overtone that's accented by fresh grapes and sour grapefruit. The Grape Diamonds high comes rushing in almost as soon as you exhale, launching you into an unfocused and giggly state almost immediately. A sense of sociability accompanies this giddy state, giving you the energy that you need to take on any social situation or conversation with ease. Thanks to these effects and its high 25-30% THC level and 1% CBD level, Grape Diamonds is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress, depression or mood swings, chronic fatigue and nausea or appetite loss.

Grape Diesel.name: Grape Diesel
Grape Diesel.description: Being a sativa dominant strain, Grape Diesel is unlike any other strain you may have come across before. With a 25:75 indica/sativa ratio and an amazing 20% THC content, the strain will keep you coming back for seconds. Looking at the strain, you will come to realize that the buds are not only good looking but quite tempting at the same time. The buds are large and covered with bluish pink spots all over it. Additionally, the strain has no stems at all, which is preferred by most experienced cannabis users. Even though it is bitter, the scent has citrus undertones to go along with it. The taste is very smooth with a fruity finish during the exhale. The high will give you an immediate headstone. After a few hits, you will realize your vision will start getting fuzzy. Smoking the strain in larger doses will knock you out which is why it is recommended specifically for night time use. The buzz is clear, but it will not numb your senses completely. You will still find it easier to focus and concentrate on tasks. That being said, the strain is incredibly useful for individuals suffering from asthma, migraines, stress, depression and even insomnia.

Grape Dream.name: Grape Dream
Grape Dream.description: Grape Dream is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic celebrity Granddaddy Purps X Blue Dream strains. This tasty bud is not to be confused with its sister strain, “Purple Dream,” another descendant of Blue Dream. The Grape Dream effects are certainly dreamy and surreal, with an uplifted happy onset that boosts your mood and launches your mind into hazy bliss that's slightly sedative. As your mind soars through deep introspection, your body will become numbed by a stoney body buzz that locks you into wherever you're sitting and eventually pulls you down into a sleepy and narcotic melted state. These effects paired with its high 13-25% average THC level make Grape Dream ideal for treating insomnia, chronic pain, depression, and chronic stress. Like its parents, Grape Dream has a super fruity flavor of berries and spicy pungency that can be super strong at times. The aroma is super sour and pungent, with a spicy earthy overtone that's accented by a stench of rotting berries that becomes slightly sweet as the nugs are burned. Grape Dream buds have small minty green grape-shaped nugs with purple and blue undertones, dark amber hairs, and a frosty thick coating of tiny crystal trichomes that look almost blue in the light.

Grape Durkle.name: Grape Durkle
Grape Durkle.description: Grape Durkle is an indica dominant hybrid (75% indica/25% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic Grape Ape X Durkle strains. Grape Durkle is one potent bud that's pretty hard to get your hands on, but once you try it, you'll be scrambling to get more as soon as you can. The high is very sleepy and sedating, with an overwhelming sense of calm that can lull even the most experienced user into a deep and peaceful sleep. It starts with a euphoric onset that boosts your mood, but not your energy, and numbs your mind with a hazy effect. A creeping body buzz comes next, filling your very being with a powerful sense of relaxation that causes hunger but draws you into a dreamy deep narcotic state. Because of these effects and its powerful 20-23% average THC level, Grape Durkle is a patient favorite for treating insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, inflammation, and muscle spasms or cramps. This bud has dense but airy dark olive green nugs with lots of amber hairs, rich purple undertones, and a frosty coating of tiny amber colored milky crystal trichomes. Like its parents, Grape Durkle has a sweet grapey flavor that's slightly musky with a sour skunky exhale. The aroma is super pungent and skunky, with a hint of sweet grape and berries that's incredibly sour and very potent.

grapefruit blaze.name: grapefruit blaze

With these calming effects and its moderate 12-15% THC level and high 5-8% CBD level, Grape Muerto is said to be the perfect medicinal strain for treating conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, inflammation, seizures, muscle spasms or cramps and depression. This bud has a sweet and fruity grape flavor with a notably skunky spicy exhale. The aroma is heavy and pungent with a spicy grape overtone that's accented by savory skunk and rich woods. Grape Muerto buds have fluffy dark green airy nugs with dark amber hairs, deep purple undertones and a coating of clear crystal trichomes dripping with sweet syrupy resin.

Grapenstein.name: Grapenstein
Grapenstein.description: Grapenstein is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other deliciously fruity Grape strains. While its parentage is kept a closely guarded secret by its breeders, Grapenstein is often sought out by breeders and patients alike for its super amazing flavor and soothing high that will have your mind and body feeling like you don't have any cares in the world. Like its name very much implies, Grapenstein has a super sweet and fruity grape berry flavor with hints of sugary blueberries and touches of woody pine. The aroma is very similar, almost like a fresh bouquet of grapes and berries accented by spicy diesel and pungent woodiness. The Grapenstein high is just as delicious, with effects that start in the eyes before taking on the rest of your body. You'll feel a light pressure behind the eyes that soon spreads throughout your entire brain, leaving you feeling euphoric and lifted yet super hazy. As your mind settles into this heady state, your body will begin to settle into a state of pure relaxation and ease that has you feeling super kicked back and pretty hungry at times. Combined with its high 23-25% average THC level, these effects make Grapenstein a great choice for treating a variety of conditions including eye pressure or glaucoma, chronic stress, depression, chronic pain and appetite loss. This bud has fat oversized Christmas tree-shaped nugs with dusty green undertones, lots of thin yellow-orange hairs and milky white crystal trichomes.

Grapeology.name: Grapeology
Grapeology.description: Grapeology is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Skunk X Grape Pie strains. Named for its super delicious flavor, Grapeology is the perfect choice for any classic indica lover who's after smooth effects and a mouthwatering taste. Like its name suggests, Grapeology packs a super sweet fruity grape flavor with hints of sour candy and a touch of spiciness, too. The aroma is very similar, with a rich spicy grape overtone accented by hints of fresh skunk and earthy herbs. The Grapeology high is one that's perfect for an afternoon when you still have things to do but want to kick back and relax in an hour or two. It starts with an almost immediate rush of energy that boosts the spirits and fills your mind with a get-moving sense. You'll be creative and focused, easily carrying on conversations with those around you.
