As the high continues, this focus will suddenly take a heady shift, dropping you into an unfocused sedation that has you sleepy and drifting off before you know it. Combined with its high 18-20% average THC level, these effects make Grapeology a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression or mood swings, headaches or migraines and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has fat small rounded olive green nugs with dark brown hairs and tiny frosty purple crystal trichomes.

Grape Ox.name: Grape Ox
Grape Ox.description: Grape OX is a heavily indica dominant hybrid (90% indica/10% sativa) strain created as a cross between the powerful Grape Ape X OX strains. This dank bud was the 3rd Place Winner at the High Times' Michigan Medical Cup in 2014 and was bred specifically to combine a powerful THC level and CBD level in one delicious bud. Grape OX offers an insanely high average THC level between 20-24% and a CBD level that ranges between 4-6% on average. Grape OX has a creeping head high that you probably won't notice until it reaches its peak, at which you'll feel extremely uplifted and euphoric. This feeling has gentle waves of utter pain-free bliss that slowly flow into a state of sleepy sedation. Upon the comedown, you may find yourself falling peacefully into a deep and pain-free sleep that lasts for hours on end. Because of these relaxing effects and its high CBD level, Grape OX is perfect to treat chronic pain, inflammation, mild to moderate cases of depression, and muscle spasms. This bud has a classic Purple aroma of sweet and spicy grape and a taste of sweet grapes with a spicy blueberry aftertaste upon exhale. Grape OX buds have extremely frosty large dense leafy cone-shaped light minty green nugs with amber hairs and rich purple undertones.

Grape Pearls.name: Grape Pearls
Grape Pearls.description: Grape Pearls, also known as “Grape Pearl,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Pie X Silver Pearls strains. Named for its celebrity parentage and delicious flavor, Grape Pearls is the perfect choice for any hybrid lover. Like its name suggests, Grape Pearls has a sweet and fruity berry grape flavor with a lightly sour and citrusy exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a fruity and woody kush overtone accented by a punch of sour citrus and sweet fruity grapes. The Grape Pearls high will settle in a few minutes after your final exhale, pushing its way gently into your brain with a happy sense that leaves no room for bad moods or negative thoughts. At the same time, a physical sense of relaxation will wash over your body, lulling you into an eventual couch-locked state of calm and ease. This combination will quicky turn sedative, leaving you dozing off before you know it. Combined with its super high 28-29% average THC level, these effects make Grape Pearls a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as hypertension, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic pain and arthritis. This bud has long and dense spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with bright amber undertones, furry orange hairs and chunky golden-amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Rancher OG.name: Grape Rancher OG
Grape Rancher OG.description: Grape Rancher OG is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (75% indica/25% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Purple Kush X Route 66 strains. Perfect for any indica lover who wants a little help getting to sleep at night, Grape Rancher OG packs a high level of potency and a super delicious flavor. The Grape Rancher OG high starts with a subtle building effect, filling your mind with a sense of expansive and unfocused euphoria. As your mind lifts further into this heady state, a sense of deep relaxation will begin to wash over your physical form, leaving you helplessly couch-locked and pretty sedated before you know it. Thanks to these effects and its high 15-21% average THC level, Grape Rancher OG is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, nausea or appetite loss, and depression or mood swings. This bud has a sweet fruity herbal flavor with a lightly spicy exhale. The aroma is of earthy herbs and spicy berries with a sweet overtone that lingers long after the nugs are burned away. Grape Rancher OG buds have hard rounded dark olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, deep amber hairs and a coating of purple-tinted crystal trichomes.

Grape Romulan.name: Grape Romulan
Grape Romulan.description: Grape Romulan is an out-of-this-world indica dominant hybrid (80% indica/20% sativa) strain that's an insanely delicious crossbreed of the famously potent Romulan X Grapefruit strains. This bud offers a moderate 16-18% THC level that is perfect for newer patients and more seasoned patients alike. The Grape Romulan nug is caked with sugary white crystals and has a neon green body with deep purple and violet-red hues and orange hairs. When smoked, this frosty bud gives a soothing high that leaves you alert and focused but completely relaxed in body. Be ready for euphoric bouts of creativity and an insanely potent 2-3 hour duration of effects. Be careful not to overdose on this strain - Grape Romulan is known to give users dizziness, the jitters, and psychedelic effects if too much is smoked at once. Grape Romulan tastes exactly how it sounds - musky, sour-grape candy with an earthy grape smell. Because of its uplifting effects and full-body relaxation, its oftentimes used to treat depression, anxiety, and chronic pain. Grape Romulan is sure to take you to a smooth, fruity high that is out of this world!

Grape Skin.name: Grape Skin
Grape Skin.description: Grape Skin, also known as “Cookies Grape Skin,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other hybrid strains. Although its exact parentage is kept a closely guarded secret, Grape Skin is often highly sought out for its super well-balanced high and delicious flavor that’s perfect for any purple kush lover. The high starts with a heady lift that fills your mind with giddy euphoria and a sharp sense of clarity and focus. This focus will soon ebb and fade away, replaced with heady relaxation that permeates your entire brain. Soon, your body will begin to settle into an accompanying relaxing state that has you fully couch-locked and pretty sedated before you know it. Combined with its high 20-29% average THC level, these sleepy effects make Grape Skin a great choice for treating chronic stress, depression, insomnia, ADD or ADHD, headaches or migraines and chronic pain. This bud has a super sweet and sugary fruity grape flavor with a light touch of nutty cookies upon exhale. The aroma is much like a fruity grape cookie with a hint of earthy spiciness to it, too. Grape Skin buds have oversized and fluffy grape-shaped forest green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, golden white crystal trichomes.

Grape Smuggler.name: Grape Smuggler
Grape Smuggler.description: Grape Smuggler is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) strain created through crossing the iconic Grape Ape X Face Off OG BX1 strains. Looking for a super delicious grape flavor? You've found it. Grape Smuggler packs a super mouthwateringly delicious sweet berry flavor into each and every spicy toke. The aroma is very similar, although with a slightly sour dank overtone to it. The Grape Smuggler high is just as delectable as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that hit both mind and body with a high level of potency thanks to its super high 15-23% average THC level. It starts first in the head with a buzzy effect, filling your cerebral state with a hazy unfocused layer of bliss. As your mind lifts into pure blank happiness, your body will begin to settle into a heavy couch-locked state that leaves you pretty stoned. These effects quickly turn sedative, which can have you dozing off in no time at all if you're not careful. With these effects and its high potency level, Grape Smuggler is recommended for the experienced patient suffering from conditions such as migraines or headaches, chronic stress, insomnia, chronic pain, and muscle spasms or cramps. This bud has fluffy popcorn-shaped olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, sparse orange hairs, and a coating of thin white crystal trichomes.

Grapes N Cream.name: Grapes N Cream
Grapes N Cream.description: Grapes N Cream, also known as “Grapes and Cream,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Pie X Sundae Driver strains. This celebrity child boasts a super mouthwatering flavor and a heavy-hitting high that will have you flying high before dropping you right back down into sweet sedation. Like its name suggests, Grapes N Cream has a sweet and creamy sugary vanilla flavor that's accented by fresh and fruity grapes and cherries. The aroma is just as delicious, with a spicy grape overtone that's accented by sweet and sugary fruits. The Grapes N Cream high comes on a few minutes after your final toke, hitting the mind with a sense of creative focus while lulling the body into a state of pure relaxation and ease. You'll feel your senses sharpen as your creative sense expands, allowing you to access your sociability and easily carry on conversations with those around you. At the same time, a calming body high will work its way into your physical form, helping to ease aching muscles while making you pretty hungry, too. In combination with its high 23-35% average THC level, these effects make Grapes N Cream perfect for treating depression, nausea or appetite loss, chronic stress or anxiety and inflammation. This bud has fat oversized rounded bright neon green nugs with deep amber undertones, thick orange hairs and frosty golden amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Soda.name: Grape Soda
Grape Soda.description: Grape Soda is an indica dominant hybrid strain created as a potent phenotype of the infamous Tahoe OG Kush strain. If you're in the market for a super tasty grape flavor, you've found it! Grape Soda brings on the sweet grape tastes and accents them with citrus and pine for a flavorful all around toke. The aroma takes on an earthy tinge, with a pungent grape effect that becomes slightly spicy as the nugs are burned. The Grape Soda high has a lightly lifting effect that starts with a touch of focus before fading into happy relaxation. You'll feel a light pressure behind the eyes that soon transitions into a happy euphoria with mental clarity. As your mind settles into this focused state, your body will start to drop into a state of calm that doesn't affect your energy level in the slightest. Rather, you'll be physically at ease as your mind functions at the optimal level. With these effects and its high THC level, Grape Soda is often chosen to treat conditions such as depression, headaches or migraines, inflammation, and chronic pain. This bud has fluffy forest green nugs with piecey orange hairs and tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Grapes of Wrath.name: Grapes of Wrath
Grapes of Wrath.description: Grapes of Wrath, also known as “The Grapes of Wrath,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Grape Pie X Jet Fuel Gelato strains. Named for its delicious flavor and high-powered effects, Grapes of Wrath will have you feeling great for hours on end with just one tasty little toke. The high starts fast and hard, slamming into your brain with a lifted sense that fills you with a sense of euphoria. You'll feel almost giddy in this state with a rush of creativity that gets you chatting with those around you and easily laughing. At the same time, a relaxing body high will take hold, locking you to the couch and leaving you totally sedated. Thanks to these effects and its high 21-23% average THC level, Grapes of Wrath is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, depression, PTSD, mood swings and insomnia. This bud has a sweet and fruity grape berry flavor with a lightly flowery diesel exhale. The aroma follows the same profile, with a sweet and spicy nutty grape overtone accented by earthy diesel and flowery herbs. Grapes of Wrath buds have small grape-shaped dark olive green nugs with purple undertones, vivid orange hairs and a coating of purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Grape Stomper.name: Grape Stomper
Grape Stomper.description: Grape Stomper, also known as “Sour Grapes,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the classic Purple Elephant X Chemdawg Sour Diesel strains. With its sour taste and sweet sativa heavy effects, Grape Stomper will have you begging for more after just one toke. Its sweet and sour grape candy flavor is deceptively delicious and often leads to users having a little too much at once, especially given that its THC level falls between 18-26% on average. The aroma is just as sweet, with a super strong sour overtone and a fruity candy effect that's complemented by a potent earthiness that's released as the nugs are broken apart. The Grape Stomper high is an almost immediate full body experience that is uplifting yet relaxing in nature. The high hits you hard with a tingly punch to the head, pulling your mind into utter bliss and infusing it with a slight sense of social energy. This tingle will spread throughout the rest of your body slowly, laving you completely relaxed and at ease, although not weighed down in the slightest sense. Because of these effects, Grape Stomper is often chosen to treat chronic pain, mood swings, depression, chronic fatigue, and chronic stress. This bud has dense forest green spade-shaped nugs with bright orange hairs and a frosty coating of oversized chunky white crystal trichomes.

Grape Stomper Alien DD.name: Grape Stomper Alien DD
Grape Stomper Alien DD.description: Grape Stomper Alien DD is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Grape Stomper X Alien Kush strains. This hard-to-come-by bud is infamous for its super rich flavor and high THC level of 22% on average. Grape Stomper Alien DD has a fresh grape flavor with hints of sour earth and lemony pine. The aroma is very pungent and earthy, with a rotting grape effect that's accented by sharp citrus and rich spicy woods. The high comes on soon after your final exhale, slowly building into a happy lift that fills your mind with a sense of euphoria and ease. You'll feel an influx of focus and creativity as the high builds, perfectly complementing the relaxing body high that will fill your physical form. With these potent effects and its high THC level, Grape Stomper Alien DD is recommended for the experienced user suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression, chronic fatigue, ADD or ADHD, and migraines or headaches. This bud has small rounded fluffy olive green nugs with purple undertones, bright orange hairs, and a coating of frosty amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Stomper x Sour Candy.name: Grape Stomper x Sour Candy
Grape Stomper x Sour Candy.description: Grape Stomper X Sour Candy is a unique hybrid strain that varies between being evenly balanced (50% indica/50% sativa) and being slightly indica dominant (60% indica/40% sativa), depending on breeder practices. Although this bud is pretty hard to find, it is well-loved for its slowly building, short lasting effects. The high hits after a few hits, building into a tingly cerebral effect in the head and a sense of laser-sharp focus. You’ll be euphoric and uplifted with tendencies to fall into fits of uncontrollable giggles. As you start to come down, you’ll fall into a sleepy and hazy state that typically end in a deep and peaceful sleep. These effects coupled with its powerful 25.71% average THC level and 1.73% average CBD level make Grape Stomper X Sour Candy perfect for treating patients suffering from chronic stress or anxiety, chronic pain, and appetite loss. This bud has a flavor of sweet juicy grape with a smooth hash exhale. The aroma is of strong grape pine with an earthy undertone. This bud has medium-sized dark forest green nugs with light green patches, sparse amber hairs, and a thick frosty coating of amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Topanga.name: Grape Topanga
Grape Topanga.description: Grape Topanga is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Grape Pie X Topanga Canyon OG strains. The perfect flavorful hybrid, Grape Topanga is ideal for a day when you want to get a quick pick-me-up but don't have much of anything to do at all. This bud has a sweet and fruity grape flavor with a rich spicy tropical fruit exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a peppery tropical overtone accented by spicy grapes and fresh earth. The Grape Topanga high is definitely a creeper, waiting a few minutes before it finally takes hold. You'll feel a light lifted sense in your forehead and behind the eyes that boosts the spirits and fills you with a feeling of almost giddy euphoria. A sense of calm comes next, washing over both mind and body and leaving you fully relaxed from head to toe. Combined with its super high 27-30% average THC level, Grape Topanga is often recommended for experienced patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression, chronic stress, mood swings and insomnia. This bud has dense grape-shaped minty green nugs with vivid orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny golden amber crystal trichomes.

Grape Train Kush.name: Grape Train Kush
Grape Train Kush.description: Grape Train Kush, also known as “Grape Snow Train Kush,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the powerful (WiFi OG #3 X Snow Lotus) X Trainwreck strains. If you're after a deliciously fruity bud with a super heavy high, you've found it with Grape Train Kush. Like its name suggests, Grape Train Kush has a sweet and fruity berry grape flavor with touches of fresh anise and spicy black pepper. The aroma is very much the same, although much spicier, with a fruity grape overtone accented by spicy black pepper, earthy kush and rich anise. The Grape Train Kush high isn't quite as vibrant, with effects that will have you feeling totally stoned in no time at all. It starts with a slow build of effects, creeping into both mind and body with a slowly building sense of weightiness. One minute you'll feel nothing and the next you'll be hit with a train of heavy sedation that leaves your eyes drooping and your body hopelessly locked to the couch. This combination will quickly turn sleepy, causing you to immediately doze off before you realize what's happening. Combined with its high 15-20% average THC level, these effects make Grape Train Kush a great choice for treating chronic stress or anxiety, nightmares or insomnia and chronic pain. This bud has fat oversized grape-shaped forest green nugs with dark amber undertones, thin orange hairs and tiny purple-white crystal trichomes.

Grapeview Glory.name: Grapeview Glory
Grapeview Glory.description: Grapeview Glory is an indica dominant hybrid (70% indica/30% sativa) strain created through crossing the extremely rare Transparent Grape X Myers Lemon strains. This delicious combination makes for one tasty treat with an outrageously high terpine profile that packs a unique grape blueberry citrus flavor and well-balanced yet lazy effects. Grapeview Glory buds have a delicious blueberry citrus flavor that's surprisingly exactly how it sounds. The aroma is of sweet pine accented by lemons and berries with just a touch of subtle earthiness. These buds have round hairy dark olive green nugs with bright red orange hairs and a coating of tiny amber crystal trichomes. The Grapeview Glory high is very energetic yet somehow lazy in nature, making it perfect for kicking back on a lazy Saturday afternoon when you still might have to get something of use done. It starts with an energetic lift that boosts you mood and leaves you feeling confident and ready to tackle anything that comes your way. As this energy level builds, a combatting sense of complete lethargy and laziness will overcome you, launching you into a sense of couch-lock and a crazy powerful case of the munchies. With these effects and its powerful 20-24% average THC level, Grapeview Glory is perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, insomnia, appetite loss, and migraines or headaches.

Grape Wreck.name: Grape Wreck
Grape Wreck.description: Grape Wreck, also known as “Ape Wreck,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Grape Ape X Trainwreck strains. Like its Ape Grape parent, this bud packs a mouthwatering flavor of sweet musky grape with a super smooth exhale that will leave you begging for more. The aroma is of rich red wine with a slightly earthy overtone that's somehow both pungently musky and delicious. Grape Wreck buds have thick spade-shaped dark olive green nugs with rich purple undertones and leaves, bright amber hairs, and a striking coating of bright white crystal trichomes. The Grape Wreck high is not to be underestimated – much like its Trainwreck parent, you can expect head heavy effects that leave you stoned and experiencing borderline psychedelic effects, although at a heavier level due to its insanely high THC level that typically bottoms out at about 24% on average. It starts with a powerful cerebral slam to the head that drops your mind into a hazy stoned situation where you can hardly focus on anything. As your mind drifts further and further away, your body will be slowly overtaken by a heavy body high that leaves you completely sedated and helpless to move. Because of these powerful effects, Grape Wreck is perfect for the experienced user suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, muscle spasms or tremors, insomnia, and appetite loss.

Grapist.name: Grapist
Grapist.description: Grapist is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (75% indica/25% sativa) created through crossing the potent Tony's Grape X Hawaiian Indica strains. Perfect for any indica lover who loves a great fruity flavor, Grapist brings on a super relaxing high that is perfect for any late night kick back. The high starts with a subtle lifted feeling that slowly builds behind the eyes and forehead, expanding its happy tendrils through your mind and leaving you feeling totally euphoric and without a care in the world. A relaxing body high accompanies this lifted state, keeping you totally calm and at ease as you settle further and further into sleepy sedation before you finally fade away into a long and peaceful nap. In combination with its super high 19-20% average THC level, these effects make Grapist perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, muscle spasms or cramps, and spasticity. The flavor is of sweet and sour tropical citrus with a lightly spicy grape exhale. The aroma is of citrusy herbs and spices with an earthy tropical overtone that's accented by deep dank grapes. Grapist buds have conical fluffy forest green nugs with thick orange hairs and a coating of frosty tiny golden crystal trichomes.

Grateful Dawg.name: Grateful Dawg
Grateful Dawg.description: Grateful Dawg is a rare indica dominant hybrid (80% indica/20% sativa) strain created through crossing the classic Dawg Waltz X Gupta Kush strains. This combination creates a beautiful relaxing high that's fueled by both a high THC level and a high CBD level. The Grateful Dawg high comes on slowly, filling your mind with happy thoughts and racing any painful or racing ones. As your mind starts to fall into a state of calm, a euphoric lift will come, pulling you into a state of pure bliss. As this high continues, it will start to expand throughout the rest of your body, dropping you into a state of pure deep relaxation that can cause you to become sleepy at times. Thanks to these powerful effects and its medicinal nature, Grateful Dawg is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic pain, stress or anxiety, muscle spasms, and insomnia. This bud has a classic spicy grape flavor with hints of fruity diesel on each pungent exhale. The smell is very earthy and sweet with a grape diesel overtone that can fill a room. This bud has tight spade-shaped minty green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny golden crystal trichomes.

Grateful Glue.name: Grateful Glue
Grateful Glue.description: Grateful Glue is an indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through a cross of the infamous Gorilla Glue #4 X Grateful Breath strains. This bud combines the best of both of its parents, melding a mind-bending high from GG#4 with the delicious flavors and lung expansion from Grateful Breath for a beautiful and lifted high from start to finish. The Grateful Glue high starts with a lifted feeling that builds behind the eyes and in the forehead before expanding into an unfocused state of euphoria. You'll feel a lightly tingly relaxing body high wash over you as your mind settles, leaving you ravenously hungry and slightly couch-locked. Soon this combination of effects will have you feeing very sedated, which often ends in a long and peaceful sleep. With these effects and its high 21-28% average THC level, Grateful Glue is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, chronic stress or anxiety, insomnia, and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet fruity berry flavor with a light coffee diesel exhale. The aroma is very earthy with a pungent coffee overtone accented by sour spices and chemicals as the nugs are burned. Grateful Glue buds have super sticky dense neon green spade-shaped nugs with yellow hairs and a coating of bright amber crystal trichomes.

Gravenstein.name: Gravenstein
Gravenstein.description: Gravenstein, also known as “Gravenstein Tangerine,” is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (70% sativa/30% indica) created through crossing the delicious (New York City Diesel X G-13 Haze) X Sweet Tooth #3 F2 strains. Odd name aside, Gravenstein is often sought out for its vibrant flavor and even brighter effects. This bud has a super sour yet sugary sweet tangerine taste with hints of orange candies galore. The aroma is just as heavy, with a delightfully tangy orange overtone accented by punches of sour citrus and flowery earthiness. The Gravenstein high is every bit as bright, with vibrant daytime effects that will have you soaring for hours on end. You'll feel a near instant boost of energy smash into your brain with your first exhale, lifting you into a euphoric cerebral state that has you feeling mentally stimulated and ready to jump on your to-do list. But you'd better act fast – a relaxing body high will soon settle in, keeping you physically calm without affecting your mental energy level. Combined with its super high 23-24% average THC level and 0-1% average CBD level, these effects give Gravenstein an edge in treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, cramps or PMS, chronic stress, depression and chronic pain. This bud has oversized grape-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thin red-orange hairs and chunky, amber crystal trichomes.

Gravity OG.name: Gravity OG
Gravity OG.description: Gravity OG is indica dominant hybrid strain and it has a 90:10 indica/sativa ratio. Little is known about the strain and its heritage but one thing is for certain: it is not for the faint of heart. With an amazing 27% THC content it produces lush green buds with red hairs seeping through the surface. The nuggets are tight and dense and have relatively good trichome coverage. The taste and smell are what truly sets this strain apart from the rest of the crowd. It has a musky citrus scent with a nutty, rotten grapefruit flavor which is mouthwatering to say the least. One of the best things about this strain is that it offers a sensational high. Considering its body numbing effects, it will put you to sleep in no time. The effects tend to last longer and will keep you medicated for long. You may even feel euphoric and happy which is why it is often recommended to patients suffering from stress, depression and anxiety. The body buzz is great and can help you accomplish some of your daily tasks to a certain extent but that depends on how much of the strain you have already consumed. On the other hand, it does have other applications and can also be used to treat individuals suffering from mood disorders, anorexia and muscle spasms.

Gravy.name: Gravy
Gravy.description: Gravy is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Orange Apricot X MAC #5 strains. Don't let the name of this bud scare you off – Gravy doesn't actually taste like gravy. Rather, this bud has a super sugary and sour citrusy orange flavor with. hints of fresh spices and earthy woods. The aroma is just as vibrant, with a sour orange overtone accented by spicy kush, earthy skunk and woody herbs. The Gravy high will settle in with a slow burn of effects, washing over you in warming waves before fully taking hold. You'll find your mind settling down into a state of happiness that boosts your spirits without increasing your energy level. At the same time, your body will begin to settle further and further into a state of pure relaxation that's slightly weighty and pleasantly warming. This state will soon turn into heavy couchlock and sedation, leaving you dozing off before you know it. Combined with its high 24-25% average THC level, these effects make Gravy a great choice for treating chronic stress or anxiety, inflammation, chronic pain, insomnia and depression. This bud has dense conical forest green nugs with yellow-green undertones, thick orange hairs and frosty, golden-white crystal trichomes.

Greaseball.name: Greaseball
Greaseball.description: Greaseball, also known as “Grease Ball,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (80% indica/20% sativa) created through crossing the classic Afghani X Chemdawg X Trainwreck strains. If you're into super sticky strains that will leave you swirling around in your own mind, look no further. Greaseball brings on everything that you've been dreaming of and more, all wrapped up with a super sweet flavor and long-lasting high. This bud has super dense and small rounded olive green nugs with clear amber hairs and a frosty thick coating of clear crystal trichomes that are practically dripping with sweet syrupy resin. As you break apart each sticky little nugget, sharp sour apple and flowery chemical aromas are released, turning pungent as the nugs are burned. The flavor is of Granny Smith apples with a light touch of spicy florals and pungent earth upon exhale. The Greaseball high is definitely one that's best suited for the end of the day when you need a little extra help to get kicked back and relaxing. With these effects and its high 19-24% average THC level, Greaseball is the perfect choice for any patient suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, depression, chronic stress, and nausea or appetite loss.

Grease OG.name: Grease OG
Grease OG.description: Grease OG is an indica dominant strain with an amazing 20% THC content. With an 80:20 indica/dominant strain, it is incredibly potent and effective to medicate with. Even though little is known about the strain and its genetics, one thing is for certain it is every cannabis users dream strain. The strain is extremely rare to come across. In fact, it has made quite a few appearances to the general public in recent years. The taste and aroma is a blend of sweet ginger and diesel fuel, which indicates is genetics belong to the 'Fuel family'. The high is exceptionally good and strong to say the least. You will feel the high start from your head and make its ways through the rest of your body in no time. Even the most experienced of cannabis users will find the strain to be overwhelming. Any individual who has medicated with Grease OG will tell you that the high originates from the back of the eyes. Rest assured you will still be in control and will feel creative, talkative and happy. On the other hand, Grease OG is renowned for being used to treat medical conditions like insomnia, anxiety, anorexia, muscle spasms and even chronic pains and aches.

Greasy Pink Bubba.name: Greasy Pink Bubba
Greasy Pink Bubba.description: Greasy Pink Bubba, also known simply as “Greasy Pink,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the classic Bubba Kush X Pink Kush strains. Named for its celebrity parentage and gorgeous appearance, Greasy Pink Bubba is the perfect choice for any fan of iconic indicas. Like its name suggests, Greasy Pink Bubba has beautiful small tapered spade-shaped forest green nugs with thick dark amber hairs and a coating of frosty, milky pink-tinted white crystal trichomes dripping with sweet sticky resin. As you pull apart each greasy little nugget, aromas of spicy flowers, pungent diesel and earthy herbs are released, intensifying in potency the more that you toke. The flavor is on the lighter side of things, with a sweet and flowery flavor that's accented by spicy diesel and a punch of pungency that's still sweet. The Greasy Pink Bubba high will hit you a few minutes after your final exhale, sneaking into your brain with a creeping effect before suddenly taking hold. You'll find your mind suddenly dropped into a calming yet euphoric plane that has you feeling absolutely amazing and not really able to focus on much of anything. This heady state will soon turn sedative, leaving you falling in and out of a dozy state that can have you falling asleep before you know it. With these effects and its high 22-25% average THC level, Greasy Pink Bubba is often chosen to treat chronic pain, appetite loss or nausea, insomnia and mood swings or depression.

Greasy Runtz.name: Greasy Runtz
Greasy Runtz.description: Greasy Runtz is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Runtz X Grease Monkey strains. If you're on the hunt for a great classic indica with an amazing flavor, too, you've found it with Greasy Runtz. This bud backs a mouthwatering sugary cherry berry candy flavor with hints of fresh tropical citrus upon exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a sweet fruity berry overtone accented by sour tropical citrus and spicy earthiness, too. The Greasy Runtz high hits you a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your brain almost immediately with an expansive sense of lifted happiness and creativity. You'll find your mind fading in and out of focus as you fall further and further into this blissful state. A relaxing body high accompanies this heady lift, filling your physical form with a light heaviness that is soothing and calming at the same time. This combination can turn sedative at times, so mind your dosage if you have anything to get done. Combined with its super high 20% + average THC level, these effects make Greasy Runtz a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as depression, chronic stress, insomnia and nausea or appetite loss. This bud has grape-shaped dark olive green nugs with dark purple undertones, vivid red-orange hairs and a coating of frosty chunky white crystal trichomes.

Great Divide.name: Great Divide
Great Divide.description: Great Divide is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the potent Kosher Kush X Phishhead Kush strains. If you're on the hunt for the perfect combination of heady and physical effects, look no further than the Great Divide. This bud packs soothing, full-bodied effects that will boost the spirits before helping you gently settle down into deep relaxation. You'll feel happy a few seconds after your first toke as your mind is filled with an expansive bliss that is pretty heady and unfocused. A soothing body high comes next, creeping slowly into your limbs and leaving you feeling locked to the couch and immovable for hours on end. Thanks to these effects and its high 10-15% average THC level and 10-15% CBD level, Great Divide is often chosen to treat those patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, depression, inflammation, insomnia and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has a sweet and fruity citrusy pineapple flavor with hints of woody pine. The aroma is very similar, although spicier, with a sweet tropical fruit overtone accented by fresh woods. Great Divide buds have oversized and fat fluffy grape-shaped olive green nugs with deep purple undertones, thin red-orange hairs and tiny, purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Great Northern.name: Great Northern
Great Northern.description: Great Northern is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain with unknown parentage due to a high level of breeder secrecy about its background. Grown in Northern California, this bud is beloved by growers and patients alike for its sturdy structure and full-bodied effects. Great Northern buds have super sticky and dense minty green grape-shaped nugs that are totally covered with bright orange hairs and frosty golden amber crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sparkling nugget, aromas of spicy herbs and sharp sour citrus are released, all wrapped up with a pleasant earthy woody overtone. The flavor is very similar, with a sour lemon taste that’s accented by pine and sweet herbs. The Great Northern high is definitely a classic sativa, with energizing effects that will get you up and moving before you finally settle down into deep relaxation and ease. It starts in the head with a boost of the spirits, filling your mind with a sense of cerebral euphoria and creative energy that really helps get you moving on your to-do list and helps inspire conversation with those around you. With these long-lasting effects and its moderately high 16-18% average THC level, Great Northern is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, depression, chronic stress and chronic pain.

Great White.name: Great White
Great White.description: Great White, also known as “Great White Shark” or “Peacemaker,” is a sativa dominant hybrid (65% sativa/35% indica) strain created by crossing Super Skunk X Brazilian X South Indian strains. This bud has small and fluffy dark forest green nugs that are spattered with thin amber colored hairs and a thick frosty coating of oversized chunky white crystal trichomes and sweet sticky resin. The Great White flavor is of sweet citrus with an earthy skunkiness upon exhale that is accented by fruitiness. The aroma is of sweet skunky tobacco with a hint of citrus pungency upon breaking the nugs apart and smoking them. The exact THC level of this bud varies from about 12-15% on average, although the high is relatively strong. It starts with an almost immediate onset of a cerebral head rush that leaves you euphoric and happy with a touch of haziness. The more spacey you become, the more a body buzz will spread throughout you, leaving you couch-locked and completely relaxed as your mind soars. These effects combined with its moderate THC level make Great White perfect for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, migraines, chronic stress or anxiety, and inflammation.

Great White Shark.name: Great White Shark
Great White Shark.description: Great White Shark, also known more commonly as "Peacemaker" or "White Shark" among the cannabis community, is a indica dominant hybrid (80% sativa/20% indica) strain that is an extremely potent cross between the hugely popular Super Skunk X Brazilian X South Indian strains. This dank bud boasts a moderate THC level that ranges from 15-21% and was the 1997 winner of the High Times' Cannabis Cup for Best Hybrid. Users describe the Great White Shark high as having an almost immediate onset of an intense cerebral head high that leaves you feeling easily distracted and cloudy. This spaciness is accompanied by a slowly building warming buzz that spreads evenly throughout your mind and body, leaving you feeling completely relaxed and pain-free. Upon the come down, you'll be eased into a deep and peaceful sleep. Due to these potent effects, Great White Shark is ideal for treating chronic pain, muscle spasms, and anxiety or stress. This bud has an aroma and taste of sweet tobacco with a pungently harsh aftertaste upon exhale. Great White Shark buds have small fluffy dark olive green nugs with rich amber hairs and undertones as well as a layer of thick chunky white trichomes and sweet sticky resin.

Green -O- Matic.name: Green -O- Matic
Green -O- Matic.description: Green-O-Matic is a heavily indica dominant hybrid (90% indica/10% sativa) strain created through a four-way cross of Ruderalis X Moroccan X White Dwarf X Low Rider strains. Don't let its ruderalis parentage fool you – this bud packs a long-lasting stoney high, albeit pretty mild, powered by an impressive 15% average THC level. The high hits you quickly, almost immediately after your first toke, with an uplifting cerebral calm. This is followed by a powerful body buzz that leaves you couch-locked and hungry. You'll feel stoned in body but energized and uplifted mentally. These effects last for hours after you smoke, making this bud ideal for a wake and bake when you need a boost of quick energy to get you going. Green-O-Matic is ideal for treating patients suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, appetite loss, muscle spasms, chronic pain, and inflammation. Green-O-Matic has a very fresh and fruity flavor with a hint of melon and sweet berries. The aroma is very fragrant, with a melon grape smell that's accented by an earthy tinge. These buds have long and narrow very piecey light green nugs with lots of bright orange hairs and fine amber hued crystal trichomes.

Green Apple OG.name: Green Apple OG
Green Apple OG.description: Green Apple OG is a heavily sativa dominant hybrid (90% sativa/10% indica) strain created by breeders at the infamous Green Apple Co-Op farms in Santa Ana, California. This dank bud has unknown genetics due to breeder secrecy and boasts a moderate THC level ranging from 15-18% on average. Green Apple OG has a memorable aroma of a freshly baked apple pie and a taste akin to a Granny Smith apple doused in powdered sugar. This bud has dense yet fluffy bright neon green buds with sparse dark olive green twisty leaves and thick rich amber hairs and amber undertones. These nugs are dusted with a fine layer of milky white almost amber trichomes and sweet sticky resin. Users describe the Green Apple OG high as having a heavy sativa high. Upon the onset, you'll feel an intense feeling of uplifted euphoria and a burst of creative energy. This is accompanied by an all-encompassing buzz felt primarily behind the eyes and in the forehead and back of the head that leaves you with significant mind relief. The high from smoking Green Apple OG is hugely potent and tends to last hours on end. Due to these effects, this bud is ideal for treating arthritis pain, chronic stress, and fatigue.

Green Beret.name: Green Beret
Green Beret.description: Green Beret is a 100% pure sativa hybrid strain with unknown parentage due to a high level of breeder secrecy about it. Even with its rarity and the general lack of knowledge about it, Green Beret brings a medicinal head-heavy high that lasts for hours on end with no release. The high starts with a cerebral onset that boosts your mood with a powerful effect, infusing you with a sense of euphoria that lasts for hours. As your happiness builds and builds, your body will fall into a state of deep relaxation that doesn’t weigh you down but rather leaves you feeling at ease and able to accomplish anything on your to-do list. With these effects and its powerful 19-20% average THC level, Green Beret is the perfect sativa heavy strain for treating conditions such as fatigue, chronic migraines or headaches, mood swings, and chronic stress. This bud has a sweet herbal flavor with hints of rich florals and earth and a super smooth exhale. The aroma is just as delicious with an herbal earthy overtone accented by sweet florals and a fragrant effect that’s released as the nugs are burned. Green Beret buds have small piecey light minty green nugs with bright amber hairs and a matching coating of tiny amber colored crystal trichomes.

Green Crack 2.0.name: Green Crack 2.0
Green Crack 2.0.description: Green Crack 2.0 is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through backcrossing the infamous Green Crack strain. The resulting child is a super potent spiced-up version of its parent, with a super powerful 20% average THC level and long-lasting effects that will leave you cerebrally stimulated for hours on end. The Green Crack 2.0 high hits you fast and hard with mind-boggling cerebral effects that launch you into an energetic state of euphoria and focus. You'll be alert and energized, ready to tackle anything and everything that comes your way. As this heady effects grow, your body will feel a coordinating increase in energy that won't leave you feeling too anxious. Thanks to these effects and its super potent THC level, Green Crack 2.0 is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, PTSD or stress, depression, and migraines or headaches. This bud has a classic sweet tangy flavor of citrus and pine. The aroma is of fresh sweet lemon with a sour zesty woody effect that's released as the nugs are burned. Green Crack 2.0 buds have dense tight bright neon green nugs with light amber hairs and a coating of clear crystal amber trichomes.

Green Crack Auto.name: Green Crack Auto
Green Crack Auto.description: Green Crack Auto is a sativa dominant hybrid strain (45% sativa/35% indica/20% ruderalis) created through crossing the classic Green Crack X an unknown Ruderalis strain. An autoflowering descendant of one of the world's most infamous strains, Green Crack Auto offers the potency you love along with a convenient grow. That being said, the Green Crack Auto is just as potent as its parent strain, with super energizing and lifted effects that will activate the mind and get you moving on any task on your to-do list, whether mental or physical. You'll feel motivated and creative with an influx of focus that works well for any task you need to complete or social situation. Thanks to these effects and its high 20% + average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, Green Crack Auto is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as glaucoma or eye pressure, nausea or appetite loss, Multiple Sclerosis, arthritis, epilepsy and PMS. This bud has a classic sweet tropical citrus flavor with a lightly peppery exhale. The aroma follows the same profile, with a spicy peppery overtone accented by sweet mango and sour tropical citrus. Green Crack Auto buds have oversized and fluffy spade-shaped dark green nugs with minty undertones, thick orange hairs and a coating of tiny chunky white crystal trichomes.

Green Crush.name: Green Crush
Green Crush.description: Green Crush is a 100% pure sativa strain with a reputation among the cannabis community for its insanely high level of CBDs, ranging from 2-3% on average. This dank bud is a potent cross between the hugely popular Skunk X AK-48/Sweet Leaf strains and boasts a THC level ranging from 12-16% on average. Green Crush has dense, leafy heart-shaped nugs that are bright neon green with amber undertones and thick blue hairs. This dank bud is coated in a thick caked-on layer of trichomes and sweet syrupy resin. Green Crush has an aroma of earthy sweet skunk with a vanilla accent and a skunky taste with hints of buttery caramel. Users describe the high of Green Crush as an extreme euphoric cerebral head high that slowly builds until you reach the peak of happiness and mind relief. This leaves you uplifted, focused, creative and motivated with a mellow come down. Patients who use Green Crush to medicate often do so as a wake-and-bake strain due to its uplifting and motivating cerebral effects. Due to its potent sativa effects, Green Crush is an ideal strain for treating patients with conditions such as anxiety, chronic pain, depression, and appetite loss.

Green Curry OG.name: Green Curry OG
Green Curry OG.description: Green Curry OG, also known as “Green Curry” or “Green Curry OG Kush,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of OG Kush strains. Although its exact parentage is kept a closely guarded secret, this bud is often sought out for its delicious flavor and happy effects that are great for any hybrid lover. Like its namesake dish, Green Curry OG packs a super spicy and peppery nutty herbal flavor with hints of sour citrusy lemon and a touch of woodiness. The aroma follows the same profile, with a heavily spicy black pepper overtone accented by herbal sage, sour citrusy lemon and fresh woody pine. The Green Curry OG high will settle in a few minutes after your final exhale, filling your brain with a lifted sense of happy euphoria that pushes out any negative or racing thoughts, replacing them with pure heady bliss. You'll be unfocused yet sociable in this state, attempting to chat with people around you, although you may find yourself falling out of touch with reality and succumbing to fits of the giggles instead. Thanks to these effects and its moderate 15-16% average THC level, Green Curry OG is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress, depression or mood swings and appetite loss or nausea. This bud has fluffy spade-shaped lime green nugs with thin orange hairs and golden-amber crystal trichomes.

Green Demon OG.name: Green Demon OG
Green Demon OG.description: Green Demon OG, also known as “Green Demon” or “Green Demon Kush,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Purple Fever X Fruity Pebbles OG F2 strains. Named for its super heavy high and beautiful buds, Green Demon OG is perfect for any hybrid lover. Green Demon OG buds have small and fat rounded olive green nugs with beautiful amber undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny blue-tinted white crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of sour citrus and spicy herbs are released. The flavor is very similar, with a fruity lemony overtone that turns sour and citrusy upon exhale. The Green Demon OG high isn't quite as bright as the flavor, with effects that lift you up before dragging you right back down. You'll feel the high hit you almost as soon as you exhale, smashing into your brain with a high-flying euphoria that infuses you with mental energy and motivation. But you'd better act quick if you have anything to get done – this lifted state quickly turns heady and stoney, locking you into hazy bliss and leaving you to fade in and out before you finally drift off into a long and peaceful sleep. With these long-lasting and relaxing effects paired with its super high 15-21% average THC level, Green Demon OG is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, insomnia and chronic stress or anxiety.

Green Gelato.name: Green Gelato
Green Gelato.description: Green Gelato is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (55% indica/45% sativa) created through crossing the potent Thin Mint Girl Scout Cookies X Sunset Sherbet strains. If you're looking for a relaxing high and an insanely delicious flavor, you've found it with Green Gelato. This bud packs effects that are best suited for a lazy night at home after a long and stressful day, with a high level of potency that bottoms out at about 25% on average. You'll feel energetic and lifted at the onset before fading away into a deeply relaxing physical state that can have you dropping off to sleep in no time at all. With these effects and its high level of potency, Green Gelato is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, chronic fatigue, mood swings and cramps or muscle spasms. Green Gelato has a sweet creamy mint flavor with a sharp tropical citrus exhale. The aroma is nutty and earthy with a cookie effect that's kicked up a notch by minty tropical citrus. Green Gelato buds have dense rounded grape-shaped neon green nugs with dark purple undertones, bright orange hair sand a coating of tiny clear crystal trichomes.

Green Ghost.name: Green Ghost
Green Ghost.description: Green Ghost is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the potent 7 Ghosts X Bruce Banner #3 strains. Named for its celebrity parentage and gorgeous appearance, Green Ghost is a great choice for any fan of classic hybrid strains. Like its name suggests, Green Ghost has small and rounded vibrant minty green nugs with vivid amber undertones, thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny, milky white crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of pungent dank and spicy kush are released, intensifying in heaviness the more that you toke. The flavor is on the lighter side of things, with a sweet and nutty taste accented by spicy kush and earthy herbs. The Green Ghost high will hit you a few minutes after your first exhale, electrifying your mind with an otherworldly sense of energy. You'll feel insanely euphoric with your mental gears turning, but you'd better act quickly – this effect will soon fade into sleepy nothingness. At the same time, a heavy physical high will lock you to the couch, eventually dropping you into a peaceful and long-lasting sleep. Combined with its high 20-23% average THC level, these effects give Green Ghost an edge in treating chronic pain, depression, chronic fatigue, gastrointestinal disorders and appetite loss or nausea.

Green Goblin.name: Green Goblin
Green Goblin.description: The name "Green Goblin" can refer to two similar strains: either Green Goblin or a phenotype of that plant. In either case, it's a sativa-dominant hybrid with a 65:35 sativa/indica ratio. This strain was created by crossing two popular strains, Northern Lights and Skunk #1. THC levels can be very high, upwards of 24%, and that means a potent head high with a powerful burst of energy. There isn't much CBD in this strain, though, much less than 1%. The high is happy and dreamy, with sharp focus, creativity, and a case of the giggles. Use Green Goblin to treat anxiety, stress, depression, mood disorders, pain, and, for some patients, insomnia. Expect dry mouth and possibly dry eyes, while dizziness and paranoia are less likely. The flavor is earthy and sweet, while the aroma is pungent and loamy. As the name suggests, the dense nugs are lime green with small flecks of brown. Like Green Crack, Green Goblin is found mostly on the West Coast, especially in California and neighboring Oregon, as well as on the legal medical market in Arizona.

Green Goo.name: Green Goo
Green Goo.description: Green Goo, also known as “Green Afgooey,” is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the powerful Green Crack with the super stick Afgoo strain. If you're looking for a resinous bud, you've found it – Green Goo buds are completely coated, if not dripping, with beautiful amber colored resin that is dotted with chunky trichomes. Each thick neon green nug is spattered with rich amber hairs and has long twisty dark leaves that are completely coated in these beautiful resin droplets. As you break apart each nug, fresh spicy citrus aromas are released, which quickly become skunky and pungent as the nugs are burned. The inhale brings fresh fruity pine flavors with hints of skunky herbs and spices on each savory exhale. The Green Goo high is not to be underestimated, with full-bodied effects fueled by a super potent 22% average THC level. IT comes on quickly with a lifted cerebral state that infuses you with creativity and euphoria. This effect will soon become tingly and wash throughout the rest of your body, leaving you buzzing and incredibly aroused. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Green Goo is often chosen by users suffering from conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, stress, insomnia, and chronic pain.

Green Grapes.name: Green Grapes
Green Grapes.description: Green Grapes is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains. Named for its delicious flavor and gorgeous appearance, Green Grapes is the perfect bud for any indica lover. Like its name suggests, Green Grapes has gorgeous small rounded grape-shaped bright neon green nugs with thin amber hairs and a coating of tiny golden amber crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sparkling little nugget, aromas of sour grapes and fresh fruity Granny Smith apples are released, intensifying with hints of spiciness as the nugs are burned away. The flavor is very similar, with a sour grape taste that's accented by sharp apple and spicy earth. The Green Grapes high isn't quite as vibrant as the flavor, with long-lasting effects that hit you hard and last for hours. The high comes on with a creeping effect, sneaking into your mind with a cerebral boost that fills you with a sense of lifted happiness and ease. As your mind flies further and further into oblivion, your body will begin to settle into a deeply relaxing state of calm that has you fully immovable from head to toe. In combination with its high 13-19% average THC level, these effects make Green Grapes a great choice for treating conditions such as nausea or appetite loss, depression, PTSD, insomnia and headaches or migraines.

Green Gum.name: Green Gum
Green Gum.description: Green Gum, also known as “Green Gum CBD” or “Green Gum Hemp,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of other hybrid strains. Although its exact heritage is kept a closely guarded secret by its breeders, Green Gum is often sought out for its super high CBD level and soothing clear-headed effects. You’ll feel the effects wash over yo9u almost as soon as you exhale, filling your mind with a sense of clarity. Your senses will be activated as you are infused with a sense of focus and creativity that are perfect for helping you get to work. A light physical calm comes next, washing over you and helping you to feel fully relaxed from head to toe without any sedation whatsoever. Thanks to these calming effects and its low 0-1% THC level and super high 11-14% average CBD level, Green Gum is often chosen to treat a variety of conditions including chronic stress or anxiety, depression, chronic pain, inflammation, cramps or muscle spasms and the side effects of cancer. Green Gum has a sweet and grassy woody pine flavor with a lightly woody exhale. The aroma is very similar, with a lightly flowery and grassy overtone accented by fresh earthiness and a hint of woody pine. Green Gum buds have dense spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Greenhouse blend.name: Greenhouse blend
Greenhouse blend.description: Greenhouse Blend, also known as “Greenhouse OG,” is a clone only indica dominant hybrid strain that is exclusive to a single dispensary in Pacific Beach, California near San Diego. Although it's a rare find, Greenhouse Blend is a local patient-favorite descendant of OG Kush grown in an all-organic greenhouse. The Greenhouse Blend high is incredibly strong and long-lasting, fueled by a powerful 18-23% average THC level that can prove overpowering to novice users. The high hits you hard with an immediate euphoric effect that quickly fades into a stoney cerebral buzz. This buzz will slowly ebb throughout the rest of your body in tingly waves, leaving you completely sedated and couch-locked with a sharp pang of hunger that will have you eating anything you can find, that is if you can get off the couch. This full-body stone will last for two hours or more and can leave some users falling asleep almost immediately after toking a few times. Because of these effects, Greenhouse Blend is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as insomnia, chronic pain, appetite loss, nausea, and chronic stress. This bud has an earthy lemony flavor of sweet pine and herbs and an aroma of kushy herbs and woody earth with a pungent effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart. Greenhouse Blend buds have dense and leafy bright neon green small round nugs with amber hairs and a frosty thick coating of golden milky trichomes.

Green House Thai.name: Green House Thai
Green House Thai.description: Green House Thai is a sativa dominant hybrid (85% sativa/15% indica) strain created as a cross between the classic Thai X Laotian strains. With an insanely delicious taste and a moderate average THC level between 15-18%, Green House Thai is perfect for any level of cannabis user! It has been said that this bud tastes like Christmas – with a delicate nutty flavor that sweetens with a spicy cinnamon aftertaste, who can possibly disagree? The aroma is very similar, although notes of sandalwood can be detected when the bud is broken apart. In addition to its delicious full-bodied smell and taste, Green House Thai offers a peaceful mind-opening cerebral head high that is somehow both uplifting and relaxing. You'll be hit with deep introspection and philosophical thought, making it a perfect smoke to use for mediation or when practicing yoga. Because of its tendencies to increase energy and motivation, Green House Thai is often used as a morning wake-and-bake smoke. These effects make this bud perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, mild cases of depression, chronic stress, and chronic migraines or headaches. This bud has long tapered bright neon green nugs with gorgeous gold hairs and undertones and light layer of sandy golden milky trichomes.

Green Huckleberry.name: Green Huckleberry
Green Huckleberry.description: Green Huckleberry, or “Huckleberry Crack,” is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the infamous Green Crack with the potent Huckleberry strain. This bud brings on the delicious high-powered flavor of both of its parents strains and gives them an oomph with a potent cerebral high perfect for kicking back in the morning or early afternoon. Green Huckleberry has a sweet herbal berry flavor with a spicy exhale that lingers long after you toke. The aroma is very earthy and dank with a spicy berry overtone that's incredibly fruity and pungent as the nugs are burned. The Green Huckleberry high is that of your typical powerful sativa, brining in high energy levels and euphoria for hours on end. You'll feel a rush of happiness at the onset of the high that lifts you from any mental anguish or pain and eases you into happy bliss. As your head soars, a creeping buzzing energy will wash over your entire body, giving you the fuel that you need to tackle anything that comes your way. In combination with its high 15-20% average THC level, Green Huckleberry is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, depression, chronic stress, migraines, and chronic pain.

Green Inferno.name: Green Inferno
Green Inferno.description: Green Inferno a sativa dominant hybrid (70% sativa/30% indica) strain that was made infamous among cannabis users and nonusers alike by Eli Roth's "The Green Inferno" cannibal-themed stoner movie in 2013. Green Inferno was created by breeders at Gage Green Genetics, who have since then kept its genetics shrouded in secrecy. However, it is thought that Green Inferno is a cross between the insanely popular Inferno Haze X Green Crack strains. This dank bud boasts a THC level ranging from 16-23% on average and an average CBD level of 2%. Green Inferno has an aroma of sweet earthy citrus and a taste of sweet citrus with a peppery earth aftertaste. The Green Inferno buds have huge dense narrow neon green nugs that are furry and leafy with rich gold undertones and forest green hairs. These nugs are covered in a fine layer of trichomes and syrupy sweet resin. Users describe the Green Inferno high as clear-headed and euphoric with an intense body stone and feelings of sedation and relaxation that slowly creep up on you. These feelings are typically accompanied by an intense case of the munchies. Due to these effects, Green Inferno is ideal for treating nausea and lack of appetite as well as anxiety.

Green Kiss.name: Green Kiss
Green Kiss.description: Green Kiss is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains, although it is thought to be a member of the Skunk family. Best known for its gorgeous appearance, Green Kiss packs a super skunky taste and a giddy high that will have you laughing and totally kicked back in no time at all. This bud has super dense grape-shaped emerald green nugs coated with thin minty green hairs and tiny clear crystal trichomes dripping with sweet sticky resin. As you pull apart each heavy little nugget, aromas of pungent skunk and spicy earth are released. The flavor takes on a different profile, with a sweet skunk overtone accented by a kick of chocolate mocha coffee. The Green Kiss high is like experiencing your first kiss all over again, with a light flutter of energy that soon bursts through your mind with a giddy sense of pure euphoria. You'll feel happy with an unfocused mind that has you falling in and out of fits of the giggles while you chat with anyone and everyone around you. A relaxing body high accompanies this heady state, keeping you anchored as you fade further and further into pure bliss. Combined with its high 21-22% average THC level, these effects make Green Kiss perfect for treating chronic pain, depression or mood swings, chronic stress and cramps or muscle spasms.

Green Kryptonite.name: Green Kryptonite
Green Kryptonite.description: A close relative of the powerful Kryptonite indica, Green Kryptonite is a great choice for insomnia and chronic pain. It's an indica-dominant hybrid of Green Crack, a sativa-dominant hybrid, and Kryptonite. The THC levels are largely a mystery, but there's no question this is a strong strain. Green Crack has top THC levels of 24%, while Kryptonite can be even stronger. The exact ratio of sativa to indica is also unknown, though the indica genes are much stronger than the sativa genes. The effects are calming and euphoric, with a significant mood boost. The high lasts longer than most and is ideal for relieving pain and stress. Green Kryptonite has a pungent pine taste and an earthy aroma. It has a bright green appearance similar to Green Crack., with deep flecks of brown and a thick layer of frosty trichomes. It's a great strain for treating insomnia, anxiety, and depression, as well as chronic pain. Unlike its parents, this strain is definitely hard to find. It's probably most common in California and the Pacific Northwest, though it's rare even there.

Greenleaf Platinum Cookies.name: Greenleaf Platinum Cookies
Greenleaf Platinum Cookies.description: Greenleaf Platinum Cookies, also known as "Greenleaf Platinum Girl Scout Cookies," is a super dank indica dominant hybrid (85% indica/15% sativa) strain created by breeders at the infamous Greenleaf Farms. This potent bud is a cross between the insanely popular OG Kush X Cherry Pie X Durban Poison strains and boasts an average THC level ranging from 20-28% and an average CBD level of 1%. Greenleaf Platinum Cookies won 1st Place in the High Times Cannabis Cup in 2012 for best hybrid and is a favorite among all types of patients. The smell of this bud is a mix of all of its parentages – smoky pine from OG Kush, spicy berry from Cherry Pie, and a grassy sweet aftertaste from Durban Poison. The taste can only be described as a minty, well-baked sugar cookie. Users describe the high that comes with using Greenleaf Platinum Cookies as one that is euphoric and uplifting with a sense of focus and alertness. These effects aren't too overpowering due to the high level of CBD in the strain. Because of these effects, Greenleaf Platinum Cookies is ideal for treating patients with conditions such as anxiety, pain, and depression. This bud has dense, tight lime green nugs with orange hairs and a thick layer of crystal trichomes.

Green Manalishi.name: Green Manalishi
Green Manalishi.description: Green Manalashi is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (65% indica/35% sativa) created through crossing the powerful Pacific G13 X G13 Hash Plant strains. Perfect for any indica lover who’s after a true and heavy stone, Green Manalashi brings on the hard-hitting effects that will have you spinning for hours on end. The high starts with a creeping effect, slowly building in the back of the head and neck before taking hold. You’ll suddenly go from toking to a heavy cerebral stone, unfocused and floating in and out of deep hazy introspection. While your mind drops away, your body will fall off, too, leaving you completely couch-locked and immovable, fully relaxed from head to toe. This can quickly take a sedative turn, so mind your dosage if you have anything you need to get done! With these effects and its super high 20% + average THC level, Green Manalashi is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as insomnia, chronic pain, arthritis, chronic stress and depression. This bud has a sweet and sour chunky lemon flavor with a super spicy and herbal aroma to match. Green Manalashi buds have long pepper-shaped minty green nugs with dusty undertones, vivid orange hairs and a coating of tiny dusty amber crystal trichomes.

GREEN marvel.name: GREEN marvel
GREEN marvel.description: Green Marvel is an extremely rare sativa dominant hybrid strain of unknown parentage due to a high level of breeder secrecy. This crazy rare bud is difficult to find east of California, but after tasting its sweet and smooth kushy flavor, you’ll be hooked. Green Marvel has a mild yet sweet spicy kush taste that’s accented by a smooth lemongrass hint upon exhale. The aroma is very mellow, with hints of earthy kush topped with spicy herbs and a subtle sweetness that’s drawn out as the nugs are burned. Green Marvel buds have airy and piecey dark olive green nugs with lot of furry orange hairs and a coating of oversized chunky white milkly crystal trichomes. The Green Marvel high is immediate and well-balanced, with full body effects that are perfect for any hybrid lover. The high starts with a euphoric energetic lift that leaves the user happy and giddy with the tendency to fall into fits of giggles. This is quickly countered by a building body buzz that relaxes the physical form and provides a sense of calm that doesn’t weigh down your energy, but rather serves to anchor it to reality. Because of these effects and its high 20% average THC level, Green Marvel is ideal for treating experienced users suffering from chronic fatigue, mood swings, depression, and chronic stress or anxiety.

Green Panama.name: Green Panama
Green Panama.description: Green Panama is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created as a phenotype of the beloved Panama F8 strain. Named for its classic effects and gorgeous appearance, Green Panama is the perfect choice for any hybrid loving connoisseur. Like its name suggests, Green Panama has beautiful small heart-shaped forest green nugs with deep olive undertones, thin orange hairs and a frosty thick coating of tiny clear crystal trichomes. As you pull apart each sticky little nugget, aromas of spicy flowers and grassy kush are released, accented by touches of woody pine and fresh earthiness. The flavor is very similar, with a sweet flowery overtone accented by spicy woods and fresh earthiness. The Green Panama high is just as delightful, with soothing effects that will help you settle down before gently easing you way into a long and peaceful sleep. It starts with a subtle boost of cerebral effects that boost your mood and fill you with a sense of euphoria and ease. At the same time, a slowly building physical relaxation will begin to seep into your body, helping you to settle down into a state of calm before dropping you into heavy sedation. Combined with its moderate 10-20% average THC level and 0-1% CBD level, these effects make Green Panama a great choice for treating those suffering from conditions such as nausea or appetite loss, chronic stress or anxiety, insomnia and chronic pain.

Green Punch.name: Green Punch
Green Punch.description: Green Punch is a super rare sativa dominant hybrid strain of unknown origins due to breeder secrecy and a general lack of information about it. Even with its rarity, users often say that Green Punch is a perfect blend of energetic and relaxed states, with effects that can amplify anxiety in users who suffer from it. The high starts with a super energetic lift that slams into your forehead with a tingly sensation. You’ll feel motivated and ready to tackle anything that comes your way with a sense of creative inspiration and focus. As this high builds, you’ll become more and more introspective, pulling away from the world into a state of psychoactive creativity that’s oddly relaxing throughout your physical form. These heavy head effects paired with its moderate 7.3% THC level and powerful 13.5% CBD level make Green Punch a highly medicinal choice that’s perfect for treating conditions such as inflammation, chronic stress or anxiety, muscle spasms or cramps, and glaucoma. This bud has bright green airy and round nugs with rich purple undertones, lots of furry amber hairs, and a blanket of thick oversized milky white crystal trichomes. Green Punch has a super strong aroma of sweet tropical fruits accented by hashy earth and florals. The taste is very sweet with a touch of sugary pineapple and citrus accented by herbs and earth.

Green Rainier.name: Green Rainier
Green Rainier.description: Green Rainier, also known as “Rainier Crack” or “Crack Mountain,” is a rare sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the potent Green Crack with the blissful Mount Rainier #2 strain. This bud brings on the relaxation even with its sativa dominance, filling both mind and body with peaceful energy and stimulation for hours on end. The Green Rainier high comes on pretty quickly after your first few hits, launching your mind into a happy cerebral state that's focus and lifted. As your happiness grows and your continues to expand, a slightly buzzy effect will slowly creep from the back of your head and make its way throughout the rest of your body. This effect will be relaxing and somewhat stimulating, leaving you feeling aroused and ready to get up and moving. Thanks to these effects and its high 16-19% average THC level, Green Rainier is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigue, mood swings, depression, and chronic stress. This bud has a sweet herbal citrus flavor with a notable hint of pine on each exhale. The smell is very earthy and citrusy with an almost Pine-Sol like effect. Green Rainier bud shave round grape-shaped bright neon green nugs with orange hairs and a spattering of tiny amber crystal trichomes.

Green Skunk.name: Green Skunk
Green Skunk.description: Green Skunk is a are evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through crossing the infamous Skunk #1 with the potent Green Crack. This bud brings together the classic delicious flavors of both of its parent strains, resulting in a mouthwatering skunky herbal spice flavor with a punch of sharp citrus on each exhale. The aroma is very pungent and skunky with an herbal citrus overtone and hints of spicy earth as the nugs are burned. The Green Skunk high comes on slowly, creeping into your mind with a lifted cerebral effect that fills you with mental energy and a touch of focus. As this effect grows, so will your creativity, lending itself well to any artistic task at hand. Your body will remain relaxed throughout the duration of the high, an effect that can leave you slightly sedated at times as your mind soars through bright activation. In combination with its high 15-20% average THC level, Green Skunk is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic fatigued, depression, migraines or headaches, nausea, and ADD or ADHD. This bud has heavy dark forest green nugs with dark twisty leaves, bright amber hairs, and a coating of rich amber crystal trichomes.

Green Spirit.name: Green Spirit
Green Spirit.description: Green Spirit is a rare evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Big Bud X Skunk #1 strains. Perfect for any hybrid lover, Green Spirit brings on a clear-headed and sociable high that is ideal for getting you moving on a chill day spent at home. You'll feel a lift almost immediately upon your first exhale, boosting your mood and leaving you feeling totally euphoric. A sense of sociability comes next, filling you with mental clarity and creativity that is greatly needed to carry on easy conversations with those around you without much effort at all. With these effects and its high 18-20% average THC level, Green Spirit is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from conditions such as mood swings or depression, chronic pain and chronic stress. This bud has a classic pungent spicy flavor with a skunky exhale that intensifies the more that you toke. The aroma is very earthy and pungent with a skunky overtone that turns dank and spicy as the nugs are burned away. Green Spirit buds have gorgeous oversized spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with vibrant orange hairs and a coating of chunky frosty white crystal trichomes.

Green Steam.name: Green Steam
Green Steam.description: Green Steam is an indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing an unknown combination of other indica hybrids. Although its exact parentage is unknown due to general disagreement and a high level of breeder secrecy, Green Steam is often sought out for its high potency level and super giddy high. In fact, those who enjoy Green Steam often are quoted as saying that it’s like laughter in a toke – you can’t stop giggling with this lovely lady! You’ll feel a lifted sense fill your brain a few minutes after your final toke, pushing out negative or racing thought and replacing them with unfocused giggly happiness that leaves you laughing at everything around you. At the same time, a soothing body high will wash over your physical form, locking you to the couch and leaving you feeling pretty sleepy before you know it. Combined with its high 20%+ average THC level, these effects make Green Steam a great choice for treating chronic pain, insomnia, depression and chronic stress or anxiety. This bud has a sweet and fruity flowery lavender flavor with a grassy and woody pine aroma to match. Green Steam buds have fat triangle-shaped bright emerald green nugs with long curly leaves, thick orange hairs and a coating of frosty, minty white crystal trichomes.

Green Stream.name: Green Stream
Green Stream.description: Green Stream is an Indica strain that is best to use during nighttime. It has long, narrow green colored leaves and the strain has a fresh appearance. It has many green colored buds. The strain has a sweet aroma that has a floral scent. Its taste is quite nice too and is a strong blend of sweet and floral flavors. Green Stream is best used for providing relief from stress and anxiety. Depression patients can smoke it without any worry as well as it has no side effects on their system. It can also help in providing relief from insomnia and aids you in sleeping better at night.
