This strain has an excellent soothing effect on a variety of pains as well, which is why it is perfect for pain management. The exact THC level of Green Stream is not known yet, but it is assumed to be moderate. Most of its effects on your body are safe, except that it makes the eyes and mouth very dry.

Green Sulawesi.name: Green Sulawesi
Green Sulawesi.description: Green Sulawesi, also known as “Green Vein Sulawesi” or “Green Sulawesi Kratom,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through an unknown combination of hybrid strains. Like the classic Green Malay strain, this bud is named for the traditional Kratom medicine used on the island of Sulawesi. That being said, expect a super medicinal high with this bud, packed full of calming effects that soothe aches and pains in both the mind and body. The high starts with a euphoric effect, stimulating the mind with touches of happy energy and creativity that gets your gears turning almost immediately. As your mind expands and sharpens, a soothing tingle will work its way throughout your body, lulling you into a relaxed state that has you fully kicked back and pain-free. Combined with its high 15-20% average THC level, these soothing effects make Green Sulawesi perfect for treating chronic stress or anxiety, depression or mood swings, chronic pain and inflammation. Green Sulawesi has a classic sweet and flowery flavor with a rich woody pine aroma to match. This bud has bright emerald green nugs with clear amber hairs and a coating of golden crystal trichomes dripping with sweet sticky resin.

Green Supreme.name: Green Supreme
Green Supreme.description: Green Supreme is a rare heavily sativa dominant hybrid strain (90% sativa/10% indica) created through crossing the classic Green Crack with another unknown hybrid strain. Looking for a super potent sativa to get you up and moving when you just can't seem to get out of bed? Green Supreme is totally the bud for you. This lovely lady packs a super high 22-26% average THC level and effects that are perfect for a wake-and-bake when you need a little extra oomph. The high starts with a rush of cerebral effects that fill your mind with lifted energy alongside a sense of clarity and focus. An influx of creativity and motivation comes next, lending itself well to any artistic task that you have at hand. A light body high will accompany this cerebral lift, keeping you anchored to the world below without affecting your energy level in the slightest. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, Green Supreme is said to be perfect for treating those suffering from chronic fatigue, depression, ADD or ADHD, chronic stress, and chronic pain. This bud has as super sweet and sour citrusy herbal flavor with a pungent skunky aroma to match. Green Supreme buds have elongated bright green pepper-shaped nugs with lots of light orange hairs and a frosty layer of chunky light amber crystal trichomes.

Green Urkle.name: Green Urkle
Green Urkle.description: Green Urkle is an indica dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the classic Green Crack X Purple Urkle strains. With its super kushy flavor and heady high, Green Urkle is a patient favorite for those who love the classics but with a new-age twist. The high starts with an uplifted onset that infuses you with a sense of happiness, but leaves you incredibly spacey and introspective with the tendency to become distracted and lost in your own thoughts. As you fall victim to your own mind, a sleepy body buzz will start to wash over you, lulling you down into a completely relaxed state in both mind and body that often ends in a deep and peaceful sleep. These effects partnered with its high 16-20% average THC level make Green Urkle great for treating conditions such as chronic pain, insomnia, depression, and migraines or headaches. This bud has a sweet grape flavor with hints of earthy kush and florals. The aroma is very delicate, with an earthy floral overtone that's accented by sweet and spicy kush and just a touch of grape. Green Urkle buds have dense spade-shaped bright green nugs with rich purple undertones, vibrant orange hairs, and a frosty coating of tiny milky white crystal trichomes.

Greyberry.name: Greyberry
Greyberry.description: Greyberry is a rare slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the classic Blueberry X Bubble Gum strains. If you're fan of either of its parent strains, you're going to be head over heels in love with Greyberry. This gorgeous girl packs a super delicious flavor into each and every toke, with tastes of sweet berries and sugary fruity bubblegum dancing across your tongue. The aroma is very similar, although with hints of earth and cherries to it that turn slightly spicy at times. The Greyberry high is just as delightful as the flavor, with lifted effects that are perfect for helping you boost the spirits when you're closing out a long and stressful day or week. You'll feel a sense of euphoria settle into your brain a few minutes after your first toke, throwing out any negative feelings and replacing them with pure happiness and ease. In combination with its high 15-18% average THC level, these effects give Greyberry an edge in treating conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, chronic pain, mood swings, chronic stress and depression. Greyberry buds have grape-shaped dusty green nugs with long thin orange hairs and a coating of sandy amber crystal trichomes.

Grey Mist.name: Grey Mist
Grey Mist.description: Grey Mist is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Power Plant with the peaceful Shiva strain. This bud is a classic among the coffee shop community in Amsterdam, hailing from the infamous Grey Area Coffee Shop. You may also recognize this bud from its role in parenting the powerful Matanuska Mint strain, among many others. All of that being said, Grey Mist is one deliciously potent indica that you'll seek out again and again after just one delicious toke. Grey Mist has a classic sweet and spicy herbal flavor with hints of savory black coffee on each rich exhale. The aroma is very sweet and woody with a pungent chemical effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart. This effect quickly becomes minty as the nugs are burned. Grey Mist buds have light green super dense nugs with furry orange hairs and a sandy coating of tiny milky white crystal trichomes that look almost silvery grey in the right light. The Grey Mist high has a spacey light-headed effect that hits you almost immediately after the first toke and lasts for hours on end afterwards. You'll feel lifted and happy in this state with an inability to focus on much of anything. Thanks to these effects and its moderate THC level, Grey Mist is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as migraines or headaches, glaucoma or eye pressure, nausea, and chronic stress.

Grim.name: Grim
Grim.description: Grim, also known as “Grimace,” is a sativa dominant hybrid (75% sativa/25% indica) strain created through crossing the classic Face Off OG #4 X Purple Urkle strains. With powerhouse parents like these, you know you're in for one hell of a ride! The Grim high hits hard and fast with a euphoric cerebral rush that leaves you feeling insanely happy although utterly relaxed and lethargic. As this laziness washes over you, you'll start to feel slightly sedated and couch-locked and ravenously hungry. This effect can sometimes end in sleep if you toke a little too much at once, even with its sativa dominance. With effects like these and a 15-19% average THC level, Grim is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as appetite loss, chronic pain, depression, and migraines. The Grim flavor is that of a classic OG, with hints of sweet lemon and earthy pungency accented by a spicy exhale that's incredibly smooth. The aroma takes a dank turn with smells of tangy lime and sweet pungent grape with a spicy musky effect that's released as the nugs are burned. Grim buds have oversized dark purple spade-shaped nugs with bright fiery orange hairs and vibrantly white tiny crystal trichomes.

Grim Bastard.name: Grim Bastard
Grim Bastard.description: Grim Bastard is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Biker Kush X Black Banana strains. Don't let the name of this bud scare you away – you'll be anything but with Grim Bastard. This bud packs a super happy and soothing high that stimulates both mind and body, helping to get you the relief that you need in no time at all. You'll feel lifted a few minutes after your final exhale, filled with a happy sense of calm that pushes out any negative moods or racing thoughts gently. Your body will be hit next with a slowly building stimulation that starts as a tingle before turning into a fully-fledged body buzz that's filled with couchlock. This can be arousing at times, too, so mind your dosage if you have things to do. With these effects and its high 21-26% average THC level, Grim Bastard is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress or anxiety, muscle spasms or cramps, depression and chronic pain. This bud has a sweet and sugary fruity banana flavor with a hint of spicy diesel to it, too. The aroma is just as delicious, with a fruity banana overtone accented by woody pine, spicy black pepper and a punch of earthy diesel. Grim Bastard buds have dense spade-shaped bright neon green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, golden-white crystal trichomes.

Grimmdica.name: Grimmdica
Grimmdica.description: Grimmdica is a heavily indica dominant hybrid strain created by the infamous Grimm Brothers growers as a cross of Hash Plant X Afghani. This classic combination results in a high potency flower that brings on your favorite indica effects without causing sleep or heavy sedation. You'll feel a rush of happy tingly energy just a few minutes after your last toke that fills you with a deep permeating sense of relaxation and pretty potent arousal. As your mind and body fill with lifted euphoria, your thoughts will start to fade in and out of introspection and fits of the giggles. Thanks to these buzzy effects and its high THC level, Grimmdica is often chosen to treat patients suffering from ADD or ADHD, PMS, cramps, and depression. Grimmdica packs a classic indica flavor into each toke, blending together tastes of fresh pine and rich fruity florals for a light on the tongue smoke. The aroma is very peppery and nutty with a sweet floral effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart. Grimmdica buds have bright green nugs with rich purple and orange hairs and a coating of bright white chunky crystal trichomes.

Grizzly Kush.name: Grizzly Kush
Grizzly Kush.description: Grizzly Kush is an indica dominant hybrid strain (65% indica/35% sativa) created through crossing the classic The True OG X (The True OG X Abba Zabba) strains. Named for its super-powered high, Grizzly Kush is recommended for experienced patients who need a little potency behind their medicine. That being said, do not underestimate Grizzly Kush – it can easily knock you flat out with just a toke or two if you're not mindful of your dosage. The high starts with a creeping effect, sneaking up on you a few minutes after your final toke and taking hold of your mind and body. You'll feel totally relaxed and unfocused with lifted spirits and an uncontrollable case of the giggles almost immediately. Soon, this turns sedative, knocking you flat on your back as you find yourself slipping away into a deep and peaceful sleep. With these effects and its super potent 22%+ average THC level, Grizzly Kush is best suited for experienced patients suffering from conditions such as appetite loss or nausea, depression, insomnia, and chronic stress. This bud has a classic super sour flavor with a dank kush exhale and a spicy herbal aroma to match. Grizzly Kush buds have chunky oversized bright neon green nugs with lots of amber hairs, frosty white trichomes, and a coating of sweet sticky resin throughout.

Grizzly Ogre.name: Grizzly Ogre
Grizzly Ogre.description: Grizzly Ogre is a super rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Ogre Kush X Grizzly Kush strains. This rare bud may be hard to find on your average market but is infamous among users for its super skunky flavor and long-lasting and lifted effects. Grizzly Ogre buds have a super spicy skunky flavor with hints of sharp citrus. The aroma is very similar, with a sharp earthy overtone accented by skunky citrus that can fill any room with its stench. The Grizzly Ogre high comes soon after your last toke, filling your mind with a rushing euphoria. As your mind lifts to new heights of bliss, you'll start to feel super giggly and talkative, chatting and laughing with anyone and everyone around you for hours on end. A relaxing physical high accompanies this lifted state, keeping you anchored and pain-free as your mind expands. Thanks to these effects and its high 26-32% average THC level, Grizzly Ogre is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress, depression, insomnia, appetite loss, and chronic pain. This bud has oversized heavy amber-green nugs with orange hairs and a coating of chunky sandy crystal trichomes.

Grizzly Purple Kush.name: Grizzly Purple Kush
Grizzly Purple Kush.description: Grizzly Purple Kush is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain (70% indica/30% sativa) created through crossing the infamous Great White Shark X OG Kush strains. If you're looking for a totally gorgeous bud, you've found it! Grizzly Purple Kush buds have oversized super dense olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, dark amber hairs, and a coating of matching crystal trichomes. As you break apart each sticky little nugget, fresh aromas of sour fruits and pungent earth are released with a citrus dank that hangs around long after you toke. The flavor is very sweet and fruity with an earthy citrus overtone that's slightly sour upon exhale. The effects of Grizzly Purple Kush come roaring in a few minutes after your final exhale, slowly creeping and then suddenly ramping up and leaving you insanely lifted and euphoric with a crazy case of the giggles. As your mind expands through happy visions, you'll start to feel a heaviness settle into it and your body, lulling you into a slightly sedated state that can leave you feeling pretty sleepy at times. Thanks to these effects and its super high 23-31% average THC level, Grizzly Purple Kush is often chosen to treat conditions such as chronic stress, nausea or appetite loss, chronic pain, and insomnia.

grouch.name: grouch
grouch.description: The Grouch, also known as “Grouch OG,” is an evenly balanced hybrid (50% indica/50% sativa) strain created through a surprisingly happy cross of OG Kush X Jolly Rancher. Don't let the name fool you – you'll feel anything but grouchy after just one taste of this sweet bud! The Grouch brings a powerfully uplifting high to the table fueled by an 18% average THC level. It hits you first with a euphoric mood boost that pulls your mind out of anxious racing thoughts and replaces it with pure bliss. As your spirits lift, a deep sense of calm will wash over your mind before slowly spreading throughout the rest of your body, leaving you feeling at ease without a care in the world. These smile-inducing long lasting effects are great for treating patients suffering from conditions such chronic pain, migraines or headaches, depression, and inflammation. The Grouch has a sweet lemony pine flavor with a rich berry earth exhale that sweetens with each toke. The aroma is of earthy kush and pine with a citrus effect that's released as the nugs are broken apart and burned. This bud has fluffy spade-shaped olive green nugs with rich purple undertones, amber hairs, and a coating of glittering clear crystal trichomes.

Grunk.name: Grunk
Grunk.description: The Grunk, also known as “Earwax” in its concentrate form,” is a sativa dominant hybrid (70% sativa/30% indica) strain created through a cross of the potent Grape Ape X Skunk #1 strains. This pungent bud is best loved for its effects as a concentrate and its crazy powerful stench. The Grunk has a super musky aroma of pungent skunk with sweet earthy grape hints that are released as the nugs are broken apart and burned. The taste is a little less harsh, with a sweet grapey berry flavor that suddenly takes a turn for the pungent with a skunky earthy aftertaste that stays long after you finish smoking. This bud has super sticky fuzzy spade-shaped forest green nugs with thick furry amber hairs and a light dusting of tiny crystal clear trichomes. In addition to its sticky feel and powerful stench, The Grunk is loved by many for its heavy hitting effects fueled by a 22-24% average THC level. The high starts with a tingly head buzz that provides an uplifted sense of happiness that also serves to slowly wipe away any lingering racing thoughts or mental pain. A relaxing body buzz follows, leaving you completely mellowed out with a slight feeling of sedation that lingers for hours after you finish smoking. These effects make The Grunk perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, nausea, chronic stress or anxiety, mild to moderate cases of depression, and insomnia.

Grunk Panda.name: Grunk Panda
Grunk Panda.description: Gunk Panda is a rare indica dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the classic Grape Ape X Skunk #1 strains. This powerhouse brings on the head-melting effects with a super potent 29-30% average THC level. The high starts with a super strong rush of euphoric energy that barrels through your mind, leaving you totally sedated and unfocused but totally blissful. As your mind settles into oblivion, your body will start to follow suit, leaving you totally relaxed and slightly sedated. As your physical form drops off into a deeper sedation, you'll become totally couch-locked and stoned, immovable for hours and hours on end. Thanks to these effects and its super high THC level, Gunk Panda is often chosen to treat conditions such as depression, insomnia, chronic anxiety or stress, chronic fatigue, and chronic pain. This bud has a heavy skunky pungent earthy flavor with a spicy fruity exhale. The aroma is super heavy and dank with a pungent fruity earthy overtone that fills any room with its crazy powerful stench. Gunk Panda buds have fluffy dense olive green nugs with purple undertones, dark amber hairs, and a coating of chunky matching crystal trichomes.

GSC Extreme.name: GSC Extreme
GSC Extreme.description: Girl Scout Cookies Extreme, also known as “GSC XTRM,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through a cross of the classic Durban Poison X OG Kush strains. A super-powered iteration of the beloved Girl Scout Cookies, this bud takes its classic effects and amps them up to a whole new level of amazing. The high comes on with a quickly building effect, slamming behind the eyes with a lifted sense and filling you with a pure euphoric creativity. As your mind reaches higher and higher into the clouds, you'll feel a sense of relaxation wash over your body, keeping you anchored to the world below and pretty hungry at times, too. With these heavy effects and its super high 19-28% average THC level and 5-10% CBD level, Girl Scout Cookies Extreme is the perfect highly medicinal strain to treat a variety of conditions including depression, nausea or appetite loss, inflammation, chronic pain, and chronic stress. This bud has a classic spicy diesel cookie flavor with a notable punch of pungency to it. The aroma is very earthy and dank with a spicy fuel overtone that intensifies as the nugs are burned. Girl Scout Cookies Extreme buds have long and lumpy bright neon green nugs with lots of thin orange hairs and a thick frosty coating of tiny amber-tinted crystal trichomes.

GSC x Bubba Kush.name: GSC x Bubba Kush
GSC x Bubba Kush.description: GSC X Bubba Kush, also known as “Bubba Scout,” is an indica dominant hybrid strain that packs a super potent 20% + average THC level into each tasty little nugget. The GSC X Bubba Kush is very relaxing in nature and hits harder in the head than the body, even with its indica dominance. The high comes on slowly, lifting your cerebral state subtly before launching you into hazy happiness. You'll start to fall deeper and deeper into beautiful calming visions that leave you distracted and introspective without causing anxiety or paranoia. As your mind falls slowly away, your body will start to relax into a buzzy body high that won't leave you too sedated or couch-locked. Thanks to these effects and its high THC level, GSC X Bubba Kush is said to be perfect for treating conditions such as chronic pain, arthritis, mood swings, appetite loss or anorexia, and depression. This bud has a super sweet and herbal woody flavor that has a notable spicy exhale. The smell is very earthy and herbal with a spicy citrus overtone accented by pungent pine as the nugs are burned. GSC X Bubba Kush buds have fluffy sticky bright green nugs with dark orange hairs and a coating of light amber crystal trichomes.

Gspot.name: Gspot
Gspot.description: Gspot, also known as “gSpot” or “G-Spot,” is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created with unknown parentage, although it is said to be a combination of a bunch of different varieties of OG Kush. If you're looking for the perfect calming yet stimulating hybrid high, this bud will definitely hit the right spot. Gspot brings on full-bodied and tingly effects that fuel the mind while relaxing the body, giving you the perfect arousing experience from start to finish. You'll feel lifted with a sense of buzzing euphoria that boosts your spirit and gets your creative juices flowing. At the same time, this tingly effect will sneak its way throughout your entire body, lulling you into a relaxed state that has you feeling kicked back and at ease without too much sedation. Combined with its insanely high 28-34% average THC level, these effects give Gspot an edge in treating experienced patients suffering from chronic pain, cramps or muscle spasms, chronic stress or anxiety and depression. This bud has a super spicy and flowery woody flavor with a lightly fruity exhale. The aroma is very similar, with an earthy woody overtone that has hints of fresh fruits and lightly spicy flowers. Gspot buds have grape-shaped forest green nugs with thin orange hairs and a coating of tiny golden amber trichomes.
